(1359, 'Zisgq5o7d8joxwrdLP', 'Scholarship', 'CPRG - Social Science research grant', 'https://www.cprgindia.org/ssr/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IkzNHDfz5hY&list=PLGF-es7U0ZzHrYPTCkF2FAADSqqlb7SSt&index=23', 'The Center of Policy Research and Governance (CPRG India) invites applications for the second edition of the CPRG Social Sciences Research Grant (CPRG-SSR Grant). The grant aims to support students and early career researchers working on pertinent themes in Humanities and Social Sciences.<br><br>\r\n<li>Applications from postgraduate, doctoral students, and postdoctoral researchers are invited. <br><br>\r\n<li>The fellowship is open to Indian students from all Indian and foreign universities.<br><br>\r\n<li>Funds are available for fieldwork, archival research, acquisition of primary sources (including reprography of manuscripts), research assistance, or other academic activities.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Students or researchers should be affiliated with recognized universities at the postgraduate level or above and must have good academic standing.<br>\r\n<li>Preference would be given to projects with the viability of publication.<br>\r\n<li>Preference would be given to those who have secured primary grants from elsewhere and want to use the CPRG-SSR grant to supplement them.<br>\r\n<li>For doctoral students, preference would be given to those at advanced stages of their degree.<br><br>\r\n<b>Research Themes:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Research focusing on contemporary India in disciplines such as, but not limited to, sociology, political science, international relations, anthropology, diaspora studies, law and jurisprudence, economics, development studies, environment, and gender studies, among others.<br>\r\n<li>Research focusing on Indian value systems, culture, and history (ancient, medieval, and modern) in humanities and social sciences.', '<li> Research proposal<br>\r\n<li> CV (In case of a joint application, CVs of all co-applicants should be uploaded as a single PDF.)<br>\r\n<li> Writing sample<br>\r\n <li> Budget estimate<br>', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button <br>\r\n2. Go through the scholarship guidelines carefully<br>\r\n3. Hit \"Click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n4. Fill out the form and submit', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-10', '2022-10-30', 'The Center of Policy Research and Governance, India', 100000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-11 11:23:07', 1, NULL, '2022-10-22 10:05:25', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1360, 'pZGCRhM8TO8OtFdW8d', 'Competitions and Awards', 'SVASTIK Photography Contest', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/indian-architectural-heritage-through-your-lens-svastik-photography-contest/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'India has a rich legacy of practices and traditional knowledge touching different spheres of life across diverse disciplines. <br><br>\r\n<li>Architecture is one of the principal areas of Indian traditional knowledge. Due to the country\'s diverse socio-cultural, traditional, and religious history and climatic conditions, various architectural styles have evolved in different regions. <br><br>\r\n<li> Most surviving art and architecture from Ancient and Medieval India are religious, while others are signatures of regional kingdoms. In addition, ancient architecture is an exquisite blend of art and science. <br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Architecture aims to design a useful facility that can resist any foreseeable conditions over time. Therefore, comprehension of the science underlying traditional architecture may contribute to sustainable technology development. <br><br>\r\n<li>Even though some Indian traditional architectures, such as the Ramappa temple, are well-documented, many remain undocumented. <br><br>\r\n<li>Moreover, due to globalization and the uncritical adoption of western science, our Traditional Knowledge Systems have seen rapid deterioration<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Intending to conserve Indian traditional architecture, NIScPR-SVASTIK is collaborating with MyGov to host this \"Indian Architectural Heritage through Your Lens - SVASTIK Photography Contest.\"<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Guidelines:</b><br>\r\nâ¢ Describe the science that underlies traditional Indian architecture.<br>\r\nâ¢ Demonstrate how traditional Indian knowledge and architecture contribute to society through science and the arts.<br>\r\nâ¢ Explain the scientific rationale underlying Indian traditional architecture technologies.<br>\r\nâ¢ Provide scientific facts regarding architectural structures\' art, shape, and construction.<br>\r\nâ¢ Explore the history of the scientific discoveries that led to the building of architectural structures.<br><br>\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\nIn the first-ever photo contest of its kind, SVASTIK, CSIR-NIScPR offers the winners exciting prizes and is set to be more inspiring than ever.', '<li>Entry must be submitted in JPG/JPEG/ PNG format.<br>\r\n<li>The photographs should be shot in HD Standard having pixel appropriate size within the\r\nlimit of 2 Mb.<br>\r\n<li> The file should look clean when viewed on-screen at 100%. Entries should not be submitted\r\nin compressed or self-extracting formats.<br>\r\n<li> While submitting, participants must provide a title and a detailed description of their\r\nphotograph in English or Hindi in up to 500 words.', '1) Click on the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the details of the competition carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on the \"log in to apply\" button<br>\r\n4) Submit your entry<br>', 'exciting prizes ', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-10', '2022-11-30', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-12 10:37:22', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-12 05:13:07', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
