(772, 'y1uqGyiF9ePuhW', '', 'Post Matric Scholarship for SC Students, Delhi', 'https://edistrict.delhigovt.nic.in/in/en/Account/Register.html', '', '', '', '', '', 'Department for the Welfare of SC/ST/OBC, Government of NCT of Delhi invites applications for Post-Matric Scholarship for SC Students, Delhi 2020 from scheduled caste students. This scholarship aims to provide financial assistance to eligible students so that they can pursue their further studies at post matriculation/ post-secondary (college/University) levels within India. Selected students will receive a scholarship of up to INR 1,200 per month for 10 months.', '', '', 'Day scholar studens of Degree and post-graduate level courses and research studies will get ? INR 550 per month and Hostellers will get ? INR 1,200 per month. Day scholar studens Professional courses leading to degree/diploma/certificate will get ? INR 530 per month and Hostellers will get ? INR 820 per month. All other courses leading to a graduate degree Day scholar students will get ? INR 300 per month and Hostellers will get ? INR 570 per month. All post-matriculation level non-degree courses, Day scholar students will get ? INR 230 per month and Hostellers will get ? INR 380 per month.', NULL, NULL, '', 0, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '0', 0.00, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '', 0.00, 'centralizedspace@gmail.com', NULL, 1, NULL, '2021-03-03 06:21:19', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
