(1068, 'zGqAdnTOC9Vjaj47Oi', 'Educational Based', ' Eklavya Scholarship', 'https://mahadbtmahait.gov.in/RegistrationLogin/RegistrationLogin', '', '', '', '', '', 'To provide financial aid among the students of Arts, Commerce, Law and Science studentâs for their further postgraduate studies the Directorate of Higher Education, Maharashtra has launched a new scheme known as Eklavya Scholarship Maharashtra.<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\n- Eligibility criteria : <br/>\r\n<li>The main eligibility criterium is that the applicant should be a resident of Maharashtra state.<br/>\r\n<li>Law, Commerce, and Arts students should have completed graduation degree with at least 60% marks.<br/>\r\n<li>Science students should have completed graduation level with at least 70% marks.<br/>\r\n<li>The candidates should not be working in any part-time or full-time job.<br/>\r\n<li>The applicants should be studying in Maharashtra to be eligible for the scholarship (Students pursuing studies outside Maharashtra are not eligible).<br/>\r\n<br/> <hr>\r\nDocuments required :<br/> \r\n<li>Annual Income certificate of the family issued by Tahsildar<br/>\r\n<li>Mark sheet of the previous year<br/>\r\n<li>Domicile certificate', '', '1. Login your Account <br/>\r\n2. He/ she should click on the âNew Applicant Registrationâ. <br/>\r\n3. The candidate should fill in all the required details, verify the email ID and phone number and click on âRegisterâ.<br/>\r\n4. The next step is to complete the Aadhar authentication process through OTP or Biometric.\r\nOn opting for OTP authentication, the candidates will receive an OTP to their registered mobile number.<br/>\r\n5. The applicant should complete the registration process by entering all the required details. <br/>\r\n6. The candidate should now log in to the portal by entering the username and password. <br/>\r\n7. Finally, the applicant should complete the scholarship application, upload all the supporting documents, and click on âSubmitâ.', '', '[\