(1069, 'OhpIIHP01FoNyMCz0S', 'Educational Based', 'Sitaram Jindal Foundation Scholarship For Undergraduates 2022', 'https://www.sitaramjindalfoundation.org/assets/images/file/application_annexure_form.pdf', '', '', '', '', '', 'The Jindal scholarship is a merit-cum-means scholarship provided by the Sitaram Jindal Foundation. The program offers financial aid to underprivileged students aspiring to study higher. <br/>\r\n\r\n1) <b>What are the major eligibility criteria associated with Sitaram Jindal Foundation Scholarship?</b><br/>\r\n\r\nAll candidates applying for the scholarship should not exceed the age limit of 30. <br/>\r\n\r\n2)<b>Who can apply for this scholarship?</b><br/>  \r\n\r\nCandidates pursuing an undergraduate (B.A., B.Com, B.Sc., BFA, BCA, BBA, BBM, Bachelor of Business Economics/Finance, B.Sc. (Ag.), BVSC Integrated course of 5 years (first 3 years will be treated as graduation course)) are eligible for the Sitaram Jindal foundation scholarship <br/>   \r\n\r\n3)<b>What is percentage criteria?</b><br/>\r\nMale applicants should have scored at least 55%, and female applicants should have scored 50%, for Karnataka (male : 65% and female : 60%) , for West Bengal ( male : 60% and female : 55%) in the last qualifying examination. <br/>\r\n\r\n4)<b>Any concision for physically challenged students?</b><br/> \r\nYes, for all the physically challenged students, the eligibility percentage of marks is the minimum pass marks. <br/>\r\n<li>The selected candidate will receive the scholarship amount per month, for girls Rs.1400 and for boys Rs.1100<br/> \r\n<li>Students belonging to different states have to submit the Sitaram Jindal foundation scholarship application form at different addresses. Given below are the details of the postal addresses: <br/>\r\n\r\n1) Students from Andhra Pradesh, Andaman & Nicobar Island, Dadra & Nagar Haveli, Daman & Diu, Gujarat, Goa, Karnataka, Kerala, Lakshadeep, Maharashtra, Puducherry, Tamil Nadu and Telangana should send the completed Jindal scholarship application form with all the supporting documents to: \r\n<br/>The Trustee, Sitaram Jindal Foundation, <br/>Jindal Nagar, Tumkur Road, <br/>Bengaluru 560073. <br/>\r\n\r\n2) Students from  Assam, Arunachal Pradesh, Bihar, Chhattisgarh, Chandigarh, Delhi, Haryana, Himachal Pradesh, Jharkhand, Jammu & Kashmir, Madhya Pradesh, Manipur, Meghalaya, Mizoram, Nagaland, Odisha, Punjab, Rajasthan, Sikkim, Tripura, Uttar Pradesh, Uttarakhand and West Bengal should send the completed Sitaram Jindal foundation scholarship application form with all the supporting documents to:\r\n<br/>The Trustee, Sitaram Jindal Foundation 11, <br/>Green Avenue, Behind Sector D-3Vasant Kunj, <br/>New Delhi 110070.\r\n<br/> <hr>\r\n<li><b>Documents Required : </b><br/>\r\n1) Marksheets <br/>\r\n2) Fee receipt <br/>\r\n3) Income certificate <br/>\r\n4) Passport size photo <br/>\r\n5) SSLC/ HSC marks card <br/>\r\n6) Disabled certificate (if applicable) <br/>\r\n7) Admission certificate (government merit quota) <br/>\r\n8) Hostelers need to give a certificate (from warden/ accommodation owners) <br/>\r\n9) Declaration about not getting scholarship from any other source <br/>\r\n10) PPO, ex-servicemen widow I-card, and relationship dependency card for widows and veterans <br/>\r\n', '', 'Steps to be followed: <br/>\r\n1. Login your Account https://www.theglobalscholarship.org/student-login <br/>\r\n2. Go to Notified Scholarships tab <br/>\r\n3. For Detailed apply process visit: https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg <br/>', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelor Of Arts - B.A\",\"Bachelor Of Business Administration - B.B.A\",\"Bachelor Of Business Management - B.B.M\",\"Bachelor Of Commerce - B.Com\",\"Bachelor Of Computer Applications - B.C.A\",\"Bachelor Of Science - B.Sc\",\"Bachelor Of Arts - B.A\",\"Bachelor Of Business Administration - B.B.A\",\"Bachelor Of Business Management - B.B.M\",\"Bachelor Of Commerce - B.Com\",\"Bachelor Of Computer Applications - B.C.A\",\"Bachelor Of Fine Arts - BFA or BVA\",\"Bachelor Of Science - B.Sc\"]', '', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 50.00, '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', NULL, '[\"All\"]', 'Both', '[\"All\"]', 0, 30, '[\"\"]', 400000.00, NULL, 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-03-26', '2022-12-31', 'Sitaram Jindal Foundation', 16800.00, 'kavitamath@triwits.com', '2022-03-30 18:35:51', 1, 'radrsh@triwits.com', '2022-06-30 12:45:05', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
