(1074, '8wYnGTnrF64Fvy48jp', 'Scholarship', 'Vidyadhan Scholarship 2022', 'https://www.vidyadhan.org/register/student', '', '', '', '', '', 'The initial duration of the scholarship will be 2 years (classes 11 and 12). However, suppose the candidate continues to pursue their studies with excellent results. In that case, there is a fair chance for the extension of the scholarship in order to help the student further in pursuing their degree course. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>To avail of 2022, candidates who have completed the 10th class/SSLC should submit an application form online. Before proceeding with the application form, it is important to know if the candidate is eligible for the Sarojini Damodaran Foundation  2022.<br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Last date to apply:</b><br/>\r\n<li>Andhra Pradesh-30th June<br/>\r\n<li>Tamil Nadu-30th June<br/>\r\n<li>Telangana-30th June<br/>\r\n<li>Gujarat-31st July<br/>\r\n<li>Maharashtra-31st July <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\nCandidate must have scored a minimum of 90% or equivalent in class 10/ SSC examination. However, disabled candidates have a privilege of a 75% cut-off mark.<br/>\r\n', 'Marksheet for Class 10 (If the original mark sheet isnât available yet, you can make use of the provisional certificate)<br/>\r\n<li>Parental income certificate of the candidate<br/>\r\n<li>A recent photograph of the candidate<br/>\r\n<li>Identity card or address proof<br/>\r\n<li>For Disabled candidates: Certificate of disability issued by a competent authority<br/>', '1) Once you are logged in, you need to update your profile by filling in all the necessary information.<br/>\r\n2) Select the \'scholarship\' option to enter the scholarship application<br/>\r\n3) Fill in all required information and upload the supporting documents<br/>\r\n4) Finally submit the application<br/>', '', '[\"Class 11-PUC 1\"]', '[\"Class 11 - PUC 1\"]', '', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"Andra Pradesh\",\"Gujarat\",\"Tamil Nadu\",\"Telangana\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 'Both', '[\"All\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 600000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-06-02', '2022-07-31', 'Sarojini Damodaran Foundation', 60000.00, 'kavitamath@triwits.com', '2022-03-31 12:41:18', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-07-18 11:28:32', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1075, 'dfQCFfxnTsm9X9o5W1', 'Talent Based', 'Design a Logo for Kurukshetra Magazine 2022', 'https://auth.mygov.in/user/login?destination=oauth2/authorize', '', '', '', '', '', 'Kurukshetra is a monthly magazine on rural development published by the Publications Division, Ministry of Information and Broadcasting. It is being published since 1952, and is carrying the message of rural development to the masses through credible and analytical articles to enlighten readers about different subjects related to rural development. Kurukshetra has proved to be crucial for competitive exam aspirants as well as for knowledge enthusiasts.<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Technical Parameters<br/>\r\n- The participant should upload the logo as a file in JPG or PNG format.<br/>\r\n- The logo should be designed on a digital platform. The winner of the competition<br/>\r\nshall be required to submit the design in an editable and open file format.<br/>\r\n- Do not imprint or watermark your logo design.<br/>\r\n- The logo should be designed in colour.<br/>\r\n- Please bear in mind that for the actual utilization of the winning logo, the size may\r\nvary from 2 cm X 2 cm to 10 cm X 10 cm. While designing, this aspect should be kept in mind.<br/>\r\n- The logo image should be in high resolution with minimum 300 DPI. Logo should look clean (not pixelated or bit-mapped) when viewed on screen at 100%.<br/>\r\n- Each entry should submit with a detailed logic and explanation of rational and creative thought (not more than 100 words) on the designed logo.<br/>\r\n- Please note that the logo design must be original and should not violate any provision of the Indian Copyright Act, 1957.<br/>\r\n<br/><hr>\r\n<li>Evaluation Criteria <br/>\r\n- The Competition is open to all Indian citizens.<br/>\r\n- The participant should make sure that his/ her MyGov profile is accurate and updated for further communication. This includes details such as name, country declaration, complete postal address, email ID and phone number, etc. Entries with incomplete profiles would not be considered.<br/>\r\n- Entries will be judged on creativity, originality, composition, visual impact and how well they convey the essence of Kurukshetra.<br/>\r\n- The logo designed by the winner will be the intellectual property of the Directorate of Publications Division, Ministry of Information & Broadcasting, Government of India.<br/>\r\n- The participant must be the same person who has designed the logo and plagiarism would not be allowed. Anyone found infringing on othersâ copyright would be disqualified from the competition. Directorate of Publications Division, Ministry of Information & Broadcasting, Government of India does not bear any responsibility for copyright violations or infringements of intellectual property carried out by the participants. <br/>\r\n- There would be no constraint on Directorate of Publications Division, Ministry of Information & Broadcasting, Government of India to adopt the logo that is judged to be best. Also, all rights to modify logos would be with the Directorate.<br/>\r\n- All the entries received by the Division will be placed in front of a Selection Committee for final selection.<br/>\r\n- The disqualified entries shall not be used by the Department for any purpose and the\r\nDepartment shall have no intellectual rights over the same.<br/>\r\n- Payment to the winner will be made through electronic mode for which the necessary\r\nbank details will be taken after the declaration of the result.', '', 'Steps to be followed: <br/>\r\n1. Login your Account https://www.theglobalscholarship.org/student-login <br/>\r\n2. Go to Notified Scholarships tab <br/>\r\n3. For Detailed apply process visit: https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg <br/>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"\"]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, '[\"All\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-03-28', '2022-04-08', 'Ministry of Information and Broadcasting', 25000.00, 'kavitamath@triwits.com', '2022-03-31 17:15:44', 1, 'kavitamath@triwits.com', '2022-03-31 12:25:02', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1076, 'GVCaxvMSzmHujEm4jQ', 'Talent Based', 'Design a Logo for Virtual Courts 2022', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/design-logo-virtual-courts/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Department of Justice invites the citizens across the country to design a logo for Virtual Courts dealing with traffic violations that will depict the concept of Virtual Courts as well as its objectives.<br/>\r\n<li>Technical Parameters<br/>\r\n<li>A high resolution(600dpi) image of the logo in JPEG, PNG, BMP and TIFF format may be submitted.<br/>\r\n- The logo should be distinctive and scalable, usable in large hoardings, posters, creatives, and any kind of print material and appropriate for any kind of web device.<br/>\r\n- The winner shall be required to provide the original open-source file of the designed logo.<br/>\r\n- The logo should be multi-colour but convertible to mono chrome as well.<br/>\r\n- The logo must not pixelate when viewed on screen at 100%.<br/>\r\n- Entries must not be submitted in compressed or self-extracting formats.<br/>\r\n- The logo design must not be imprinted or watermarked.<br/>\r\n<br/><hr>\r\n<li>Terms and Conditions <br/>\r\n-The Contest is open to all citizens across India.<br/>\r\n- The submission of entry is free.<br/>\r\n- All entries are to be submitted through www.mygov.in. Any other medium/ mode of submission will not be considered for the evaluation.<br/>\r\n- The winning design/logo will be the intellectual property of the Ministry.<br/>\r\n- After the acceptance of the prize, the winner cannot exercise any right over his/her submission. The\r\nGovernment of India reserves the right to use the prize-winning logo for promotional, advertising\r\nand display purposes and to assign it to any person or group of people. The logo can be adapted as\r\nper the requirement.<br/>\r\n- The logo should not have been previously published in any print and digital media and must not\r\ncontain any provocative, objectionable, or inappropriate content.<br/>\r\n- The logo should be in English/Hindi or in both.<br/>\r\n- A participant can submit only one entry. Multiple submissions by the same participant will not be\r\naccepted.<br/>\r\n- The logo design must be original and should not violate any provision of the Indian Copyright Act,\r\n1957. Plagiarism/Copying of any nature would not be allowed.<br/>\r\n- Anyone found infringing on othersâ copyright would be disqualified from the competition. The\r\nGovernment of India does not bear any responsibility for copyright violations of infringements of\r\nintellectual property carried out by the participants.<br/>\r\n- The winners will be notified through the email address that he/she provides along with his/her\r\nsubmission. The MyGov portal shall also display the name of the winner through the announcements\r\nblogs section.<br/>\r\n- There will be no notification to the participation of the rejected entries.<br/>\r\n- The winnings may be subject to Tax deduction and reporting. It shall be the sole responsibility of the\r\ncontestant receiving the prize. Participants shall agree to supply any necessary information to affect\r\nthe same and to fully cooperate in fulfilling all applicable legal requirements.<br/>\r\n- The responsibility to comply with the guidelines and other conditions lies entirely with the\r\nparticipant(s) and the Government of India shall not be answerable to any dispute raised by a third\r\nparty.<br/>\r\n- There would be no constraint on the Government to adopt the logo that is judged to be the best.\r\nAlso, all rights to modify logos would be with the Government. \r\n\r\n', '', 'Steps to be followed: <br/>\r\n1. Login your Account https://www.theglobalscholarship.org/student-login <br/>\r\n2. Go to Notified Scholarships tab <br/>\r\n3. For Detailed apply process visit: https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg <br/>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, '[\"All\"]', 0, 0,