ents, \r\n       loan confirmation letter, scholarship nomination (if \r\n       the student is not financially independent, sponsorâs \r\n       evidence is required).<br><br>\r\n<li>  Visa.<br><br>\r\n\r\n', 'Students must meet eligibility requirements and complete an application form. Please read all of the information in the application form, including the selection criteria and requirements for shortlisted applicants before completing this application. The information provided will be used to select recipients.<br><br>\r\nSteps to be followed.<br>\r\n1. Login your Account.<br>\r\n2. Go to Notified Scholarships tab.<br>\r\n3. For Detailed apply process visit:<br>', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\"]', '\" Bachelor of Business in Hospitality Management\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-30', '2022-12-31', 'Torrens University.', 1216763.00, 'radrsh@triwits.com', '2022-07-07 17:48:34', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-08-12 08:11:39', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1203, 'b8OP4BKjPw8Cp3nPuy', 'Scholarship', 'Wagh Bakri Scholarship ', 'https://www.vidyasaarathi.co.in/Vidyasaarathi/login', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Wagh Bakri as a brand always supported the \'Hamesha Rishtey Banaye\' culture. A cup of tea together, may erase differences between people and promote co-existence, harmony, and peace within society. Wagh Bakri Tea Group, which is well known for its premium tea & having business with a huge number of Wagh Bakri tea lovers around the world promoted, the Wagh Bakri Foundation for philanthropic and developmental activities. <br/><br/>\r\n<li>The \'Wagh Bakri Scholarship\' is the project of the foundation in collaboration with the Vidyasaarathi portal for providing financial assistance to young students from poor economic backgrounds for the continuation of their education. This scholarship would not apply to Wagh Bakri Tea Group employees and their children.<br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>This scholarship is applicable  for Students of </b><br/>\r\nMMBS ( Reward 75000 INR)<br/>\r\nBAMS/BDS/BHMS  (Reward50000 INR)<br/>\r\nBsc  Nursing (Reward 30000 INR)<br/>\r\nANM/GNM (Reward 20000 INR)<br/>\r\nB.Ed  (reward 25000 INR)<br/>\r\nDiploma (Reward 20000 INR)<br/>\r\nB.E/B.Tech  (Reward 40000 INR)<br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>NOTE</b><br/>\r\n\r\nThis scholarship is only applicable to \"GUJARAT\" State students <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>1) What mandatory documents are required?</b><br/>\r\nRefer Certificate Instruction<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>2) Whether compulsory to have a bank account?</b><br/>\r\nYes<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>3) Is Any Preference available to a particular caste?</b><br/>\r\nNo, It is open to all.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>4)What is the minimum percentage required to apply?</b><br/>\r\nStudent Must have secured at least 50% in Class 12th & Previous Academics.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>5) Any Gender Preferences?</b><br/>\r\nNo, Open to All Gender.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>6) Is there any lo