nformation which you have entered  <br/>', '', '[\"\"]', '[\"B.E (All)\"]', '', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-29', '2022-07-27', 'KSCSTE Technological ', 20000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-20 16:18:06', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-07-27 11:59:53', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1223, 'GE2MKrj8qLRycSt3hg', 'Competitions and Awards', 'KSCSTE Science Literature Awards', 'https://kscste.kerala.gov.in/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Science Literature Awards (SLA) are meant to recognize the contributions made by science writers in promoting Science through Science Literature in Malayalam. The awards are under the following five categories<br/>\r\n1. Science Book (Childrenâs Literature)<br/>\r\n2. Science Book (Popular Science)<br/>\r\n3. Science Book (In-depth Science)<br/>\r\n4. Science Journalism Award<br/>\r\n5. Science Book (Malayalam translation)<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Benefit<br/></b>\r\n<li>Each award carries a cash prize of Rs. 50,000/- and a certificate.<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Contact<br/></b>\r\nScientist â in- Charge (SLA)\r\nKerala State Council for Science, Technology <br/>\r\nEnvironment (KSCSTE) <br/>\r\nSasthra Bhavan, Pattom, Thiruvananthapuram â 4. <br/>\r\nTel: 0471-2548250, <br/>\r\nEmail: esanil.kscste@kerala.gov.in,<br/> sasthrabodhini2011@gmail.com <br/>', '<li>Applications are invited through advertisements every year. The application should be submitted in the prescribed format along with 3 copies of the books.<br/>\r\n', '1) log in to your Dashboard<br/>\r\n2) Fill the google form with the relevant information<br/>\r\n3) Attach the required documents correctly<br/>\r\n', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-09', '2022-08-20', 'KSCSTE ', 50000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-26 17:03:53', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-12 09:28:23', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1224, 'B8OQK1ymXnBs9KDd6i', 'Competitions and Awards', 'International Youth Math Challenge 2022', 'https://www.iymc.info/en/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Qualification Round 2022 of the International Youth Math Challenge has opened for submissions. Use your math skills and creativity to qualify for the global final round to win great prizes and certificates!<br/><br>\r\n\r\n<li>IYMC is one of the biggest online math competitions for students from all around the world. You can win awards and cash prizes worth over 700 USD, qualify for the final round, become an official IYMC ambassador in your country, or join an international network for outstanding students â take this unique opportunity and participate today: <b><a href=\"www.iymc.info\" target=\"_blank\">www.iymc.info</a></b><br/>\r\n <hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Benefits / Prizes<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>Successful participants will receive certificates, cash prizes, and honours<br/>\r\n<li>All participants will receive  Participation Certificate<br/><br>\r\n<li><b>Youth Category:</b><br>\r\n1st Prize: 150 USD Cash Prize, Certificate<br/>\r\n2nd Prize: 100 USD Cash Prize, Certificate<br/>\r\n3rd Prize: 50 USD Cash Prize, Certificate<br/><br>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Junior Category:</b><br>\r\n1st Prize: 150 USD Cash Prize, Certificate<br/>\r\n2nd Prize: 100 USD Cash Prize, Certificate<br/>\r\n3rd Prize: 50 USD Cash Prize, Certificate<br/>\r\n<li>National Awards (best participant from each country)<br/><br>\r\n<b>Other awards:</b>\r\n\r\n<li><b>IYMC School Award for Most Participants:</b> For the school with the most overall participants in the qualification round to honour the efforts of the teachers in encouraging students to participate in mathematical competitions.<br/>\r\n\r\n<li> <b>IYMC School Award for Most Finalists:</b> For the school with the most students participating in the pre-final and final round<br/>\r\n\r\n<li> <b>IYMC School Award for Excellence:</b> The school with many outstanding students who have achieved high results throughout the overall competition to honour quality education<br/>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Besides that, the IYMC offers the following benefit</b><br/>\r\n<b>Join a Global Network:</b> A successful participation allows you to join the IYMC network: You will get the rare chance to connect and exchange with outstanding, similar-minded, and inspiring students worldwide.<br/>\r\n <hr>\r\n<b>Rounds / Process<br/></b>\r\n\r\n1)Qualification Round: The qualification round consists of five math problems. To qualify for the pre-final round, you must solve at least three (under 18) to four (over 18) problems correctly. You can submit your solutions online by 16. October 2022. All participants receive certificates.<br/><br>\r\n\r\n2)Pre-Final Round: Successful participants can register for the pre-final round in November. You have one week to solve eight problems of three types: 3x basic problems, 3x, advanced problems, and 2x special-creativity problems<br/><br>\r\n\r\n3)Final Round: Successful finalists can participate in the final round: You will take a 20-minute online exam supervised by a supervisor. The winners receive certificates and cash prizes worth over 700 USD<br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b> Eligibility<br/></b>\r\n<li>All High School and University Students.<br/><hr>\r\n', '<li>ID proof ', '1. Click the below\"click to apply button\" <br/>\r\n2. Click on participate now<br>\r\n3. Download the questions by clicking on \"Qualification round\"<br>\r\n4. Fill out the submission form and attach the answer script<br>\r\n5. Submit\r\n\r\n', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-10', '2022-10-16', 'International Youth Math', 55866.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-26 18:03:04', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-13 12:14:29', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, 