logged in, you need to update your profile by filling in all the necessary information.<br/>\r\n2) Select the \'scholarship\' option to enter the scholarship application<br/>\r\n3) Fill in all required information and upload the supporting documents<br/>\r\n4) Finally submit the application<br/>', '', '[\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', 'null', '', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-02', '2022-08-05', 'Senior Research Fellow (SRF) OR Research Associate (RA)', 47000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-27 16:01:35', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-08-05 06:53:47', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1226, 'areP6t0G1vyjPCjCbO', 'Abroad', 'KILLAM DOCTORAL SCHOLARSHIPS', 'https://www.grad.ubc.ca/awards/affiliated-fellowships-doctoral-program', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Killam Scholarship and Prize Programmes were established in memory of Izaak Walton Killam through the Will of his wife, Dorothy J. Killam, and through gifts made during her lifetime. Their primary purpose is to support advanced education and research at five.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Canadian universities and the Canada Council for the Arts. The UBC Killam Doctoral Scholarships are provided annually by the Izaak Walton Killam Memorial Fund for Advanced Studies. It was Mrs. Killamâs desire that those selected to receive scholarships: âBe likely to contribute to the advancement of learning or to win distinction in a profession. A Killam scholar should not be a one-sided personâ¦ Special distinction of intellect should be founded upon sound character.â<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Killam Doctoral Scholarships are the most prestigious awards available to graduate students at UBC. Approximately 15-20 awards are made each year to the top doctoral candidates in the Affiliated Fellowships competition. At present, the<b> Killam Doctoral Scholarship</b> provides an annual stipend valued at $30,000 for two years plus a $2,000 allowance for research-related travel during the 24 months of the scholarship*.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Killam Doctoral Scholarships awardees on the UBC-Vancouver campus also become Four Year Fellowship holders and receive additional tuition funding from the 4YF program if they are eligible.<br/>\r\n\r\n  \r\n<hr>\r\n<b>ELIGIBILITY<br/></b>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>To be eligible to apply for Killam Doctoral Scholarship funding, applicants must have completed no more than 24 months of doctoral study as of the start date of the scholarship. Therefore, applicants to the 2022-2023 competition must have completed no more than 24 months of doctoral study .<br/>', '<li>No separate application or documents will be required.\r\n\r\n<li>The bursary will be automatically applied using the information provided at the point of registration for the postgraduate study.\r\n\r\n<li>Students will be auto-considered for this scholarship when they apply for the courses on which this scholarship is applicable. No separate application is needed.\r\n', '1) Register Online.<br/>\r\n\r\n2) Choose your program and fill out your application form.<br/>\r\n\r\n3) Make your academic profile and submit your documents and certificates.<br/>\r\n', 'ghyte', '[\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\",\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"Masters\\r\\nPHD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-07', '2022-09-01', ' British Columbia', 2398141.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-27 17:58:25', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-21 09:55:44', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1227, 'U1YniZUGzyHmY0KXI0', 'Internship', 'Inlaks-Kings India Institute Studentship 2022', 'https://www.inlaksfoundation.org/irtg/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'This opportunity was launched in 2016 and is similar to the Inlaks Research and Travel Grant. It will enable scholars currently enrolled in Ph.D. programs at Indian universities to undertake a short-term visit to the Kingâs India Institute, Kingâs College London to collect material, use facilities, and consult experts for their research for their PhDs. The successful candidates can also access other libraries and academic institutions in the UK.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The Inlaks-Kingâs India Institute Studentship will offer financial support to a maximum of two candidates for a period of up to three months. The studentship will cover:<br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n1) Reasonable travel allowance reimbursable on actuals (up to USD 1000)<br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n2) Maintenance expenses (up to USD 2000 per month)<br/>\r\n\r\n3) Funds for buying materials and making copies of relevant literature, reimbursable on actuals (up to USD 500)<br/>\r\n\r\n4) Health allowance/Covid allowance, reimbursable on actuals (up to maximum USD 500)<br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>ELIGIBILITY</b>(All applicants must fulfill the following criteria)</br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li> Applicants must hold confirmed Ph.D. registration for at least two years but for not more than three years<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Applicants must have a first-class degree at Bachelorâs (Honours) and Masterâs level<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Applicants those born on or after 1st January 1987 are eligible to apply for the grant<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> Applicants must be an Indian passport holder, currently resident in India<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n <li>The award will be given only in Humanities and Social Sciences related subjects<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>IMPORTANT CONDITIONS<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>The visit should commence between January and April 2023<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Any material collected by the selected candidates (photocopies, literature, etc.) must become the property of the candidateâs institution for wider use by future scholars<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> All the above material must carry a statement regarding the support received from the âInlaks-Kingâs India Institute Studentship<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> The candidates must submit a written report in a prescribed format to the Inlaks Foundation within a month of their return<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>A candidate can apply for either the âInlaks Research and Travel Grantâ or the âInlaks-Kingâs India Institute Studentship in any given year<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>SELECTION PROCEDURE<br/></b>\r\n\r\nThe candidates will be expected to go through a two-tier selection procedure<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n <li>First round: Short-listing on the basis of the written application submitted<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Final round: Personal interview of the short-listed candidates, either in-person or virtually<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Short-listed candidates for the interview will be informed in September 2022<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Final interviews will be held in September or October 2022<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n', '<li>Updated CV/ resume limited to two pages only in PDF format <br/>\r\n<li>A written and signed statement from the applicantâs current supervisor stating the candidateâs ability, focus, and progress in the work done under her/his supervision<br/>\r\n<li> The candidate needs to go abroad, and the funds for the visit cannot be obtained from any other source<br/>', '1. Log in to your dashboard<br/>\r\n2. Click on the apply button, and fill in all the details <br/>\r\n3. Attach your cv if required and click on submit', 'jytgj', '[\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\",\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"Masters, PHD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-15', '2022-09-01', ' âInlaks-Kingâs India Institute Studentship', 15940320.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-28 16:05:03', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-21 09:49:32', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1228, 'mpRNspbfqUJK0y5e5e', 'Scholarship', ' Santoor Scholarship ', 'https://santoorscholarships.com/index.php', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'A future full of opportunities is now within your reach. Choose your desired career path after Class 12 and Wipro will help you achieve your academic goals. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>This year we launch, the sixth edition of âThe Santoor Scholarship Programmeâ for young women. Wipro Cares and Wipro Consumer Care & Lighting Group together have been supporting the education of close to 3000 young women over the last five years through the Santoor Scholarship Programme.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Initiated in 2016-17, the program offers support to 900 students every year, across the states of Andhra Pradesh, Karnataka, and Telangana. Under this program, young women can avail of INR 24,000 per annum until the completion of their degree program.<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>Available only for young<b> women</b> from underprivileged backgrounds in the states of<b> Andhra Pradesh, Karnataka, or Telangana</b><br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Have passed Class 10 from a local government school<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Have passed Class 12 from a government school/junior college in the academic year <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Have enrolled in a full-time graduate program beginning 2020-21<br/><hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Note:</b> The duration of the full-time graduatation course must be a minimum of 3 years<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Terms and Conditions<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>The applicant is required to read the following terms and conditions. The candidate on applying is deemed to have accepted the terms and conditions herein.<br/> <br/>\r\n\r\n<li>This application is meant for applying for a grant under the âSANTOOR SCHOLARSHIPâ program for the year 2021-22, for girl students who wish to pursue higher education after grade 12, in any discipline of a minimum of three years duration. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Any application which does not meet the pre-requisites is liable to be rejected.\r\nWipro Cares reserves the sole right to offer the scholarship and also has the right to modify/reject/withdraw and/or discontinue the offer without assigning any reason. No other body/agency is authorized to make any offer on the Santoor Scholarship. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>The application doesnât guarantee the scholarship.  <br/><br/>\r\n', '<li>One recent passport size photograph<br/>\r\n<li>Photocopy of applicant\'s passbook (other than Gramin Bank)<br/>\r\n<li>Photocopy of Aadhaar Card<br/>\r\n<li>Photocopy of class 10 certificate<br/>\r\n<li>Photocopy of class 12 certificate<br/>', '1. Log into your dashboard <br/>\r\n2. Click the âApply Nowâ <br/>\r\n3. You will now be redirected to the âSantoor Scholarship Programmeâ application form page.<br/>\r\n3. Click on the âStart Application button to begin the application process.<br/>\r\n4. Fill in the required details in the online application form.<br/>\r\n5. Upload relevant documents.<br/>\r\n6. Accept the âTerms and Conditionsâ and click on âPreviewâ. <br/>\r\n7. If all the details filled in by the applicant are correctly showing on the preview screen, click on the âSubmitâ button to complete the application process.<br/>\r\n', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\"]', '\"Undergraduate(Bachelors)\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-09', '2022-09-15', 'Wipro Consumer Care ', 24000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-28 18:18:24', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-08-10 04:28:17', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1229, 'fdj1wA1IhyghCO9P5L', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Kerala Sasthrapuraskaram Award', 'https://kscste.kerala.gov.in/kerala-sasthrapuraskaram/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Kerala Sasthrapuraskaram is an award instituted by the Government of Kerala for honoring outstanding Scientists of Kerala origin working anywhere in the world. The Government of Kerala, through KSCSTE, administers the award procedure. Lifetime research contributions and achievements in science will be considered for the award.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Scientists can be nominated by Fellows of National Academies of Sciences, Vice Chancellors/Directors of scientific institutes and establishments, and by Eminent Scientists of national/international repute. A Selection Committee consisting of eminent Scientists representing leading Science and Technology Institutions and Academies in India will select the Awardee.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The Kerala Sasthrapuraskaram is to be given to a Scientist / Technologist working anywhere in the world, but of Kerala by birth who has made a significant contribution in any branch of Science and Technology.\r\nThe Candidate must be an outstanding scientist, a good leader & organizer in S&T, a great institution builder in S&T, a national leader and role model in S&T, and/ or a visionary in S&T.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>There is no age limit for consideration for the Awad<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Procedure for Application<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>Nominations are invited for Kerala Sasthra Puraskaram 2022<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Nomination Proforma is available in downloads<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Self Nominations or applications will not be entertained<br/><br/>\r\n', '<li>ID prof <br/>\r\n', '1. log in to your dashboard <br/>\r\n2. click on downloads <br/>\r\n3. Download Nomination Proforma<br/>\r\n4.  Fill out the form and post it to the below-mentioned Address<br/>\r\n<p style=\"color:blue;\">Dr. Binuja Thomas <br/>\r\nPrincipal Scientist<br/>\r\nKerala State Council for Science Technology and Environment<br/>\r\nSasthra Bhavan, Pattom, Thiruvananthapuram - 695004<br/>\r\nTel: +91 471 2548211<br/>\r\nE-mail: ksasthrapuraskaram2022@gmail.com</p>\r\n', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-09', '2022-08-20', 'Sasthrapuraskaram Award', 200000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-29 15:50:36', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-12 09:31:20', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1230, '37im84UrndppSZTVQg', 'Scholarship', 'MEDHAVI National Scholarship Scheme ', 'https://medhavionline.org/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'MEDHAVI National Scholarship Scheme invites applications for the âSAMADHAN scholarship examination â 2022â. Under this exam, scholarships will be awarded solely on a MERIT basis, to candidates who qualify for the prescribed exam. <br/> <br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b> Aim <br/></b>\r\n \r\n<li>SAMADHAN aims to pay money to candidates studying or preparing for government jobs to pay their application/registration fee for various jobs, admission, etc. SAMADHAN provides small scholarship money <b>(Rs.300, Rs.500 & Rs.1000) </b>to SCHOLARS from all sections of society directly into their bank account after qualifying for a prescribed exam. <br/> <br/>\r\n\r\n<li>This small money helps such scholars to fill various paid application forms for jobs, entrance exams, scholarships, etc. including various Medhavi scholarship examinations such as SWABHIMAN, SAKSHAM, SWAWLAMBAN & newGEN. <br/> <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n', ' <li>Marksheets <br/>\r\n<li>Fee receipt <br/>\r\n<li>Income certificate <br/>\r\n<li>Passport size photo <br/>\r\n', '1) Once you are logged in, you need to update your profile by filling in all the necessary information<br/>\r\n2) Select the \'scholarship\' option to enter the scholarship application<br/>\r\n3) Fill in all required information and upload the supporting documents<br/>\r\n4) Finally submit the application<br/>', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\"]', '\"Undergraduate(Bachelors)\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-08-07', '2022-08-17', 'MEDHAVI National Scheme ', 1000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-07-29 16:49:32', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-08-09 06:32:49', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
