/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr>', '1) Once you are logged in, you need to update your profile by filling in all the necessary information<br/>\r\n2) Select the \'scholarship\' option to enter the scholarship application<br/>\r\n3) Fill in all required information and upload the supporting documents<br/>\r\n4) Finally submit the application<br/>', '', '[\"Diploma\",\"Bachelors\",\"Agri\",\"B.E\\/B.Tech\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\",\"B.Tech (All)\",\"B.E (All)\",\"Diploma in Technical (All)\",\"Diploma in Health (All)\",\"Bachelor of Agriculture (BScAgri)\"]', '\"Diploma, B.E & B.Tech, Undergraduate(Bachelors), B.Ed., B.Sc. Agriculture\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"All\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 500000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-02', '2022-08-31', 'Astral Foundation Renewal ', 40000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-08 16:02:23', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-08-10 04:23:18', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1239, '6EjEKJeuEYu4iHKPwW', 'Competitions and Awards', 'IET India Scholarship Award 2022 ', 'IET India Scholarship Award 2022 Offered By Institution of Engineering and Technology', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Our India scholarship award is designed for undergraduate engineering students and rewards their creativity, innovation, leadership and excellence. IET India Scholarship Awards is now in its 6th edition and is a prestige award that recognises and nurtures future engineering leaders of India.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThis year, the awards are open to 1st, 2nd, 3rd and 4th-year undergraduate engineering students. Students from all AICTE-approved undergraduate engineering programmes can apply to win our scholarships this year. More than 36,000 engineering students have applied to the IET India Scholarship Award over the last 5 editions and we hope to see a wonderful response from the young engineering talent across India this year as well.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility for IET India Scholarship Award 2022<br/><br/></b>\r\n \r\n\r\nThe IET India Scholarship Awards will be open to students of 1st,2nd,3rd and 4th-year B.Tech programmes. The scholarship is also open for lateral entry students who join the B.Tech programme in the 2nd year.<br/>\r\n\r\n <hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility Guidelines:<br/></b>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Any first, second, third year and fourth year full-time regular UG Engineering student from an AICTE/UGC approved institution. (open to all engineering students from all engineering fields)<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>All regular credit courses must have been cleared in a single attempt by the applicant<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>UG marks should be at least 60% in aggregate for the semesters cleared so far or corresponding to a CGPA of at least 6.5 on a 10-point scale<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>There is no age limit for the applicant<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Application is open for all IET members and non-members and for all branches of engineering as recognised by the AICTE/UGC<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Students from AICTE/UGC-approved Institutions and national institutes are eligible to apply for scholarships<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n <hr>\r\n\r\n<b>About the IET<br/></b>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>The Institution of Engineering and Technology (The IET) is one of the worldâs largest professional societies for engineers, headquartered in the UK. Turning 150 this year, the IET works closely with industry, academia and government in its mission to engineer a better world. In line with this, the IET also has specific global initiatives around key sectors that are relevant to solving problems that impact society at large. In India, the IET has wide-ranging activities in alignment with the overall global IET strategy that also includes sector focus in areas such as Future technologies. Future of Mobility and Transport, as well as the Future of Work, Shri Ratan Tata, Former Chairman Tata Sons, N R Narayana Murthy, Chairman Emeritus, Infosys and T V Ramachandran, President, Broadband India Forum (Ex-Resident Director, Vodafone), are Honorary Fellows of the IET<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>With our members, we are driving innovation and change in the fields of engineering and technology. We research, investigate, review and analyse the industryâs challenges, proposing solutions that will have a significant impact on the world for years to come<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n ', '1) Proof of identity and Address <br/>\r\n2) Previous Academic Marksheets<br/>\r\n3) Income Certificate/ITR/Salary Certificate<br/>\r\n4) Student Bank Passbook<br/>\r\n5) Current Year Fee receipt/Fee Structure - Tuition and Non-Tuition<br/>\r\n6) Bonafide Certificate from Institute<br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>', '1) Once you are logged in, you need to update your profile by filling in all the necessary information<br/>\r\n2) Select the \'scholarship\' option to enter the scholarship application<br/>\r\n3) Fill in all required information and upload the supporting documents<br/>\r\n4) Finally submit the application<br/>', '', '[\"B.E\\/B.Tech\"]', '[\"B.Tech (All)\",\"B.E (All)\"]', '\"B.E\\/B.Tech\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-03', '2022-08-15', 'IET India Award 2022 ', 100000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-08 16:40:57', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-12 09:25:50', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1240, '4e04G4m7BezIVyznPQ', 'Scholarship', 'VKSSF Scholarship 2022', 'http://konkanischolarship.com/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'World Konkani Centre, Mangaluru, Invites applications for Merit-Cum-Means Scholarships-2022 from Konkani Speaking students belonging to any caste and religion, seeking professional education in the stream of Engineering. A separate notification will be issued for the MBBS course. Eligibility Criteria for the Engineering Scholarships will be as follows.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Only candidates with Konkani as their mother tongue can apply for this scholarship regardless of caste and religion. A Mother tongue certificate needs to be provided while applying.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Only Candidates who are seeking admission to the First Year of the Engineering course in 2022 can apply<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n <li>Only Candidates who scored above 80% in the core subjects in PUC and also secured a Ranking of 20,000 or below in the Common Entrance Test (CET). OR Candidates who have secured a meritorious rank in any other entrance exam<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Only Candidates whose total Family Income is less than Rs. 5.00 Lakhs per annum can apply. The references from Family Doctor and a Chartered Accountant should be provided in this regard while applying.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n <li>The Vishwa Konkani Student Scholarship Programme is a handholding programme with Scholarships along with skill development and mentoring programme. Students should be willing to be part of this highly beneficial development programme.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> The student should be willing to sponsor 2 students after completion of studies and after securing employment.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Most deserving candidates will be selected based on verifications by independent panellists. Each selected candidate who is seeking admission to the First Year of the Engineering course in 2022 will be awarded scholarships amounting to Rs. 50,000.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Candidates fulfilling the above criteria can apply Online for Scholarships 2022 through an online application module set up by the World Konkani Centre on the website: www.konkanischolarship.com. The application module will be opened soon. Applications received in hardcopy will not be processed for the Vishwa Konkani Student Scholarships 2022.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>âVishwa Konkani Student Scholarship Fundâ envisages grant of Merit-cum-Means Scholarships to students having Konkani language as their mother tongue. Instituted in the year 2010 as envisioned by the eminent thinker and corporate leader T.V. Mohandas Pai, the World Konkani Centre has successfully raised and awarded scholarships to the tune of over Rs. 30.00 crores since 2010.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>As the Fund is functioning based on the âStreamâ concept, the entire amount generated every year will be distributed to the beneficiaries and no separate corpus will be maintained. Contributions to the Fund will be eligible for Tax Exemption under section 80(G) of the Income Tax Act.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>âVishwa Konkani Student Scholarship Fund is administered by a Governing Council headed by Pradeep G. Pai as secretary and comprising eminent personalities. Eminent Konkani Philanthropists like Shri T.V.Mohandas Pai, Dr Ranjan Pai, Dr P. Dayanand Pai, Ramadas Kamath U., K. V. Kamath, G. Nandagopal Shenoy, M. Jagannath Shenoi, Madam Grace Pinto, Ullas Kamath, Gokulnath Prabhu, Sandeep Shenoy, Pradeep G. Pai, B. R. Bhat, Jagadish Kini, and many more have been supporting this fund every year.<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n ', '1) Proof of identity and Address<br/>\r\n2) Previous Academic Marksheets<br/>\r\n3) Income Certificate/ITR/Salary Certificate<br/>\r\n4) Student Bank Passbook<br/>\r\n5) Current Year Fee receipt/Fee Structure - Tuition and Non-Tuition<br/>\r\n6) Bonafide Certificate from Institute<br/>\r\n<hr>', '1) Once you are logged in, you need to update your profile by filling in all the necessary information<br/>\r\n2) Select the \'scholarship\' option to enter the scholarship application<br/>\r\n3) Fill in all required information and upload the supporting documents<br/>\r\n4) Finally submit the application<br/>', '', '[\"B.E\\/B.Tech\"]', '[\"Bachelor Of Engineering \\/ Bachelor Of Technology - B.E \\/ B.Tech\"]', '\"Engineering\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 500000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-02', '2022-08-15', 'Vishwa Konkani Student ', 50000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-08 18:08:16', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-08-09 06:31:27', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1241, 'NN3g9shZ8AK35Qhs0Y', 'Scholarship', 'Tata Capital Pankh Scholarship', 'https://www.admissionlogin.in/tata-capital-pankh-scholarship/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Tata Capital Pankh Scholarship Programme is an initiative of Tata Capital Limited to support the higher education of students belonging to economically weaker sections of society. Under this scholarship programme, the students in Classes<b> 6 to 12 or undergraduate (general and professional) degree</b>programmes will be provided financial support to fulfil their academic dreams. <br/> <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Tata Capital Limited is a renowned financial services company of Tata Group. As part of its CSR (Corporate Social Responsibility) initiative, the company has introduced this scholarship program to bring about a positive change in society by supporting the education of deserving and needy students. The company runs several CSR initiatives in Education, Skill Development, Environment, and Health. <br/> <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<li>An applicant must be enrolled in a professional undergraduate degree programme like Engineering, Medical, Law, etc. at a recognized institute in India.\r\nThey must have scored at least <b>60%</b> marks in the preceding class. <br/> <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The annual family income must be less than or equal to INR 4,00,000 from all sources. <br/> <br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>Photo identity proof (Aadhaar Card)\r\n <br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Passport size photograph <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Income proof (Form 16A/income certificate from government authority/salary slips, etc.) <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Proof of admission (school/college ID card/bonafide certificate, etc.) <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Current academic year fee receipt <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Bank account details of the scholarship applicant (canceled cheque/passbook copy) <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Marksheets or grade cards of the preceding class <br/>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Disability & Caste certificate (if applicable) <br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>', '1) Click on the âApply Now button below <br/>\r\n\r\n2) Login with your registered ID and land on the âApplication Form Pageâ <br/>\r\n\r\n3) You will now be redirected to âThe Tata Capital Pankh Scholarship Programmeâ application form page.\r\nClick on the âStart Application button to begin the application process <br/>\r\n\r\n4) Fill in the required details in the online application form <br/>\r\n\r\n5)Upload relevant documents <br/>\r\n\r\n6) Accept the âTerms and Conditions and click on âPreviewâ <br/>\r\n\r\n7) If all the details filled in the application are correctly showing on the preview screen, click on the âSubmitâ button to complete the application process <br/>\r\n', '', '[\"Primary\",\"Secondary\",\"Class 10\",\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\",\"Masters (All)\",\"Class 6\",\"Class 7\",\"Class 8\",\"Class 9\",\"Class 10 - SSLC - Matriculation\",\"Class 11 - PUC 1\",\"Class 12 - PUC 2\"]', '\"Class 6 to 12, Undergraduate ( Bachelors), Postgraduate (Masters)\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 400000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-05', '2022-08-30', 'Tata Capital Limited', 15000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-16 15:48:30', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-16 10:43:56', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1242, 'lKFa9QyZXpL4t6hYVa', 'Scholarship', 'JSPN Educational Scholarships 2022-23', 'https://srijspn.org/jspnapp/views/home.jsf', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'JSPN Scholarship 2022-23 is an initiative of Jaya Satya Pramoda Nidhi (JSPN) (a social services wing of Sri Uttaradi Math Exempted under 80G of Income Tax Act) that serves to uplift and support the Madhwa community students who have a good academic track record. Every year 250 to 300 students benefit from the scheme, complete their studies, and progress in life. The scholarship offers financial aid to students who are facing financial difficulties to pursue education. <br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility<br/></b>\r\n\r\nTo be eligible, an applicant must belong to the Madhwa community and have a good academic record<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Benefits</b>\r\n\r\nThe selected awardee will receive scholarships according to the availability of the funds and the merit/need based on the student<br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n', 'Marksheet<br/>\r\nCertificates<br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>', 'Step 1: Click on the \"Apply Now\" button<br/>\r\nStep 2: Click on the option \"Click Here to Apply\" or âStudent Loginâ, on the home page of the JSPN Scholarships Portal<br/>\r\nStep 3: Click on \'New Student\' to Register<br/>\r\nStep 4: After successful registration, the student will receive a âJSPN SIDâ<br/>\r\nStep 5: Now, activate the student login account through a link received via the email<br/>\r\nStep 6: After activation of the account, fill in the application form and submit it<br/>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-25', '2022-08-30', 'Sri Jaya Satya Pramoda Nidhi (JSPN)', 20000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-16 16:35:51', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-16 11:14:18', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1243, 'jVjnFPw9LUsLF4Qu5f', 'Scholarship', ' Nilam Patel Bahushrut Foundation Scholarships 2022', 'https://www.bahushrutfoundation.org/_files/ugd/e3c2a7_c215dad435314e4791dcc2fecfddcfd6.pdf', '', '', '', '', 'https://youtu.be/JYejuC3CVqw', 'Applications for scholarships are invited in the first week of July every year through a press release in all the leading newspapers and magazines of Maharashtra and Gujarat. Similarly, circulars are sent to all the deaf schools in Maharashtra and Gujarat.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n<li>By this time most of the results are announced for that year. The scholarships are given at SSC, HSC, Graduate, and Post Graduate levels. Over a period, several awards have been introduced for academic excellence. Two new âStudy Abroad Scholarshipsâ have been introduced in 2017, one each, for those hearing impaired students who are going abroad to pursue Bachelorâs or Masterâs level degree program in any reputed college or university in any country.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>All application forms are available on the foundationâs website. Students can download them and submit duly filled application forms along with necessary documents between 1st July to 31st August. These are accepted at the administrative office of the trust in Vadodara by post or courier.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Scholarships, Prizes, and Special Awards, strictly based on merit are distributed to the recipients in the first week of October every year.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility<br/><br/></b>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>To be eligible for this scholarship, the candidates must\r\nbe a hearing-impaired domicile of either <b>Gujarat or Maharashtra<br/><br/></b>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Be studying in college or institute in Maharashtra and Gujarat<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Have passed HSC/Graduation/Postgraduation examination in June 2022<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Benefits<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>The selected students from the HSC, Graduate, and Postgraduate levels will receive a scholarship, various prizes, and awards based on merit.\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n', '<li>HSC/Graduate/Postgraduate level certificate and mark sheet<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>The latest audiogram was taken at a government hospital or institute<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Certificate of deafness<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Latest passport-size photograph to be pasted in the given space<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Evidence of admission in college or institute (for HSC students only)<br/>\r\n<hr>', 'Step 1: Click on the \'Apply Now button below<br/>\r\n\r\nStep 2: Navigate to \'Application Form- HSC and above level\' and download it<br/>\r\n\r\nStep 3: Fill in the details required in the application form and attach the required documents<br/>\r\n\r\nStep 4: Send the application to the Administrative Office of the trust by post to the below address- <br/>\r\n\r\n\r\nNilam Patel Bahushrut Foundation<br/>\r\n303, Aries Palms, Tower â B<br/>\r\n5/6 Shobhana Nagar<br/>\r\nVasana Road, Vadodara, 390015<br/>\r\nGujarat, India<br/>\r\n', '', '[\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"HSC, Undergraduate(Bachelors), Postgraduate(Masters)\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-01', '2022-08-31', 'Nilam Patel Bahushrut Foundation ', 0.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-16 17:04:24', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-08-26 11:10:44', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1244, 'gs5zub23ZOgNfmocQJ', 'Abroad', 'Gates scholarship (USA) ', 'https://www.thegatesscholarship.org/sign-up', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The gates scholarship along with financial support receive support that enables the best version them self\r\nthroughout their entire lives, low-income students from minorities get a chance to study in America\'s best institutions which they are not able to get admissions without gates scholarships  <br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Benefit <br/></b>\r\n<li> The tuition fee will be covered <br/><br/>\r\n<li>Residential accommodation will be covered <br/><br/>\r\n<li>Transportation cost will be covered <br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility criteria<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li> The applicant must be a high school senior<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> The applicant must be from one of these ethnicities African American, American Indian/ Alaska Native   Asian Pacific, Islander America<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> The applicant must be US citizen national or permanent citizen <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> The applicant must pell eligible<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> The applicant must not be receiving any other grant or family support<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> The applicant\'s academic performance will be an outstanding<b>  GPA of 3.3 on a 4.0 scale </b><br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li> The students need to attach their recent transcripts.\r\nA copy of the Student Aid Report (SAR) after FAFSA is completed<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> Copy of the letter offering this funding aid award\r\nAdmission letter to a full-time, four-year bachelorâs degree at a not-for-profit, public or private university<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> Candidatesâ headshot photo<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> Applicantsâ resumes highlighting their academic excellence and involvement in extracurricular activities<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>', '1) The applicant has to create an MYTGS profile on www.gatesscholarship.org in order to apply<br/>\r\n\r\n2)  In Phase II, 2000 semi-finalists will be called to further process the application<br/>\r\n\r\n3) The Gates Scholarship application will include a questionnaire, essays, updated transcripts, and\r\nletters of recommendation<br/>\r\n\r\n4) Phase Il of the scholarship must be completed by January<br/>\r\n\r\n5)  In March, 600 candidates will be selected for the final phase<br/>\r\n\r\n6) In the final phase, the candidates will be interviewed in person or on a video call<br/>\r\n\r\n7) In April the 300 finalists will be announced and asked for documentation clearance for the\r\naward<br/>\r\n', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-26', '2022-09-15', 'Bill & Melinda Gates foundation', 0.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-17 16:07:55', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-17 10:43:00', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
