(1248, 'uiSnDH14flmdsQMFSZ', 'Internship', 'CPPR Internship Programme', 'https://www.cppr.in/internships', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The main goal is to provide you with a quality learning experience. In turn, our interns will lend their expertise from various fields to our mission. As an intern at Gavi, you will<br/><br>\r\n\r\n1. Gain a good understanding of our mission, business model, and day-to-day operations<br/><br>\r\n2. Expand your work experience with meaningful assignments and projects<br/><br>\r\n3. Develop your existing skills and learn new ones that will be useful for your career<br/><br>\r\n4. Work in a dynamic and multicultural environment that will help you broaden your professional network<br/><hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Objectives of the CPPR Internship Programme</b> <br/>\r\n \r\n<li>To develop intentional learning objectives/goals that are structured and supervised by a Guide/Mentor with a relevant and related background in the field<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> To provide students with a comprehensive practical experience in a setting where learning is the primary objective of the experience<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li> Provide students or individuals with carefully supervised exposure to CPPRâs work<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li> Aims to balance the internâs learning goals with the organizationâs needs<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li> Promotes academic, career or personal development of the interns<br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>What the CPPR Internship Programme includes</b><br/>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Industry related soft skills development<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Identifying interns learning objectives<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Helping interns achieve their goals and objectives from this Internship Programme<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n <li>Typically a minimum of 45 days to a maximum of 9 months<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> The internship will be fullâtime<br/><hr/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<b>Who is applicable for the CPPR Internship Programme</b><br/>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Individuals who are in their 3rd year of undergraduate degree<br/><br/>\r\n<li> Individuals who have completed their undergraduate degree<br/><br/>\r\n<li> Individuals who have completed or are pursuing their postgraduate degree<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Note: </b>Only shortlisted applicants would be notified.(within 2 weeks)', '<li> Updated Resume ', '1. log in to your Dashboard<br/>\r\n 2. Click on Apply button and it will redirect to the application form<br/>\r\n 3. Fill the form with appropriate details and click on submit<br/>', '', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Undergraduate and Postgraduate\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-08-01', '2022-12-31', 'Centre For Public Policy Research', 0.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-08-19 12:10:55', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-08-29 10:00:20', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1249, '0EBEn1AmByq6acKPXZ', 'Internship', 'ADB Internship Program', 'https://www.adb.org/work-with-us/careers/internship-program', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Internship Program is a project-oriented learning opportunity for graduate students to gain experience through research assignments based on ADBâs current operational needs.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>ADB advertises internship assignments twice a year and welcomes motivated, open-minded, and self-directed individuals to apply.<br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>The internship program offers the opportunity to</b><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>work in a major international development organization<br/>\r\n<li>work collaboratively with experienced professionals from over 50 different countries<br/>\r\n<li> Gain a deeper understanding of development finance and the impact of the work ADB does; and\r\n<li>contribute to ADBâs business through research outputs<br/>\r\n\r\n <hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Internship candidates must</b><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Be enrolled in a Masterâs- or PhD-level program at a school in one of the ADB member nations, both prior to and after the internship assignment<br/><br/>\r\n<li>Be engaged in academic study in a field directly related to ADBâs work<br/><br/>\r\n<li>Be a national of one of ADBâs members<br/><br/>\r\n<li> Possess an excellent command of English  and have professional experience relevant to the assignment<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>The internship application process is online through the ADB Career and Employment System (ACES). School registration and nomination are no longer required.\r\n<hr.\r\n\r\n ', '<li> Updated Resume \r\n', '1. log in to your Dashboard<br/>\r\n2. Click on Apply button and it will redirect to the application form<br/>\r\n3. Fill the form with appropriate details and click on submit<br/>\r\n', 'eawg', '[\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\",\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"Masters, PHD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"