(1271, '0bZjriJIaFyR8LR3ci', 'Scholarship', 'TWAS-DBT Postgraduate Fellowship', 'https://twas.org/opportunity/twas-dbt-postgraduate-fellowship-programme', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Department of Biotechnology (DBT) of the Ministry of Science and Technology in India, and UNESCO-TWAS established a fellowship program for foreign scholars from developing countries who wish to pursue research toward a Ph.D. in biotechnology. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Field<br/></b>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n01-Agricultural Sciences<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n02-Structural, Cell, and Molecular Biology<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n03-Biological Systems and Organisms<br/>\r\n\r\n04-Medical and Health Sciences incl. Neurosciences<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n05-Chemical Sciences<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<b>Applicants for these fellowships must meet the following criteria<br/></b>\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Be a maximum age of 35 years on 31 December of the application year<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Be nationals of a developing country (other than India)<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Must not hold any visa for temporary or permanent residency in India or any developed country<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Hold a Masterâs or equivalent degree in science or engineering<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* For SANDWICH Fellowships, be registered Ph.D. students in their home country and provide the âRegistration and No Objection Certificateâ from the HOME university (sample is included in the application form)<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* For FULL-TIME Fellowships; be willing to register at a university in India<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Be accepted at a biotechnology institution in India (see sample Acceptance Letter that can be downloaded below or included in the application form). N.B. Requests for acceptance must be directed to the chosen host institution(s), and NOT to DBT<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Provide a research proposal outline based on the format of the sample that can be downloaded below<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Provide evidence of proficiency in English, if the medium of education was not English<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Provide evidence that s/he will return to her/his home country on completion of the fellowship<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Not take up other assignments during the period of her/his fellowship<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n* Be financially responsible for any accompanying family members<br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n ', '<li>Aadhar Card<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Income Certificate<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Bank Details<br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Candidate Photographs<br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1) Register to the online website from here<br/>\r\n\r\n2) Choose your program and fill out your application form<br/>\r\n\r\n3) Make your academic profile and submit your documents and certificates<br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '', '[\"Masters\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\"]', '\"Postgraduate (Masters)\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-08-11', '2022-09-15', 'UNESCO-TWAS ', 0.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-09-02 10:38:15', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-09-02 05:14:46', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1272, 'jHRQrMQ0oaLM1o5Puy', 'Scholarship', 'Facebook PhD Fellowship ', 'https://research.facebook.com/fellowship/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Meta Research Ph.D. Fellowship is a global program designed to encourage and support promising doctoral students who are engaged in innovative and relevant research in areas related to computer science and engineering at an accredited university. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>The program is open to students in any year of their Ph.D. study. We also encourage people of diverse backgrounds and experiences to apply, especially those from traditionally under-represented minority groups.<br><br><li> Applications are evaluated based on the strength of the studentâs research statement, publication record, and recommendation letters.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Winners of the Fellowship are entitled to receive two years of paid tuition and fees, a $42,000 annual stipend to cover living costs, various opportunities to engage with Meta researchers, and an invitation to the annual Fellowship Summit.<br><br>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Meta does not claim any right to work performed during or as a result of the Fellowship. All research conducted by the Fellow belongs to the Fellow. This excludes any work completed as a Meta employee, should the Fellow do an internship or consult during their Fellowship.<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility Criteria</b><br/>\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Enrolled in a Ph.D. program at an accredited university in the fall following the application cycle (i.e., Fall 2023)<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Engaged in research related to computer science and engineering in areas relevant to Meta, as specified in the Available Fellowships section<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>The program is open to students at all accredited universities around the world.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>We will not be offering awards to candidates whose research is outside the specified research areas described in the Available Fellowships section. Please review each Available Fellowship description carefully to ensure you are aligned with the correct research area<br/><br/><hr>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n ', '<li>CV or resume-there is no page limit to the resume or CV.<br/><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Research statement-statements of research should be 500 words or less and should clearly identify your area of focus, its importance to the field, and its applicability to Meta as it pertains to one of the Available Fellowships. Note that references or citations count toward the 500-word limit. To optimize the word count for research statements, references and citations should be added to CVs, which do not have a word or page limit<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Two letters of recommendation-one of the letters of recommendation needs to come from a Ph.D. advisor or a research advisor. The other may come from another professor or industry contact<br/><br/><hr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n ', '1)Click the below \"login & apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Click on apply  <br>\r\n3)Read the instructions carefully<br>\r\n4)Register and Verify your account<br>\r\n5)Fill  both the parts of the application<br>\r\n6)Submit the application', '', '[\"PHD\"]', '[\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"PHD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-08-10', '2022-09-20', 'Meta Research ', 3341515.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-09-02 11:13:47', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-03 10:25:33', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1273, 'zPv1Mp07vehWfgdya7', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Logo Design Contest for World Hindi Conference', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/logo-design-contest-12th-world-hindi-conference-0/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'As part of the promotion and propagation of Hindi language abroad, the Government of India has been organizing World Hindi Conference in India and abroad.<br><br> <li>It is organized by MEA with an interval of 3-4 years, with the active support of the host country and other local cultural & linguistic organizations.<br><br>\r\n<li>The 12th World Hindi Conference is to be held in Fiji in 2023. Hindi, mentioned in the Constitution of Fiji, is the country\'s third Official Language. It is also the link language between different Indian-origin population groups in Fiji.<br><br>\r\n<li>These conferences have primarily deliberated upon how Hindi could be a medium of serving mankind in the prevailing world environment and how Hindi could get recognized in the United Nations and move forward as a world language serving the cause of humanity.<br><hr>', 'Pdf or image of the designed logo <br><hr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Logo design criteria</b><br>\r\n<li>It should reflect the India-Fiji friendship<br>\r\n<li>It should reflect the colours of flags of the two countries<br>\r\n<li> Marine linkages and historical connections between India and Fiji should be reflected in the logo<br>\r\n<li>logo should be inspirational, with illustrations that capture the oceans to represent the island features, looking at Fijiâs geographical location in the world<br>\r\n<li>The unique national heritage of Fiji should also feature the logo in the way of art, craft etc<br>\r\n<li> The logo should showcase the journey of Hindi in Fij<br>\r\n<li>12th Vishwa Hindi Samellan Fijiâ should reflect prominently in the logo (in Devanagari script)\r\n<br><li>The logo is to be in Hindi ONLY\r\nEach entry should be accompanied by a brief description of the logo and how best it encapsulates the essence of elements mentioned above.<br><hr>', '1)Click the below \"login and apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Read the terms and conditions of the contest<br>\r\n3)Register/login yourself for the contest <br>\r\n4) Submit Your Logo<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-08-30', '2022-09-30', 'Government of India', 75000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-03 09:36:58', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-08 08:01:52', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1274, 'FNXDahGOrLkOaDfYop', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Suggest a Tagline for IRDAI', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/suggest-tagline-irdai/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority of India (IRDAI) is the regulator for the Insurance Industry in India, established in the year 2000 to ensure the protection of policyholdersâ interests as well as to promote orderly growth of the insurance industry in India.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>In that context, IRDAI invites people of the country to suggest a suitable tagline that encompasses and depicts its role.<br><br>\r\n<li>Tagline should be in Hindi<br><br><hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility Criteria:</b><br><br>\r\n1- The Participants must be above 18 years and a citizen of India.<br>\r\n2- Entries are open only for individuals and not groups/organizations<br>\r\n3- Entries will be judged on creativity, originality, simplicity, visual impact, vibrancy, artistic merit, and how well the theme is communicated.<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Prize details:</b>\r\nThe Winning entry will be awarded cash prizes for each category (1st, 2nd, and 3rd prize)<br><br>\r\n1st Prize - Rs 20 lakhs<br>\r\n2nd Prize - Rs 10 lakhs<br>\r\n3rd Prize - Rs 5 lakhs<br><hr>\r\n\r\n', 'Upload your tagline<br><hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Tagline Criteria:</b><br>\r\n<li>The tagline should be in Hindi.<br><br>\r\n<li>The tagline should be crisp and short. (Preferably not more than 10 words)<br><br>\r\n<li>The tagline should be easily understandable and contemporary.<br><br>\r\n<li>The tagline should resonate with the image of the IRDAI.<br><br>\r\n<li>The tagline should not have been previously published in any print and digital media and must\r\nnot contain any provocative, objectionable, or inappropriate content.<br><hr>\r\n', '1)Click the below \"Click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Read the terms and conditions of the contest<br>\r\n3)Register/login yourself for the contest<br>\r\n4) Submit Your tagline<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-08-30', '2022-09-15', 'Government of India ', 2000000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-03 10:59:31', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-06 05:25:29', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
