(1282, '6hxPJ5zGDWmwyLrfl8', 'Abroad', 'Chevening Scholarships For Indian Students 2023-2024', 'https://www.chevening.org/scholarship/india/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Chevening is the UK governmentâs international scholarships program. Funded by the Foreign, Commonwealth, and Development Office and partner organizations, we offer awards to study in the UK for <b>one year</b> on a fully funded masterâs degree course.<br><br><hr>\r\n<b>Scholarship details:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>As Chevening Scholarships are fully-funded, your award includes the following:\r\nuniversity tuition fees, a monthly stipend, travel costs to and from the UK, an arrival allowance, a homeward departure allowance, the cost of one visa application,\r\nand a travel grant to attend Chevening events in the UK.<br>\r\n<li>Once you are progressed to the next stage of the process, you will be required to upload two reference letters to the online application system <br>\r\n<li>Referees should be either in an academic or professional capacity. They should not be a relative or close personal friends.<br>\r\n<li>If you are shortlisted to interview, you will be invited to attend an interview in your home country, in the city/town where the British embassy or high commission has representation.<br>\r\n<li>Interview slots are available on a first-come-first-served basis, so we suggest that you book your slot as soon as possible. <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>All Chevening applicants must submit their education documents, references, and one unconditional UK university offer. <br><li>Passport<br><li>national ID.<hr>\r\n<b>Scholarship eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Be a citizen of a Chevening-eligible country or territory.<br>\r\n<li>Return to your country of citizenship for a minimum of two years after your award has ended.<br>\r\n<li>Have at least two years (equivalent to 2,800 hours) of work experience.<br>\r\n<li>Apply to three different eligible UK university courses and have received an unconditional offer from one of these choices by 13 July 2023.', '1)Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Go through the guidelines, references and interviews sections carefully <br>\r\n3)Click on the \"apply today\" button<br>\r\n4)Register yourself and Fill out the application form', '', '[\"Masters\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\"]', '\"Masters\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-01', '2022-11-01', 'Government of United Kingdom', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-08 10:54:48', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-28 04:01:15', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
