(1287, 'gNIYta7YkEHcJRoR92', 'Internship', 'SEWA Bharat-Website and Digital Systems Design internship', 'https://sewabharat.org/internship/website-and-digital-systems-design/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Self-Employed Womenâs Association (SEWA) is a movement to empower women working in the informal economy. SEWA Bharat is part of the national SEWA movement. Established in 1984, it is a national federation of SEWA organizations of women working in the informal economy.<br><br>\r\n<li> SEWA Bharat emerged out of the need to address the SEWA movementâs challenges with geographical expansion and coordination.<br><br><li> SEWA Bharat comprises a family of SEWA organizations to further informal women workersâ rights, livelihoods, financial independence, education, health, and social security.<br><hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Scope of Work:</b>\r\n<li>Unlocking Google My Business as a tool to enable the growth of women-led collective social enterprises in the financial and agricultural sector<br><br>\r\n<li>Accumulate and organize district-wise details of physical centers and offices by coordinating with the enterprise teams<br><br>\r\n<li>Coordinate with SEWA Bharatâs Digital mentor and various stakeholders for technical reviews and guidance.<br><br>\r\n<li>Designing basic multilingual websites for women-led collective social enterprises in Uttarakhand, Punjab, and Bihar<br><br>\r\n<li>Explore WhatsApp My Business and other digital platforms as livelihood tools for women micro-entrepreneurs within the SEWA ecosystem<br><hr>\r\n<b>Key Skills:</b>\r\n<li>Tech-savvy and self-learner<br>\r\n<li>Eye for Typography, Color, Composition<br>\r\n<li>Keen to probe the scope of digital mediums in<br> <li>furthering grassroots entrepreneurship<br><hr>\r\n<b>Note:</b><br>\r\n<li>Remote, but Delhi-based candidates are encouraged to apply.<br>\r\n<li>This internship is for a duration of 2 months along with a stipend of Rs. 7,500 per month.<br>', '<li>Samples of your work<br>\r\n<li>CV or Resume<br>\r\n<li>An essay of around 100 words (in the application)', '1)Click the below\"click here to apply button\"<br>\r\n2)Go through the details of the internship carefully<br>\r\n3)Click on the apply link<br>\r\n4) Fill out the application form and submit.', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-01', '2022-12-31', 'SEWA Bharat NGO', 7500.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-10 10:07:47', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-10 04:42:27', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1288, 'HYtBl1glSNltKNo1fv', 'Internship', 'WOMEN SAFETY WING, HYDERABAD- Internship Program', 'https://womensafetywing.telangana.gov.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Internship-with-WSW.pdf', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The last date for receiving applications is the 10th of every previous month for the upcoming internship batch, commencing on the 1st of every month.<br><br>\r\n<li>Applications are invited from students for the Online Internship Programme with the Women Safety Wing, Telangana State Police. This program is intended to provide exposure to students on the functioning of the department, initiatives, research, and statistical works.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Students pursuing Graduation/Post-Graduation from any recognized University/Institution on a\r\nregular basis.<br>\r\n<li>Should be less than 25 years of age<br><hr>\r\n<b>Note:</b>\r\n<li> Applicants who have access to a Laptop or Desktop will be given preference.<br>\r\n<li> The Maximum number of internships that can be awarded for each internship batch is up to 10.<br>\r\n<li> Selection of interns will be made by a Selection Committee appointed by the WSW, purely\r\nbased on merit.<br>\r\n<li>Internship Certificate will be provided to students on successful completion of the Internship <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>A 250-word â Statement of Purpose (SoP)â for interning with the Women Safety Wing, Telangana\r\nState Police will be required to be submitted by the applicants along with the application form, which\r\nwill serve as a basis for selection.<br><br>\r\n<li>SOP, Co-curricular activities, internships, successful research projects undertaken, work/projects\r\nwith NGOs are the few illustrated criteria for enhancing the chances of selection<br><br>\r\n<b>Note :</b> Resume and documents are to be mailed as per the given format only.<br>', '1)Click the below\"Click here to apply button\"<br>\r\n2)Go through the details of the internship caref