(1290, '6NzwFUcFvKUFeicH0h', 'Competitions and Awards', 'KARTAVYA PATH - Photography Contest', 'https://www.mygov.in/KartavyaPath', 'I am on Kartavya Path, MyGovIndia, competitions, free competitions, photo contest, online competitions, photography competition, contest, cash prize, win cash prize, contest reward, competitions, free competitions, Free Contest, Contesting, Online competitions, Government of India Scholarship, Scholarship, Scholarship for all, Government Scholarship, photography contest, photo contest, photography competition, photo competition, photography awards, online photography contest, free photo contest, best photography award, pictures competition, photo contest website free ', 'Free contest - Kartavya path photography contest | win cash prize', 'Ministry of Housing & Urban Affairs is launching the \'I am on Kartavya Path\' photography contest, Click  photos of Kartavya Path & get chance to win prizes', 'I am on Kartavya Path photography contest', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The renaming of Rajpath as Kartavya Path will denote the change from the colonial \'Right to Rule\' to the democratic \'Duty to Serve\', reminding the 130 crore citizens of India to contribute and work with renewed zeal towards the vision of a New India.<br><br>\r\n<li>To celebrate this momentous achievement, the Ministry of Housing and Urban Affairs is launching the <b> \'I am on Kartavya Path\' </b>photography contest. Click mesmerizing photos of Kartavya Path and stand a chance to win exciting prizes!<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Participants can also share photographs on Kartavya Path using <b>#KartavyaPath</b> tagging @MyGovIndia on any social media platforms like Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Koo, Roposo, etc.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n1) Two best photographs will be awarded weekly with a prize of Rs.5000 each.<br>\r\n2) A \'Kartavya Path Photo\' will also be selected every month. A prize of Rs.10,000 will be awarded to the winner.<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> Read the terms and conditions of the competition <b><a href=\"https://static.mygov.in/rest/s3fs-public/mygov_1662638721105216201.pdf\"_blank\">here</a></b>', '<li> Photographs must be submitted in JPG/JPEG/ PNG format. ', '1)Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Read the terms and conditions of the Competitions carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on \"Login to participate\"<br>\r\n4)Submit your entry.', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"\\\"All\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-08', '2023-01-31', 'Government of India', 10000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-12 10:26:15', 1, NULL, '2023-01-14 06:17:28', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1291, 'txyakeZGpWKo9JmwPF', 'Competitions and Awards', 'India\'s Wealth, Millets for Health - Comic Story Contest', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/indias-wealth-millets-health-comic-story-contest', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The U.N. General Assembly adopted a resolution, sponsored by India and supported by more than 70 countries, declaring 2023 as the International Year of Millets. <br><br><li>The resolution is intended to increase public awareness of the health benefits of millets and their suitability for cultivation under tough conditions marked by climate change. The Ministry of Agriculture & Farmers Welfare would be the nodal ministry for the International Year of Millet (IYoM)-2023 celebrations. <br><br><li>Therefore, India is now taking the lead in popularizing the theme in a strong manner at the international level through various campaigns.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Scholarship eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>The contest is open to the entire world.<br>\r\n<li> Multiple entries by a participant are not allowed<br><hr>\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n1. Selected entries will be <b>amplified on social Media</b>.<br>\r\n2. 100 Selected winners will get a <b>Certificate</b>.<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> Read the terms and condition of the competition carefully <b><a href=\"https://static.mygov.in/rest/s3fs-public/mygov_1662457027105216201.pdf\"_blank\">here</a></b>', '<li> Designed comic story should be saved as <b> JPEG/PDF file</b><br>\r\n<li> Description of your design should be saved as pdf file in up to <b>250 words</b>. <br>', '1)Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Read the terms and conditions of the Competitions carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on <b>\"Login to participate\"</b><br>\r\n4)Submit your entry.<br>', 'Certificate', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"ALL\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-05', '2022-11-05', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-12 11:08:50', 1, 'humera@triwits.com ', '2022-10-07 04:19:07', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1292, 'JkIdttqruSzTBd9dEO', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Mascot Design Contest for IEPFA', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/mascot-design-contest-iepfa', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Investor Education and Protection Fund Authority (IEPFA) is a Statutory Body established by the Government of India implementing the provision of Section 125 of the Companies Act, 2013. <br><br>\r\n<li>The authority has a dual mandate of promoting awareness about investors\' education and protection pertaining to the interests of investors and making refunds of shares, unclaimed dividends, matured deposits/debentures, etc., to the rightful claimant through the proper channel.<br><br>\r\n<li>To mark this spirit of glory  IEPFA is announcing a series of run-up contests & competitions, one of which is a âPehchaanâ a hybrid Mascot designing competition by IEPFA for students and the general public at the pan India level.<br><br>\r\n<li>The competition has 2 categories based on age -<br>\r\na)Category-I: 11 to 18 Yrs.<br>\r\nb)Category-II: 19 Yrs. and above<br><hr>\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\nFirst Prize Rs. 10000<br> Second Prize Rs. 5000<br> Third Prize Rs. 2000 <br><li>Certificates and mentions in IEPFAâs social media handles, Magazine.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Mascot  Design:</b><br>\r\n<li>Mascot should be based on IEPFA mandates only to make people\r\nassociate with IEPFA initiatives. <br><li> Mascots can be an object, animals, people, personifications, fictional characters, or\r\ncreatures.<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> For more details regarding the Competition,theme,result and awards click <b><a href=\"https://static.mygov.in/rest/s3fs-public/mygov_1662493908105216201.pdf\"_blank\">Here</a></b>\r\n\r\n', '<li>Digital designs should be submitted as a 300 dpi JPG or PDF. <br>\r\n<li>If submitting a traditional\r\npainting or drawing, it should be scanned and sent as a 300 dpi JPG or PDF and clearly\r\nvisible. ', '1)Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Read the terms and conditions of the Competitions <b> <a href=\"https://static.mygov.in/rest/s3fs-public/mygov_1662494089105216201.pdf\">Here</a></b><br>\r\n3) Click on \"Login to participate\"<br>\r\n4)Submit your entry.<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-07', '2022-09-30', 'Government of India', 10000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-12 11:41:20', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-12 07:31:57', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1293, 'wHbIN011FWSNZ98rHo', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Heal in India - Logo Designing Competition', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/heal-india-logo-designing-competition/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Ministry of Health and Family Welfare (MoHFW) is launching the âHeal in Indiaâ initiative, a pan-India initiative catering to citizens of the world. <br><br>\r\n<li>The âHeal in Indiaâ initiative will be focused on positioning India as a global leader in health and boosting medical tourism in the country.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>This initiative involves the launch of a digital portal for Medical Value Travel (MVT), a window of Integrated Indian Healthcare to the world. <br><hr>\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n1. Cash prize of Rs. 1,00,000/- to the winner.<br>\r\n2. Logo will be used on the Heal in India Digital Platform<br>', '<li>The participant should submit a high resolution (600 dpi) image in <b>JPEG format</b>.<br>\r\n<li> The winning entry must later be submitted in scalable vector graphic format (EPS).<br>\r\n<li>Each participant must submit a brief description (maximum 100 words) of the logo in English or Hindi along with the image (i.e., an Explanation of the logo, symbol, color, etc.)<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b>Read the terms and conditions <b><a href=\"https://static.mygov.in/rest/s3fs-public/mygov_166296400082937911.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>\r\n', '1)Click on the below\"click here to apply button\"<br>\r\n2)Read the details of the competition carefully<br>\r\n3)Click on \"login to apply button\"<br>\r\n4)Submit your entry', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-12', '2022-10-10', 'Government of India', 100000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-13 09:53:04', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-13 04:30:53', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1294, '2rSa6JTsUokvRpeOQz', 'Internship', 'Muskurahat Foundation internship', 'https://muskurahat.org.in/internship-program/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=search&utm_campaign=google-dtim-search-tier1-students&gclid=CjwKCAjwsfuYBhAZEiwA5a6CDE67By00p7G0Xy49NiLE6xe0Tmlc36tZ69CJrGe6EFr_pEDf02vZtBoCWu4QAvD_BwE', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'We are working towards uplifting children and youth from underserved communities to rise up to an equitable platform â which will enable them to become happy, independent and socially conscious people which in turn will help uplift their communities.<br><br>\r\n<li>You can contribute your skills or give <b>âShramdaan\'</b> as it is called, to support our efforts to provide our children with holistic education which includes, experiential academic learning, life skills, mental well-being, and more.<br><br><li>Your internship will be work from home social internship , with flexible hours<br><hr>\r\n<b>Roles and responsibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Gathering support by running a fundraising campaign in your network.<br>\r\n<li>Reach out to people and educate them about the cause and encourage them to contribute. <br>\r\n<li>Your contribution of 90 hours of Social service over 30 days, will make you eligible to get certified.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Perks and benefits:</b><br>\r\n<li>Get certified for the online internship and the crowdfunding course while working for a cause<br>\r\n<li>Get paid for your contribution of skills and time\r\nSpecial mentions on social media and LOR for the best performers<br>\r\n<li>Completion certificate for your social internship and community hours<br>\r\n<li> Performance-based remuneration - your stipend will be 20% of the amount you raise<br>\r\n<li>Upon completion, you will be certified for the course crowdfunding and fundraising for NGO<br>\r\n<li>Get a Letter of recommendation from the president of our organization.<br>\r\n<li>Get recommended on LinkedIn by the president of our organisation<br>', '<li>Email address and Whatsapp number<br>\r\n<li>Essay on why you want to join the internship', '1)Click the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Fill in your details <br>\r\n3)Write an essay<br>\r\n4)Submit your application', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-10', '2022-09-30', 'Muskurahat Foundation', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-13 11:50:34', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-13 06:42:40', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
