(1301, '0MnxFXpuvS0gBFL5W4', 'Internship', 'Young professional fellows- Government of Maharashtra', 'https://kaushalya.mahaswayam.gov.in/assets/img/Fellows_Advertisement.pdf', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', ' To create a holistic skilling and entrepreneurship ecosystem in the state, the Skills, Employment,\r\nEntrepreneurship and Innovation Department run various initiatives and policies through its\r\nvarious field offices <br><br>\r\n<li>The Department provides a unique opportunity for young professionals interested in the development\r\nsector to gain first-hand experience of working in Government Departments and their field offices and\r\ndirectly contribute towards making change at scale. <br><br>\r\n<li>Therefore, we are hiring Young Professional\r\nFellows with a passion for improving government performance and resolving social problems.<br><hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Skills preferred:</b><br>\r\n<li>Strong project management capabilities.<br>\r\n<li>Excellent written and verbal  communication<br>\r\n<li>strong project management skills<br>\r\n<li>sound quantitative and analytical skills<br>\r\n <li>Willingness to travel is required.<br>\r\n<li>Proficiency in Marathi will be added advantage.<br><hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Preferred Qualification:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li> A Graduate or master\'s (pursuing or completed) in fields like Economics/Public\r\nPolicy/Management/ Engineering/Mathematics/Computer Science/ Information Technology Data\r\nManagement/ Sales / HR / Media - Journalism / Communication / Literature & allied disciplines\r\nalong with strong IT and presentation skills.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li> Experience in skilling livelihoods, entrepreneurship, employment, start-ups, incubators, digital\r\nmarketing, fieldwork, human resources & admin, media, communications or public relations, and\r\nproficiency in the documentation would be an added advantage.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The candidates must be proficient in Microsoft office, data analytics, data visualization software, etc.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li> For media & communication fellows, digital marketing expertise, content management systems,\r\nsocial media platforms, graphic designing (Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, Adobe InDesign,\r\nillustrator, Corel Draw, Crello, Canva, etc) is desirable which will help in the dissemination of initiatives\r\nand through print & digital media.<br><br>\r\n<li>Upper age limit 35 yrs on September 08, 2022, <br><hr>\r\n<b>Note:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Duration of the Fellowship shall be for a period of <b>2 years</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li> The salary bracket offered YP Fellows shall be in the range of <b>Rs 40,000 to\r\n50,000 </b>depending on the qualification and experience of the candidate.<br>\r\n\r\n<li>Travel costs for official work outside Mumbai will be borne by the office.<br>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Certificates</b> will be given to Young Professional Fellows on satisfactory completion of\r\nthe fellowship period of 2 years.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>Application Form as given in the link below<br>\r\n\r\n<li>A Statement of Purpose*<br>\r\n<li>Detailed CV <br>\r\n<li> 2 letters of recommendations<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b><br>\r\n<li>For more details regarding the Fellowship, application form, and other click <b><a href=\"https://kaushalya.mahaswayam.gov.in/assets/img/Fellows_Advertisement.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b><br>\r\n<li> Mail all the above documents to <b><a href=mailto:\" application.seeid@gmail.com\"> application.seeid@gmail.com</a></b>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\"  button<br>\r\n2. Go through the fellowship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the application form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Mail the zip file to <b><a href=mailto:\" application.seeid@gmail.com\"> application.seeid@gmail.com</a>\r\n', '', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\",\"Masters (All)\"]', '\"Bachelors or Masters\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NUL