(1304, 'inD9Y04BaybUufV3cp', 'Internship', 'The Rural Media Fellowship ', 'https://www.villagesquare.in/rural-media-fellowship-2022/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Rural Media Fellowship aims to encourage young, emerging, and passionate journalists to leverage storytelling as a tool for social change. The purpose of the Fellowship is to provide an opportunity for young changemakers to bring a fresh, inspirational perspective on rural lives.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Often the stories of rural India and its changemakers are missing from the mainstream media discourse. The mainstream media platforms â both digital and print â solely focus on the stories of rural distress and alienation, never really giving an account of what it is like to be living in Indiaâs rural. <br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The Rural Media Fellowship is a step towards giving adequate voice to rural India â through nurturing and giving opportunities to dynamic, young journalists.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The Fellowship will focus on rural stories and insights from the domains of education, health, sanitation, livelihood, micro-enterprises, and arts and culture.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The stories (articles, videos, photo essays) produced by the fellows will be published on the Village Square website and social media platforms. <br><hr>\r\n<b>Selection and Eligibility Criteria:</b><br>\r\n<li>Candidates must be between the age of <b>22-30</b> <br>\r\n<li>A bachelorâs degree in mass media/journalism<br>\r\n<li>Candidates with 2 or more years of relevant experience will be preferred<br>\r\n<li>Ability to live and work in remote, rural areas \r\nMust demonstrate an interest and understanding of rural India and its issues and challenges \r\nComfort with multimedia and other innovative storytelling techniques. <br><hr>\r\n<b>Note:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Mentorship from industry experts within the Village Square network<br>\r\n<li> A stipend of <b>35000</b> per month<br>\r\n<li> The certificate will be awarded on successful completion of the fellowship <br>\r\n<li>Fellowship duration - <b>9 months</b> (November 2022 â September 2023).<br>\r\n\r\n', '<li> Resume<br>\r\n<li> Essay of maximum 250 word<br>\r\n<li>  2 professional recommendation letters<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> for more details click <b> <a href=\"https://www.villagesquare.in/rural-media-fellowship-2022/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the details of the fellowship<br>\r\n3. Click on the \" google form\"<br>\r\n4. Fill out the form and attach necessary documents<br>\r\n5. Submit the application', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\"]', '\"Bachelors degree in mass media or journalism\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-10', '2022-10-02', 'Village Square foundation', 35000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-17 12:32:01', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-17 07:06:07', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
