(1311, 'd2s77hA8tcJS8VY9co', 'Scholarship', 'YASHAD-SUMEDHA Scholarship Program', 'http://www.sumedha.org/yashad-sumedhascholarship/index.php', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Sumedha is a voluntary non-profit organization registered under the Rajasthan Society Registration Act 1958 with its office in Jaipur.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The Principal objective of the organization is to help the talented children of poor families who are deprived of higher education due to lack of resources and because of poverty they have to work at low-paid jobs in the government/private sector.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n1. 75% and above in senior secondary and studying in B.Tech in any Government College (<b>I semester</b>).<br>\r\n2. Family income to be less than two lakh fifty thousand per annum.<br>\r\n3. Students should belong to <b>Udaipur, Rajsamand, Chittor, Bhilwara, and Ajmer districts</b>.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Note:</b><br>\r\n<li>Hard copy should be sent after attestation by the college by 25th October 2022 at<br><p style=\"color:blue;\"> Sumedha office <br> 5, Keshav Vihar <br>\r\nGopalpura Bypass Road<br>\r\n Jaipur 302018.<br></p>\r\n<li> The Last date for online application submission is 15th October 2022<br>\r\n \r\n<li>The scholarship would be given for <b>four years</b> of the B.Tech program, provided the student maintains first division marks.<br>\r\n \r\n', '<li> A scanned passport size photograph (Size up to 200 kb) \r\n<li> 1 family photograph of 7x5 size. \r\n<li> Only <b>jpeg or jpg</b> formats are allowed. ', '1) Hit the below \"Click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2) Click on the \"Apply\" button<br>\r\n3) Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4) Submit the application<br>', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"B. Tech\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 250000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-2