(1317, 'JRBbLMmRguGNifeAu3', 'Abroad', 'CYD Master Thesis Fellowship', 'https://www.epfl.ch/research/services/fund-research/funding-opportunities/fellowship-mobility/cyd-fellowships/cyd-master-thesis-fellowship/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'To promote research and education in cyber-defense, the EPFL and the Cyber-Defence (CYD) Campus have jointly launched the âCYD Fellowships â A Talent Program for Cyber-Defence Research.â<br><br>\r\n<li> Cyber threats have been accelerating due to the exponential growth of network connectivity. These new capabilities provide myriad opportunities for security hackers to wreak significant damage for commercial, political, or other gains.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The Cyber-Defence (CYD) Fellowships are designed to promote new solutions to major challenges in the fields of security and data science by bringing together basic and applied research in cyber-defense.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Eligibility criteria:</b><br> \r\n<li>Citizens of any nationality may apply for the CYD <br><li>Master Thesis Fellowships for 6 months<br>\r\n<li>No age restrictions apply.<br>\r\n<li>Applicants for CYD Master Thesis Fellowships must be enrolled in a Master\'s program at a higher education institution (university or school of applied sciences) in Switzerland and have the endorsement of a professor employed in this institution willing to supervise them.<br>\r\n<li>Candidates applying for a CYD fellowship are expected to have excellent grade transcripts.<br><hr>\r\n<b>Benefits of the Fellowship:</b><br>\r\n<li>Living Allowances: CYD Master Thesis fellows receive a living allowance that is equal to CHF 2â000.- per month. <br>\r\n\r\n<li>Research Cost: A maximum amount of CHF 1â500.- for the duration of the fellowship can be granted for research costs.<br>', '<li>A letter of motivation is required, explaining why your planned research is original and why you are qualified for the fellowship and briefly describing your research achievements (maximum 2 pages).<br>\r\n<li>A curriculum vitae is required, including a list of all your publications (if relevant).<br>\r\n<li>A copy of all your diplomas and grade transcripts is required.<br>\r\n<li>The name and contact details of two referees are required.<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> For more details regarding the fellowship click <b> <a href=\"https://www.epfl.ch/research/services/fund-research/funding-opportunities/fellowship-mobility/cyd-fellowships/cyd-master-thesis-fellowship/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>\r\n\r\n', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the details of the fellowship carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit', 'Full funding', '[\"Masters\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\"]', '\"Masters\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-20', '2022-12-31', 'Swiss Federal Institute of Technology Lausanne', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-23 11:08:14', 1, NULL, '2022-09-23 05:38:14', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1318, 'HbRKg8SRnv9H06DnLQ', 'Scholarship', 'PG Indira Gandhi Scholarship', 'https://scholarships.gov.in/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'It is observed that the number of girls as against boys in certain states is declining which is a matter of\r\ngreat concern. The females are even forced to give birth to male children. <br><br>\r\n<li>In such circumstances\r\neducation of women needs to be used as an effective means for their empowerment and education will\r\nprepare them to have control over their lives. <br><br>\r\n<li>Thus, the Government of India declared\r\nelementary education as a basic human right of every child in order to achieve and promote girls\' education<br><br>\r\n<li>UGC has introduced a Post\r\nGraduate Indira Gandhi Scholarship for Single Girl Child with an aim to compensate direct costs of\r\ngirl education to all levels especially for such girls who happen to be the only girl child in their\r\nfamily<br><hr>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li><b> Single girl child</b><br>\r\n<li>Slots: 3000<br>\r\n<li>Age limit: Girl students up to the <b>age of 30 years </b>at the time of admission in the <b>first year of PG</b><br><li>Admitted to regular, full-time first year Masters Degree courses in any designated university or a post-graduate college.<br>\r\n\r\n', '<li>Affidavit regarding Single girl child status may be uploaded as per format given in the <b><a href=\"https://scholarships.gov.in/public/schemeGuidelines/Guidelines_SGC1819.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">link</a></b><br>\r\n<li> Joining report as per Annexure-I( <b><a href=\"https://scholarships.gov.in/public/schemeGuidelines/Guidelines_SGC1819.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">link</a></b>) has to be uploaded.<br>\r\n\r\n', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the details of the competition carefully <b>\r\n<a href=\"https://scholarships.gov.in/public/schemeGuidelines/Guidelines_SGC1819.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b><br>\r\n3. Login/Register on the National scholarship portal<br>\r\n4. Fill out the application form and submit<br>', '', '[\"Masters\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\"]', '\"Masters\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, 1, '2022-09-20', '2022-10-31', 'Government of India', 36000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-23 11:38:21', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-23 08:40:54', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1319, 'CFFogNoan6Z35HC71y', 'Scholarship', 'Quill Foundation Scholarship Program', 'http://www.quillfoundation.com/scholarship.php', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Quill Foundation is initiating a Scholarship/Mentoring Program for young members of society who are academically meritorious, financially weak, and interested in doing law and engaging with community issues.<br><br>\r\n<li>Quill fellows will be mentored throughout their LLB program by placing them with rights groups, community organizations, and law firms.<br><br>\r\n<li> The fellows will be trained with a vision to become community resource persons for taking up everyday struggles around rights and state provisioning.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Must pass 10+2 exams<br>\r\n<li>Must have scored a minimum of 60% marks in English<br> <li>optional/elective subjects in 10+2<br>\r\n<li>Not opting for payment/self-financing seats\r\nFinancially weak and unable to pay for their education', '<li>Essay on why you want to do law<br>\r\n<li>Previous year transcripts<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> For more details click <b> <a href=\"http://www.quillfoundation.com/scholarship.php\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Go through the scholarship details<br>\r\n3. Fill out the application form<br>\r\n4. Submit', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\"]', '\"Bachelor of Legislative Law(LLB)\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-20', '2022-12-31', 'Quill Foundation ', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-24 10:16:57', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-12 12:19:09', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1320, 'w2tjX11FjzQl6XGgc7', 'Scholarship', 'Vidya Jyoti Scholarship ', 'https://www.vidyasaarathi.co.in/Vidyasaarathi/login', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T3B3OkNtRnM&list=PLGF-es7U0ZzHrYPTCkF2FAADSqqlb7SSt&index=20', 'Rishi and Milan Khosla Foundation is a private family foundation created with a vision to deal with some of the most significant challenges facing society. <br><br>\r\n<li>The founders, Rishi and Milan Khosla have decided to initially focus on four core issues that are very important to them: Early Childhood Development, Female Empowerment, the Environment, Climate Change, and Medical Research and Healthcare.<br><br>\r\n<li> There is a significant gap in females pursuing higher education particularly in backward states and in cases of women from socio-economically underprivileged backgrounds and difficult terrains. <br><br>\r\n<li>Considering the need for gender advancement, Rishi and Milan Khosla Foundation has decided to provide scholarships to girls to improve gender equity in higher education in difficult areas.<br><br>\r\n<li>This scholarship is in collaboration with the Government of Uttarakhand to help needy and meritorious girl students through financial assistance. <br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility criteria:</b><br>\r\n<li>Minimum 75% in Class 12, Minimum 60% in Graduation<br>\r\n<li>Gender : Female<br>\r\n<li> Eligible state : Uttrakhand<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b><br>\r\n1. Students from High altitude areas (10,000 Feet and above) in Uttarakhand state will be given preference :<br>\r\na. <b>Garhwal</b> Region(Pauri Garhwal, Tehri Garhwal, Uttarkashi, Chamoli, Rudraprayag)<br>\r\nb. <b>Kumaon</b> Region(Bageshwar, Almora, Pithoragarh,\r\nChampawat)', '<li>Applicant Photo<br>\r\n<li>Proof of Identity<br>\r\n<li>Proof Of Address<br>\r\n<li>10th,12th, and Graduation Marksheets<br>\r\n<li>Previous academic marksheets<br>\r\n<li>Income Certificate/ITR/Salary Certificate/Form 16<br>\r\n<li>Student Bank Passbook<br>\r\n<li>Current Year College Fee receipt/Fee Structure Tuition and Non-Tuition <br>\r\n<li>Admission Letter<br>\r\n<li>Essay on \"Why you should be given this scholarship\"<br><br>\r\n\r\nAll documents uploaded shall be clear and must be in the <b>.jpeg .png file only</b>', '1) Hit the below \"Click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2) Login with your credentials<br>\r\n3) Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4) Submit the application', '', '[\"Masters\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\"]', '\"MA, MSc, M.Com\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 600000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-24', '2022-11-30', 'Rishi And Milan Khosla Foundation In Partnership With Govt Of Uttarakhand ', 35000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-24 17:38:57', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-11-12 05:27:50', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1321, 'o7YWJ8MAo0qDJ1vsgF', 'Scholarship', 'Indian Institute of Management Ahmedabad- Fellowship', 'https://www.iima.ac.in/c/document_library/Advt%20for%20CTL%20PDF_Nov%2015%202022.pdf', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Centre for Transportation and Logistics (CTL) is a research center that addresses critical\r\ntransportation and logistics challenges in India through an integrated, multidisciplinary\r\nprogram of research, post-graduate and executive education, technology transfer, and policy\r\nadvice. <br><br>\r\n<li>The objective of the CTL is to contribute to improving the efficiency of multi-modal\r\ntransportation systems and supply chain logistics, thereby promoting economic growth, and\r\nfostering sustainable development. <br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Ph.D. from a reputed Institute or University in India or abroad,\r\nspecializing in transportation and/or logistics (defined broadly). <br>\r\n<li>The dissertation/thesis must be\r\non a topic/theme related to transportation/logistics. <br><li>Publications in peer-reviewed journals are\r\npreferred<br><br>\r\n<b>Reward: </b><br>\r\nThe Post-Doctoral Fellow at CTL would be paid a consolidated pay plus other\r\nbenefits as per the rules of the Institute.\r\n', ' 1) A cover letter expressing interest in the position  <br>\r\n 2) A detailed CV<br>\r\n3) A detailed post-doctoral research proposal containing a research plan for two years (10 single-spaced pages max)<br>\r\n4) A synopsis of the Ph.D. dissertation (two pages max)<br>\r\n5) Three letters of reference. <br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b><br>\r\n<li>The subject line of the application email should read âApplication for the position of PDF at\r\nCTLâ. <br>\r\n<li>Candidates meeting the criteria may please send their\r\napplication to Ms. Jency Jose (Secretary, IIMA CTL) at <b><a href=mailto:\"ctl@iima.ac.in \">ctl@iima.ac.in </a></b>\r\n', '1. Hit the below click here to apply button<br>\r\n2. Go through the fellowship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Send your application along with necessary documents to to Ms. Jency Jose (Secretary, IIMA CTL) at <b><a href=mailto:\"ctl@iima.ac.in \">ctl@iima.ac.in </a></b>\r\n', '', '[\"PHD\"]', '[\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"PHD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-25', '2022-11-15', 'Indian Institute of Management Ahmedabad', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-26 10:43:21', 1, NULL, '2022-10-29 10:33:24', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
