\n<li>Academic Essay<br>', '1) Hit the below \" click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n\r\n3) Fill out the application form and submit<br>', '', '[\"Masters\"]', '[\"Masters (All)\"]', '\"Masters\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-20', '2023-01-20', 'Qatar University', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-29 10:48:54', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-29 05:54:24', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1332, '0cdUf40bnnHMcjHTYy', 'Abroad', 'IST Postdoctoral Fellowship Program 2023', 'https://ist.ac.at/en/education/postdocs/ist-bridge/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'All International Students from any part of the globe are eligible to apply for IST Postdoctoral Fellowship Scheme 2023. <br><br>\r\n<li>The IST-BRIDGE International Postdoctoral Program 2023 is great a opportunity for those candidates to have excellent academic records and who want to do their further studies in research in an international environment. <br><br>\r\n<li>The students work and learn in the field of Science with their international fellows and mentors under this Fully Funded Scholarship.<br><br>\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>This scholarship is fully funded and bears all expenses during the study duration which is 2 years.<br>\r\n<li>It gives students 4 tracks to complete their goals.<br>\r\n<li>This IST scholarship provides students BRIDGE placements and secondments if possible.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>A student can apply in any research field of his/her interest.<br>\r\n<li>Till the last date applicant must be completed a Ph.D. degree in any field before applying to IST.<br>\r\n<li>There should be 4year research experience to apply for this scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>Applicants need to complete their degrees of Ph.D. before applying to the IST for a scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>Those applicants who will not provide proof of diploma in the form of a copy are not eligible to apply.<br>\r\n<li>The applicant should not be from a local area like Austria.<br>\r\n<li>Applicant must not be involved in any other activity in Austria before applying for an IST scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>Applicant must complete research work before the call deadline after that he/she will not eligible.', '<li>Research proposal of having at least 5 pages.<br>\r\n<li>Recommendation letter.<br>\r\n<li>A table of complete ethical issues.<br><br>\r\n<b> Note:</b> For more details regarding the scholarship click <b> <a href=\"https://ist.ac.at/en/education/postdocs/ist-bridge/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>', '1) Hit the below \" click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3) Fill out the application form <br>\r\n4) submit', '', '[\"PHD\"]', '[\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"PhD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-30', '2022-11-05', 'Government of Austria', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-29 12:25:02', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-29 06:57:22', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1333, 'qa7VgmjrlndOfKI0A7', 'Abroad', 'Simmons University Kotzen Scholarship', 'https://www.simmons.edu/undergraduate/admission-and-financial-aid/tuition-financial-aid/types-financial-aid/scholarships/kotzen', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'All International Students from any part of the world are eligible to apply for Kotzen Awards at Simmons University. <br><br>\r\n<li>Candidates with high-achieving academic backgrounds are encouraged to apply for Undergraduate scholarships in the USA. <br><br>\r\n<li>Simmons University Scholarship is a Fully Funded Scholarship for all students. <br><br>\r\n<li>The scholarship duration is 4 Years until the completion of the degree. The Scholarship will cover all the expenses for an Undergraduate Degree Program.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Apply as a first-year for the fall semester<br>\r\n<li>Simmons is test optional so it is your choice if you would like to submit standardized test scores with your admission application.<br>\r\n<li> For those choosing to submit test scores, a 28 or higher on the ACT is recommended, and a 1300 or higher on the SAT<br>\r\n<li>Non-native English speakers must submit an English proficiency test (TOEFL/IELTS, TOEFL essentials, SAT/ACT scores, or Duolingo English Test)<br>\r\n<li>GPA of 3.3 or higher, unweighted<br>\r\n<li>College preparatory curriculum includes an advanced level math course during, or prior to, your senior year of high school<br>\r\n<li>A record of taking honors, advanced placement (AP), and international baccalaureate (IB) courses, as available in their high school systems<br>\r\n', '<li> short answer and a formal essay (PDF or Word Doc)<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Application details:</b> <br>\r\n\r\n<li>All candidates can apply online through Email <a href=mailto:\"mail@example.com\">ugadm@simmons.edu</a><br>\r\n<li>You need to answer short questions up to 250 words.<br>\r\n<li>You must write a formal article on the given topic in PDF format or in a maximum of 500 words.<br>\r\n<li>Need a resume mentioning the overall activities and participation in PDF or Word format.<br>\r\n<li>Submit articles and resumes via email while the subject line is called âKotzen Applicationâ.<br>\r\n<li>Each page of the document should include the studentâs full name and date of birth.', '1) Hit the below \" click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3) Email the necessary documents and essays<br>\r\n4) Submit', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\"]', '\"Bachelors\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-30', '2022-12-01', ' Simmons University', 163000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-30 10:19:38', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-30 04:55:04', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
