) Hit the below \" click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3) Register yourself on the UGC portal<br>\r\n4) Fill out the application and attach necessary documents<br>\r\n5) Submit', '', '[\"PHD\"]', '[\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"PHD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-01', '2022-10-10', 'Government of India', 35000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-09-30 11:40:17', 1, NULL, '2022-09-30 11:00:19', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
