(1341, 'XOs0d0ubtwvB9EYAxV', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Share Your Convocation Pictures', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/share-your-convocation-pictures/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship, Government of India hosted a convocation ceremony for the candidates in the skilling ecosystem, on Vishwakarma day which was held on the 17th of September.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li> To achieve PM Modiâs vision of âVikshit Bharatâ by the year 2047, skilling would play a pivotal role. Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship is making massive strides toward skilling the workforce in India and generating demand for the skilled workforce not only in the country but also in the international markets.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li> In this context, a competition calling for entries from people would seem relevant for creating and celebrating the skilled workforce of the nation<br><br>\r\n<b>Competition Guidelines:</b><br>\r\n\r\n1. The participants need to provide a picture in their convocation uniform in support of the ceremony with the hashtag #SkillKoSamman or #Respect4Skills<br><br>\r\n\r\n2. The participants should upload their entry as a high-quality picture file to social media platforms like Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\nThe top 5 (five) lucky draw entries will receive a souvenir.', '<li> Convocation picture', '1)Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2)Read the details of the competition carefully<br>\r\n3)Click on the \"log in to apply\" button<br>\r\n4)Submit your entry<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-30', '2022-10-31', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-01 12:28:01', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-01 07:00:40', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1342, 'iSSghcGZlN5C88XZPL', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Compose a Song for International Year of Millets 2023', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/compose-song-international-year-millets-2023-%E2%80%93-20/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Millets are a collective group of small-seeded annual grasses that are grown as grain crops, primarily on marginal land in dry areas of temperate, subtropical, and tropical regions. Climate Resilient Millets are grown in 131 countries. <br><br>\r\n<li>The U.N. General Assembly adopted a resolution, sponsored by India and supported by more than 70 countries, declaring 2023 as the International Year of Millets. <br><br>\r\n<li>The resolution is intended to increase public awareness of the health benefits of millets and their suitability for cultivation under tough conditions marked by climate change.<br><br>\r\n<li>Accordingly, showcasing the importance of millets and creating awareness in the masses towards it, MyGov along with the Ministry of Agriculture and Farmers Welfare is organizing a contest inviting songs on the importance of millets<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Guidelines:</b><br>\r\n1) Participants should upload their entry as a high-quality audio file to any media platform such as SoundCloud, YouTube, Dropbox, etc., and share the link in the description box.<br>\r\n2) Duration of the film should be 3 -5 minutes,<br>\r\n3) Each participant must submit a brief description (maximum 100 words) of the song.<br>\r\n4) The song should be distinctive and meaningful.<br>\r\n5) The song on millets should be usable on every platform of a government organization like radio, TV, conference, seminars, mela, etc.<br><br>\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\n\r\nâ¢ 1st Prize- Rs. 1,00,000/-<br>\r\nâ¢ 2nd Prize- 50,000/-<br>\r\nâ¢ 3rd Prize- 25,000/-<br>', '<li> The video has to be shot in HD format within the ratio of 16:9 in Horizontal format<br>\r\n <li>Brief description (maximum 100 words) of the song\r\n', '1) Click on the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the details of the competition carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on the \"log in to apply\" button<br>\r\n4) Submit your entry<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-30', '2022-11-19', 'Government of India', 100000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-01 12:57:58', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-01 09:40:42', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1343, 'f49ZgzfEEPLAVOR4TM', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Design a Mascot for Rural Postal Life Insurance ', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/design-mascot-postal-life-insurance-pli-rural-postal-life-insurance-rpli/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Postal Life Insurance (PLI) was introduced on 1st February 1884. It started as a welfare scheme for the benefit of postal employees and was later extended to the employees of the Telegraph Department in 1888. In 1894, PLI extended insurance cover to female employees of the erstwhile P & T Department at a time when no other insurance company covered female lives. It is the oldest life insurer in this country<br><br>\r\n<li>Rural Postal Life Insurance (RPLI) was introduced on 24.03.1995 for the rural populace of India. The prime objective of the scheme is to provide insurance cover to the rural public in general and to benefit weaker sections of rural areas and thereby contributing to the financial inclusion initiative of the Government of India.<br><br>\r\n<li>Department of Posts has tied up with MyGov for hosting a Contest for Designing a Mascot which will convey the basic objectives and how it encapsulates the essence of the program/mission of PLI/RPLI.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Guidelines:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li> The mascot should graphically convey the objectives of PLI/ RPLI<br>\r\n<li> Each entry must be accompanied by a brief description of the concept behind the design of the mascot and how it encapsulates the essence of the program/mission.<br>\r\n<li>File should be of high resolution â at least 1000 pixels per inch at 100% size.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Rewards </b> <br>\r\nA prize of Rs. 25,000 will be awarded to the winning design.', '<li>A high-resolution (600 dpi) image of the mascot in JPEG, PNG, BMP, and TIFF formats only <br>\r\n <li>The winner shall be required to provide the original open-source file of the designed Mascot <br>', '1) Click on the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the details of the competition carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on the \"log in to apply\" button<br>\r\n4) Submit your entry<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-30', '2022-10-11', 'Government of India', 25000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-01 14:20:53', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-06 06:16:31', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1344, 'gww9sTOmB3ERs4csyM', 'Competitions and Awards', 'STPI CoE-Kalpataru : Open Challenge Program ', 'https://innovate.stpinext.in/about-us/kalpataru', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Open Challenge Program (OCP) is a platform where a startup gets an opportunity to solve problems through innovative solutions. The objective of the Open Challenge Program (OCP) is to identify, recognize & reward aspiring and early-stage tech entrepreneurs. This platform facilitates aspiring entrepreneurs and innovators and their success through strategic networking, seed funding, mentoring, providing support for training, marketing, patenting, and access to the CoE labs, tools, software, and state-of-the-art incubation facility. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>To create a holistic eco-system for encouraging R&D, Innovation, and Entrepreneurship in the domain of Industry 4.0 i.e., Industrial IoT, Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, Augmented Reality, Virtual Reality, Industrial Automation, Industrial Robotics, Industrial Drone, Industrial 3D Printing, and other related technologies powered by AI were providing physical infrastructure and support services for prototyping, developing, testing & marketing through incubating start-ups in Industry 4.0.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>STPI is looking to identify and support promising startups working towards digital transformation products/solutions enabling equitable & inclusive growth of PSUs with a focus on Industry4.0. The selected startups would be given physical infrastructure, funding assistance, access to networks, connections, learning, and resources that are needed to build a scalable, profitable, and global business.<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<b>OBJECTIVES</b>\r\n\r\n<li> To promote innovation & entrepreneurship in Industry 4.0<br/><br/>\r\n<li>To stimulate the establishment & growth of technology-based innovators, researchers, entrepreneurs &start-ups in Industry 4.0 by providing necessary infrastructure, mentoring, marketing, funding, and overall eco-system interconnecting all stakeholders<br/><br/>\r\n<li> To help domestic start-ups in becoming global companies<br/><br/>\r\n<li>To generate employment opportunities and increase economic & social growth of the region as well as the country<br/><br/>\r\n<li>To create trained manpower on Industry4.0.<br/><br/>\r\n<li> To encourage the adoption & nurturing of Industry 4.0 by MSMEs<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<p style =\" color:perpole;\">WHO CAN APPLY</p><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>The eligibility criteria for a start-up to apply to the OCP program shall be as follows<br/><br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>The challenge invites proposals/applications from Indian Start-ups# who are working in a domain related to software product development<br/><br/>\r\n <li>Start-ups registered with DPIIT under the start-up India program are encouraged to participate in this program<br/><br/>\r\n<li>Individual Academicians, Researchers, Educators, Entrepreneurs, partnership firms, and LLPs may also participate, however, if they are selected then they will have to register as a private limited company in a stipulated time (preferably within 3 months).\r\n#At least 51% shareholding with Indian citizens or persons of Indian origin. The applicantâs entity should not be a subsidiary company of any foreign corporation<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>Note:</b> The Startups submitting the proposals/applications can be in any of the following stages<br/><br/>\r\n<li>Ideation Stage Start-up: An individual or team of individuals has an innovative product idea and wishes to focus on developing that idea into a business<br/><br/>\r\n<li>Validation Stage Start-up: A validated proof-of-concept exists in a way that the prototype is anticipated to be ready in the foreseeable future. Alternatively, the prototype is ready and awaiting testing and validation<br/><br/>\r\n<li>Early Traction Start-up: The product has been validated and the start-up needs support in establishing itself as a business<br/><br/>\r\n<li>Scaling Stage Start-up: The start-up has initial revenue from customers and needs support in scaling its business & product portfolio<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<p style =\"color:perpole;\">SELECTION PROCESS</p><br/>\r\n\r\n<b>Screening, Evaluation & Selection:<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>Designated Committee(s) shall be formed for Screening, Evaluation & Selection<br/><br/>\r\n<li>All the applications received shall be subject to a rigorous centralized multi-tier screening process with the involvement of appropriate experts from the respective domains as deemed fit<br/><br/>\r\n<li> Decision of the designated Committee(s) shall be final & binding on all<br/><br/>\r\n<li>After receiving the innovative ideas/solutions as per the prescribed format within the specified timeline a screening process will be done on the basis of relevancy. The relevant submissions will be shortlisted and called for selection through pitching/ Presentation\r\n<br/><br/>\r\n<hr>\r\n<b>FINANCIAL INCENTIVES<br/></b>\r\n\r\n<li>Project funds for each problem statement (Sl. 1 to 6) will be provided by RINL-VSP to the selected startups in four installments based on the progress of the project.<br/><br/>\r\n<li> A seed funding of options. <b>4.00 Lakhs</b> will be provided through Financial Institution for each beneficiary(physically incubated) /supported Start-ups selected through OCP based on innovative ideas, novel solutions, strong team & sound business proposal<br/><br/>\r\n<li> Disbursal of seed funds to Startups will be based on milestones achieved, periodic review, and recommendations<br/><br/>\r\n<li> Cloud Credits from leading third-party service providers<br/>\r\n ', 'ID proof ', '1)Click on the below\"click here to apply button\"<br/>\r\n2)Read the details of the competition carefully<br/>\r\n3)Click on the \"log in to apply button\"<br/>\r\n4)Submit your entry<br/>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-10', '2022-10-19', 'STPI CoE-Kalpataru', 400000.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-10-03 09:43:05', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-10-03 04:31:45', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1345, 'knZotQUip45VXqF3nK', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Showcase Your Skills Competition', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/showcase-your-skills-competition/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1XxoRpHObHg', 'The Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship, Government of India has hosted a convocation ceremony for the candidates in the skilling ecosystem, on Vishwakarma day which was on the 17th of September.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>To achieve PM Modiâs vision of âVikshit Bharatâ by the year 2047, skilling would play a pivotal role. Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship is making massive strides toward skilling the workforce in India and generating demand for the skilled workforce not only in the country but also in the international markets.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The convocation ceremony was the first of many ceremonies to be done across the skilling institutes under the scheme.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>In this context, a competition calling for entries from people to showcase their skills would seem relevant for creating and celebrating the skilled workforce of the nation.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Categories for video submission:</b><br>\r\n\r\n1. Yoga Instructor<br>\r\n2. Mason Tiling<br>\r\n3. Medicinal Plants Grower<br>\r\n4. Mushroom Grower<br>\r\n5. Sericulturist<br>\r\n6. Beauty Therapist<br>\r\n7. Hair Stylist<br>\r\n8. Goldsmith<br>\r\n9. Bamboo Mat/Carpet Weaver<br>\r\n10. Handloom Weaver<br>\r\n11. Fashion Design and Technology<br>\r\n12. Computer Software Application<br>\r\n13. IoT Technician<br>\r\n14. Robot System Integration<br>\r\n15. Additive Manufacturing<br>\r\n16. Renewable Energy<br>\r\n17. Mobile Applications Development<br>\r\n18. Digital Construction<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\n\r\n5 entries will be selected, and the winner will be awarded a certificate and a souvenir courtesy of the Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship', 'The participants should upload their entry as a good-quality video file to any media platform such as YouTube, Google Drive, Dropbox, etc., and enter the publicly accessible link in the application.', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the guidelines carefully<br>\r\n3. Log in to the competition <br>\r\n4.  Submit your entry<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-20', '2022-10-31', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-03 10:22:18', 1, NULL, '2022-10-22 10:50:35', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1346, 'h9sIOyYqYuRcZdzBHH', 'Abroad', 'International Climate Protection Fellowships', 'https://www.humboldt-foundation.de/en/apply/sponsorship-programmes/international-climate-protection-fellowship', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'With the International Climate Protection Fellowships, the Alexander von Humboldt Foundation\r\nenables prospective leaders working practically to implement a research-based proposal in the\r\nfield of climate protection or climate-related resource conservation during a one-year stay in\r\nGermany.<br><br>\r\n<li>The global challenge posed by climate change can only be met by cross-border international\r\ncollaborations. By enabling future decision-makers and multipliers to share knowledge,\r\nmethods and techniques with specialist colleagues in Germany the program promotes this\r\nobjective, particularly by taking account of issues relating to practical applicability in the fellowsâ\r\nown countries<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Explore questions in the natural or engineering sciences or address legal, economic, health-related, or societal aspects of climate change<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li> Citizen of a non-European developing or transition country (see list of countries, PDF) and have been predominantly living and working there<br>\r\n<li>Have initial experience in a leadership role and corresponding leadership skills<br>\r\n<li>Have very good knowledge of English and/or German<br>', '<li>Research-based project<br>\r\n <li>An extensive statement including confirmation of support from your host in Germany<br>\r\n<li>Two letters of recommendation <br>', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the details carefully<br>\r\n3. Click on the \"apply now\" button<br>\r\n4. Fill out the form <br>                                                                                                                     \r\n5. Submit<br>', '', '[\"PHD\"]', '[\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"PHD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-01', '2023-02-01', 'Alexander von Humboldt Foundation', 200000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-03 11:40:41', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-03 06:13:31', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
