(1347, 'B4Xz2ZlpQdTtpp1PAX', 'Competitions and Awards', 'âDeshke Utsavâ', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/share-your-videos-showcasing-your-families-friends-or-other-groups-enjoying-festivals-and/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'âDeshke Utsavâ is an initiative by the Ministry of Tourism to work towards listings of Events and festivals along with Live Darshans of India. Under the Utsav campaign, the Ministry is sharing the gratitude and joy of festivals and events across the country. This can also help promote India\'s culture from metro to rural cities to get national recognition for their innovation and effort. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>In this way, #Desh ke Utsav is an initiative to spread awareness and take steps toward saving our culture and spread them across the country.\r\nThrough this contest, we invite you to share videos showcasing your families, friends, or other groups enjoying festivals and events.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<li>Ministry of Tourism encourages users to visit the Utsav platform/website, where users can find information about various events, and festivals and can watch real-time darshans across the nation https://utsav.gov.in/<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Guidelines:<br/></b>\r\n\r\n1. The video shall not be more than 2 Minutes(120 seconds), including the beginning and end credits.  <br/>\r\n\r\n2. Both color and monochrome videos in time-lapse/normal mode will be accepted<br/>\r\n\r\n3. Please ensure the films are shot in HD format and are in the ratio of 16:9 in Horizontal format<br/>\r\n\r\n4. Films shot using vertical formats like the ones shot on mobile phones will not be accepted<br/>\r\n\r\n5. One contestant may submit a maximum of 2 entries (An entry consisting of one video clip) in the competition<br/><br>\r\n\r\n<b> Note : </b> For more information regarding the competition click <b><a href=\"https://www.mygov.in/task/share-your-videos-showcasing-your-families-friends-or-other-groups-enjoying-festivals-and/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Reward :</b><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n1. 1st Prize : 3 nights-4 days Tour of Sikkim(Accommodation with meal+ Sightseeing)for the winner Plus one<br/>\r\n\r\n2. 2nd Prize : 3 nights-4 days Tour of Chennai and Puducherry(Accommodation+ Sightseeing) for the winner Plus one<br/>\r\n\r\n3. 3rd Prize : 2 nights-3 days Tour of Ajmer-Pushkar(Accommodation+ Sightseeing) for the winner Plus one<br/>', '<li>Video of a maximum duration of 2 minutes (120 seconds) along with a description of a maximum of 1000 words on any social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, or YouTube and share the publicly accessible link on MyGov to submit their entry by pasting the link there.', '1. Click on the below \"click here to apply \" button<br/>\r\n2. Click on \"Login to participate\"<br/>\r\n3. Fill up the form and attach the required documents correctly<br/>\r\n4. Submit<br/>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"\\\"\\\\\\\"All\\\\\\\"\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-09', '2022-10-31', 'Government of India ', 0.00, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-10-04 09:35:38', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-12-02 10:35:51', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1348, 'w5tRaUJiDBnAFMfskZ', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Fasal Bima Abhiyan Mein Mera Yogdaan - Selfie Competition', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/fasal-bima-abhiyan-mein-mera-yogdaan-selfie-competition/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'With the aim of promoting Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana (PMFBY) and engaging citizens across the country in the ongoing \'Out of Home\' campaign (OOH) / Outdoor campaign of the PMFBY, the Ministry of Agriculture and Farmers Welfare has organized Fasal Bima Abhiyan Mein Mera Yogdaan - Selfie Competition.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Citizens are invited to post geo-tagged/non-geo-tagged selfies using the PMFBY banner, hoarding, and other display advertisements, at public locations like CSC centers, Krishi Kendra, agriculture offices, banks, panchayat offices, petrol pumps, and highways in their village/block/district/state and upload them in the description box below.<br><br>\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n<li> The best 2 selfies will be awarded Rs.11000/- and Rs.7000/- respectively from each state and union territory.<br><br>\r\n<b>Guidelines:</b><br>\r\n<li>Each participant can submit up to two geo-tagged selfies only<br>\r\n<li>Submitted images can be in JPG, PNG, or .PDF format only.<br>\r\n<li>The entry must not contain any provocative, objectionable, or inappropriate content. <br>\r\n<li>Each image submitted must be original and Geo-tagged. Photoshopped or edited pictures/selfies\r\nwill not be accepted. ', 'Participants should only submit a geo-tagged selfie with a PMFBY banner, hoarding, and other\r\ndisplay advertisements at public sites like petrol pumps and highways of their district/\r\nblock/State. <br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> For more information click <b> <a href=\"https://www.mygov.in/task/fasal-bima-abhiyan-mein-mera-yogdaan-selfie-competition/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>\r\n', '1) Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the details of the competition carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on the \"log in to apply\" button<br>\r\n4) Submit your entry<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-27', '2022-10-20', 'Government of India', 11000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-04 10:14:03', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-06 05:30:52', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1349, 'Vp72PfC4tLQh4qk5ze', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Create a poster using Heart', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/create-poster-using-heart/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'On the occasion of World Heart Day i.e. 29th September 2022, the Ministry of Health & Family Welfare in collaboration with MyGov invites citizens to create an online Poster using hearts for creating awareness.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>This campaign aims to drive action to educate people by controlling risk factors by the use of tobacco and alcohol, unhealthy diet, and physical inactivity and minimizing premature deaths from heart diseases and stroke.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>The competition is open to all Indian citizens.<br>\r\n<li>Please note that the work must be original and should not violate any provision of the\r\nIndian Copyright Act, 1957.<br>\r\n<li>One participant can submit only one entry. <br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\nThe top 3 winners will get a certificate from the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Hand drawn/ sketch the poster on A3 or A4 pages or create it digitally\r\ndesigned posters through computer software as well<br>\r\n\r\nThe attachments must not exceed 2MB in size<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> For more details click <b> \r\n<a href=\"https://www.mygov.in/task/create-poster-using-heart/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></b>\r\n', '1) Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the details of the competition carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on the \"log in to apply\" button<br>\r\n4) Submit your entry<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-01', '2022-10-15', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-04 10:37:21', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-10 04:17:24', 1, '', '', '', '',