(1375, 'nPf53PWQbrEF0pMHVZ', 'Abroad', 'EWC  Fellowship', 'https://www.eastwestcenter.org/education/ewc-graduate-degree-fellowship', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The EWC Graduate Fellowship 2023 in the United States is a great opportunity for those students who want to study abroad and want to do their Masterâs and Ph.D. programs in universities of the USA<br><br>\r\n<li>All those students who have brilliant minds and excellent academic records should apply for the East-West centerâs scholarship program so that they can participate in the educational mission of working together in a diverse cultural environment and coordinating with each other in a global environment without any worry of finance<br><br>\r\n<li>This EWC scholarship in the USA proves very aimful and constructive to bring a positive change in Asia-Pacific communities by engaging and encouraging young and fresh, brilliant minds to build a network of hard-working and progressive pupils that are interested to build a team, could discuss cultural change openly, cultural exchange activities, education progression, community services socially along with the leadership development that can lead their communities in a better way.<br><br>\r\n<b> Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Applicant should have the nationality of United states, Pacific Region, South East Asia, South Asia, and East Asia.<br>\r\n<li>Applicant must have a 4year degree of Bachelor or equivalent degree from a US college or University.<br>\r\n<li>The applicant must have a 3.00 CGPA out of 4.00 CGPA in four semesters or 6 semesters in the Graduate degree or Post Graduate degree.<br><br>\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\n<li>The full tuition fee will be covered during the whole study program.<br>\r\n<li>Students will get free residency and a single residency room.<br>\r\n<li>All expenses of food and incidental chances will also be covered.<br>\r\n<li>Students will get all reading material and study-related grants