(1394, 'k8nBGee8A8YsVCBFOq', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Suggest a Slogan for Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav Souvenir', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/suggest-slogan-azadi-ka-amrit-mahotsav-souvenir/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav is an initiative of the Government of India to celebrate and commemorate 75 years of independence and the glorious history of its people, culture, and achievements. <br><br>\r\n<li>This Mahotsav is dedicated to the people of India who have not only been instrumental in bringing India this far in its evolutionary journey but also hold within them the power and potential to enable Prime Minister Narendra Modi\'s vision of activating India 2.0, fuelled by the spirit of Aatmanirbhar Bharat. <br><br>\r\n<li>The official journey of Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav commenced on 12th March 2021 which started a 75-week countdown to our 75th anniversary of independence and will end post a year on 15th August 2023.<br><br>\r\n<li>To celebrate the 75th year of Independence, as a tribute and love for the country every household should have a piece symbolizing this milestone moment. To enable this idea, a unique slogan for the same can be suggested.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>This initiative is run by the Government of India for Indian nationals to contribute to the thinking of a slogan for this movement of Azadi ka Amrit Mahotsav memorabilia/ souvenirs in every house. We are calling out talents to create a unique and catchy slogan for this milestone initiative that will reach millions of homes.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility</b>:<br>\r\n\r\n<li>All Indian citizens may participate.<br>\r\n<li> All entries/designs submitted under the campaign should be free of plagiarism and be the original work of\r\nthe person submitting the design.<br><br>\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Personalized participation digital certificate from the Ministry of Culture be given to winners.<br>\r\n<li>The top 10 entries will be given cash prizes of Rs 20,000 Each.', '', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the terms and conditions carefully<br>\r\n3. Click on the \"log in to participate\" button<br>\r\n4. Submit your entry', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-27', '2022-11-15', 'Government of India', 20000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-29 11:04:12', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-29 05:36:43', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
