(1396, 'OrqRMdXKO1H2r0DXFQ', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Vande Bharatam Nritya Utsav 2023', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/vande-bharatam-nritya-utsav-2023/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Vande Bharatam - Nritya Utsav, an all-India dance competition is an initiative taken by the Ministry of Culture as part of Republic Day Celebrations 2023 and under the aegis of Azadi ka Amrit Mahotsav to work towards promoting the spirit of \'Jan Bhagidari\', while also showcasing India\'s vibrancy through its dance.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The competition is a one-of-a-kind campaign that will be held for the second time, giving top dancing talent from across the country the opportunity to perform at the Republic Day Parade in 2023. The competition will be held at the state and zonal level and will culminate with the grand finale on 18th December 2022 in New Delhi.<br><br>\r\n<b> Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Participants must be between the age group of 17-30 years.<br>\r\n<li> Performance video should not exceed 3 minutes.<br>\r\n<li>Participants can send the video as an individual or as a group of 2-10 members.<br>\r\n<li> Dance genres - <br>Classical/folk/tribal/contemporary/fusion.<br>\r\n\r\n', '<li>One Single File including the application form and age proof to be attached which should\r\nnot be more than 2 MB.<br>\r\n<li>The link to the dance video must be put in the description box <br> ', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the terms and conditions carefully<br>\r\n3. Click on the \"log in to participate\" button<br>\r\n4. Submit your entry', ' Perform at Republic Day Celebrations 2023', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-25', '2022-11-04', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-31 09:41:16', 1, NULL, '2022-10-31 04:11:16', 1