(1397, 'pbeLEGsxxlztPReLAn', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Meri Policy Mere Haath Photography competition', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/meri-policy-mere-haath-photography-competition/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9-qQLFoDRD4', 'Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana (PMFBY) aims to support sustainable production in the agriculture sector by way of :<br>\r\n1. Provide financial support to farmers.<br>\r\n2. Stabilizing the income of farmers.<br>\r\n3. Encouraging farmers to adopt innovative and modern agricultural practices,<br>\r\n4. Ensuring the flow of credit to the agriculture sector; which will contribute to food security, crop diversification, and enhancing growth and competitiveness of the agriculture sector besides protecting farmers from production risks.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The goal of this activity âMeri Policy Mere Haathâ is to engage citizens across the country in the PMFBY\'s Campaign. Citizens are expected to take a photo/selfie with a farmer who receives the policy document as part of the \"Meri Policy, Mere Haath\" campaign in their village, block, district, and state (or UT) and upload it to the MyGov activity page.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Participants should only submit a selfie with the PMFBY beneficiaries from their district/ block/State<br>\r\n<li>Clearly visible distanced selfies will also be accepted.<br>\r\n<li>Only color geo-tagged photos/selfies will be accepted<br>\r\n', '<li>Geo-tagged photos/selfies (maximum 10MB in size<br>\r\n<li>Submitted images can be in JPG, PNG or. PDF format only<br>', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the terms and conditions carefully<br>\r\n3. Click on the \"log in to participate\" button<br>\r\n4. Submit your entry', ' Amplified on Social media portals.', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"\\\"All\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-25', '2022-11-18', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-31 09:56:53', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-11-24 04:00:01', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1398, '96Ts05W1iheJHphF64', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Suggest a slogan competition for Krishi Karmyogi Abhiyan', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/suggest-slogan-competition-krishi-karmyogi-abhiyan/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The Department of Agriculture and Framers\' Welfare has taken various initiatives for capacity building of all department officers under the \"Mission Karmyogi\" program in collaboration with the Capacity Building Commission. The Mission\'s goal is to build a \"citizen-centric, future-ready civil service with the right attitudes, skills, and knowledge aligned with the vision of a New India.\"<br><br>\r\n<li>The Department of Agriculture, in collaboration with MyGov, is holding a design Slogan competition in which people are encouraged to submit creative and unique Slogans for the \"Krishi Karmyogi Abhiyan.\"<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The goal of this competition is to raise awareness among the general public about the \"Krishi Karamyogi Abhiyaan,\" which not only raises awareness but also allows people to connect with farmers.<br><br>\r\n<b>Guidelines for participants:</b><br>\r\n<li> Participants have to share a slogan that should depict agriculture and related themes.<br>\r\n<li> In case of uploading the Slogan on media platforms such as Sound Cloud, YouTube, Google Drive, Dropbox, etc., and any social media platform, then the participant has to share the link in the submission box.<br>\r\n\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the terms and conditions carefully<br>\r\n3. Click on the \"log in to participate\" button<br>\r\n4. Submit your entry', 'E â Certificate ', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-25', '2022-11-15', 'Government of India', 11000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-10-31 11:0