(1400, 'MKzQHz2wZuiVY8JqfP', 'Abroad', 'Tsinghua University CSC Scholarship', 'https://yz.tsinghua.edu.cn/en/info/1027/1117.htm3.4233', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Applications are invited to apply for the Tsinghua University CSC Scholarship 2023 in China. All International Students from all over the world are eligible to apply for the Chinese Government Scholarship (CGS) 2023 at Tsinghua University. <br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Students who want to study for their Bachelor\'s Degree, Masters\'s Degree, or Ph.D. Degrees are encouraged to apply. <br><br>\r\n<li>There is no need for IELTS to apply for this scholarship. Fully Funded Scholarships are available for the academic session of 2023-24. <br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Non-Chinese Nationals with any nationality are eligible to apply.<br>\r\n<li>Must be in good health (Mentally and Physically).\r\n<li>Currently, the candidate must not be enrolled in any Chinese University.<br>\r\n<li>The applicant who is applying for a Masterâs Degree Must have a Bachelorâs Degree and the age should be under 35.<br>\r\n<li>The applicant who is applying for a Doctoral Degree Must have a Masterâs Degree and the age should be under 40.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\n<li>Covers complete tuition fee<br>\r\n<li>Free Accommodation will be given on Campus.<br>\r\n<li>Comprehensive Medical Insurance.<br>\r\n<li>Monthly Stipend:<br>\r\nMasters\' Degree:  3,000 Yuan<br>\r\nDoctoral Degree: 3,500 Yuan<br>', '<li>Personal statement<br>\r\n<li>Previous Degree certificate<br>\r\n<li>Academic Transcript<br>\r\n<li>Two academic Recommendation Letters<br>\r\n<li>Passport personal information page<br>', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit', '', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\",\"Masters (All)\",\"PHD (All)\"]', '\"Bachelors, Masters, PhD\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-01', '2023-01-10', ' Tsinghua University', 39000.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-11-03 09:47:18', 1, NULL, '2022-11-03 04:17:18', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
