(1403, 'Z8yJ5htbQcjNvUEYQs', 'Abroad', 'ANSO Scholarship for Young Talents ', 'http://www.anso.org.cn/programmes/talent/scholarship/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Applications are invited to apply for the ANSO Scholarship for Young Talents 2023 in China. All International Students from all over the world are eligible to apply for ANSO Scholarships 2023-2024. <br><br>\r\n<li>Students who want to pursue their Masters\'s Degree or Doctoral Degree from China are encouraged to apply. <br><br>\r\n<li>200 Masters and 300 Ph.D. Fully Funded Scholarships will be given every year by ANSO.\r\ne scholarship will cover all the expenses.<br><br>\r\n<li> The scholarship duration for Masters\'s degree is 3 Years while its 4 Years for a Ph.D. degree<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Applicant must be Non-Chinese<br>\r\n<li>Masterâs Degree applicant must be born after 1 January 1993 (inclusive)<br>\r\n<li>Ph.D. Degree applicant must be born after 1 January 1988 (inclusive)<br>\r\n<li>International students must fulfill the criteria of USTC/UCAS<br>\r\n<li>Not take up other assignments during the period of his/her scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>Be proficient in English or Chinese.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\n<li>Complete Tuition Fee Waiver<br>\r\n<li>Application Fee Waiver<br>\r\n<li>Monthly Stipend:<br>\r\n<li>Masterâs Degree: 3000 RMB/month<br>\r\n<li>Ph.D. Degree: 6000 or 7000 RMB/month<br>\r\n<li>Health Insurance<br>\r\n<li>Travel Subsidies from their Home Countries to China<br>', '<li>Copy of Passport having at least 2 years validity\r\n<li>Updated CV with a brief introduction of research experience<br>\r\n<li>Copy of Original Degree certificates<br>\r\n<li>Two Reference Letters<br>\r\n<li>Research Proposal<br>\r\n<li>Photocopies of 5 published academic papers (if available)<br>\r\n<li>Proof of English and/or Chinese Language Proficiency<br>\r\n<li>Foreigner Physical Examination Form<br>', '1. Hit the