lowing address either by speed post or email courier with all the necessary\r\nenclosures:<br>\r\n<p style=\"color:blue;\">The Secretary, <br>\r\nSiddhartha Foundation,<br>\r\nC/o Siddhartha Academy of General & Technical Education,<br>\r\nSiddhartha Nagar,<br>\r\n Vijayawada 520 010<br>\r\nAndhra Pradesh.</p><br>\r\n<b>OR</b><br>\r\ne-mail address: <p style=\"color:blue;\"><a href=mailto:\"siddhartha.academy@yahoo.in\">siddhartha.academy@yahoo.in</a>\r\n', '1) Hit the below \"Click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2) Read the scholarship guidelines carefully<br>\r\n\r\n3) Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4) Send out the application form<br>', '', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"Bachelors (All)\"]', '\"Undergraduates\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 25000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-01', '2022-12-31', 'Siddharth Foundation', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-11-09 12:01:04', 1, 'prajwitagadade@triwits.com', '2022-11-24 03:48:57', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1417, 'F74pkrnclv0WVRsldM', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Design a logo of \'Stay Safe Online\' Campaign', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/design-logo-stay-safe-online-campaign/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'India will assume the Presidency of the G20 for one year from 01 December 2022 to 30 November 2023. The G20, or Group of Twenty, is an intergovernmental forum of the worldâs major developed and developing economies<br><br>\r\n<li>During Indiaâs presidency of G20, the Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology (MeitY) is running a campaign titled âStay Safe Onlineâ aimed at creating awareness among citizens to stay safe in an online world on the widespread use of social media platforms and rapid adoption of digital payments.<br><br>\r\n<li>As India is making significant efforts towards becoming a trillion-dollar digital economy, the campaign focuses on sensitizing users of all ages about online risk & safety measures and promoting cyber hygiene thereby reinforcing the cyber safety of citizens<br><br>\r\n<li>Citizens of all age groups, covering rural and urban areas, with special emphasis on children, students, women, teachers, faculty, senior citizens, Government officials of Central & State Ministries/Departments, etc. are invited to participate in the Stay Safe Online campaign.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>The contest is open to Indian citizens only.<br>\r\n<li> One entry from one participant is only accepted.<br>\r\n<li>The entry must not contain any provocative, objectionable, or inappropriate content<br>\r\n<li>Plagiarism of any nature would not be allowed.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2. Read the terms and conditions carefully<br>\r\n3. Click on the \"log in to participate\" button<br>\r\n4. Submit your entry<br>', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'nu