(1425, 'aOJQdxH1svxKAKtaYo', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Rashtriya Ekta Diwas Quiz', 'https://quiz.mygov.in/quiz/rashtriya-ekta-diwas-quiz/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'The idea of a sustained and structured cultural connection between people of different regions was mooted by Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi\r\nduring the Rashtriya Ekta Divas held on 31st October 2015.<br><br> \r\n\r\n<li> The Bharat program aims to enhance interaction & promote mutual understanding between people of different states/UTs through the concept of\r\nstate/UT pairing. <br><br> \r\n<li> The states carry out activities to promote a sustained and structured cultural connection in the areas of language learning, culture,\r\ntraditions & music, tourism & cuisine, sports, and sharing of best practices, etc.<br><br> \r\n<li> As a part of âEk Bharat Shrestha Bharatâ, the Department of Higher Education, Ministry of Education, Government of India is conducting Rashtriya Ekta Diwas Quiz to commemorate the birth anniversary of Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel and celebrate the cultural diversity of our country.<br><br> \r\n<b>Guidelines:</b><br>\r\n<li> Entry to the Quiz is open to all Indian citizens.<br> \r\n\r\n<li>  The Participant shall abide by all the rules and regulations of participating in the Quiz from time to time.<br> \r\n\r\n<li> This is a timed quiz with 10 questions to be answered in 450 seconds.<br> \r\n\r\n<li>  Certificates will be issued to all the participants.<br> \r\n\r\n<li>  There will be no negative marking for the incorrect answer.<br> \r\n\r\n <li> All Indian Citizens are eligible to participate.<br> \r\n\r\n<li>  An individual can participate only once in the quiz.<br> \r\n\r\n<li> The questions will be randomly picked from the question bank through an automated process.<br> \r\n\r\n\r\n', '', '1) Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the terms and conditions of the Competitions carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on \"Login to participate\"<br>\r\n4) Submit your entry.<br>', 'e-Certification and social media announcement', '[\"All\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-20', '2022-11-30', 'Government of India', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-11-22 09:56:35', 1, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-11-25 06:33:34', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1426, 'yOZ4lhnd9pT3P7vF6x', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Logo Competition for Mega Food Event 2023', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/logo-competition-mega-food-event-2023/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'As year 2023 has been declared as the International Year of Millets, Ministry of Food Processing Industries is organizing a Mega Food Event 2023 in October with a focus on Millets. <br><br>\r\n<li>In order to make this event more successful and increase in coverage via participation in the contest and for its wider reach, MoFPI along with MyGov is organizing a Logo Competition for Mega Food Event 2023.<br><br>\r\n<b>Guidelines:</b><br>\r\n<li>All entries must be submitted at mygov.in before 20th December 2022. No offline/manual proposal shall be accepted.<br>\r\n<li>Each participant has to submit a brief description of the logo in Hindi or English along with the image. <br>\r\n<li>The participant should make sure that his/her MyGov profile is accurate and updated since the MoFPI would be using this for further communication. \r\nThis includes details such as name, photo, complete postal address, and email id and phone number. Entries with incomplete profiles would not be considered. Participant & profile owner should be same.<br>\r\n<li>Multiple submissions by the same participant would not be considered.<br>\r\n<li>Entries must be submitted as JPEG files.\r\n For quality reproduction purposes, the winning entry must later be submitted in scalable vector graphic format (EPS).<br>\r\n <li>The logo must be easy to use, handle, resize, and manipulate for all reproduction purposes.', '', '1) Click on the below\"click here to apply\" button<br>\r\n2) Read the terms and conditions of the Competitions carefully<br>\r\n3) Click on \"Login to participate\"<br>\r\n4) Submit your entry.', '', '[\"All\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00