(1446, 'rXrEXTSlzq0b0yr87D', 'Abroad', 'University of Pecs Hungarian Scholarships', 'https://international.pte.hu/stipendium-hungaricum-scholarship-program', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Applications are invited to apply for the University of Pecs Hungarian Scholarships 2023-24 in Hungary. <br><br>\r\n<li>All International Students from all over the world are eligible to apply for Stipendium Hungaricum Scholarships at the University of Pecs. <br><br>\r\n<li>Students who want to study for their Undergraduate Degree, Masters\'s Degree, or Ph.D. Degrees are encouraged to apply. <br><br>\r\n<li>No Need for IELTS to apply. The government of Hungary is offering 5,000 Fully Funded Scholarships to all students around the world for the academic session of 2023-2024<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>All International Students (Non-Hungarian citizens) are eligible to apply.<br>\r\n<li>Candidate must be physically and mentally fit.<br>\r\n12 years school certificate is required to apply for a bachelor\'s Degree Program.<br>\r\n<li>To apply for Masters\'s Degree, applicants must hold a bachelor\'s degree.<br>\r\n<li>For a doctoral degree, Masters\'s degree certificate is required.<br>\r\n<li>If your previous degree instructions language was English then, you can submit English Proficiency Certificate from the previous institute.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Reward:</b><br>\r\n<li>All students will be exempted from the Tuition Fee.<br><br>\r\nMonthly stipend:<br>\r\n<li>Non-degree, Bachelor, Master, and one-tier master level: monthly HUF 43,700 contribution to the living expenses, for 12 months a year, until the completion of studies.<br>\r\n<li>Ph.D. level: monthly HUF 140000 for 12 months a year, until the completion of studies.<br>\r\n', '<li>Details & Updated Resume (CV)<br>\r\n<li>Degree Certificates<br>\r\n<li>Academic Transcripts<br>\r\n<li>Recommendation Letters<br>\r\n<li>Statement of Purpose<br>\r\n<li>Research Proposal (graduat