(1458, 'hHbyDUjlqcNIqHf0Qw', 'Scholarship', 'INLAKS Shivdasani fellowship', 'https://www.inlaksfoundation.org/inlaks-shivdasani-fellowship-for-social-engagement/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/@TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'Due to economic pressure, the norm in India is for young graduates to join the workforce immediately, which inhibits sufficient self-exploration and often leaves young people with little space to develop critical thinking and a broader view of the world. This impedes many talented individuals from engaging with society in a meaningful way.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The Inlaks Shivdasani Fellowship for Social Engagement will give graduates and early to mid-career professionals the confidence and security to explore alternatives and make independent choices about their lives while contributing to social change. <br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The fellowship will give young people the opportunity to work with a mentor of their choice and involve themselves in a process where knowledge drives social change. <br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>The work pursued may take many forms, including action-oriented research, cause lawyering, grassroots journalism, ecological efforts, minority rights, public health, archiving, reviving, or reporting on dying arts, culture, language, etc.<br><br>\r\n<b>Elgibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Graduates (applicants must not have attained the age of 30 years as of 5.1.2023 )<br>\r\n<li>Early to mid-career professionals (applicants must not have attained the age of 35 years as of 5.1.2023 and must have at least 3 years of relevant work experience)<br>\r\n<li>The applicant for this award must be an Indian passport holder, currently resident in India.<br>\r\n<li>Those enrolled in academic studies/Ph.D. for the duration of the fellowship are not eligible to apply.\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>Work Plan<br>\r\n<li>Statement of Purpose<br>\r\n<li>Letter of Endorsement from the Mentor <br>\r\n<li>Letter of Recommendation<br>\r\n<li>Resume<br>', '1) Hit the below \"Click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n\r\n2) Read the scholarship guidelines carefully<br>\r\n3) Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4) Submit the application', '45000/month', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-12-05', '2023-01-05', 'INLAKS SHIVDASANI FOUNDATION', 0.00, 'gautamitimmapur@triwits.com', '2022-12-09 10:43:21', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-20 12:24:56', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
