(1492, '1EAyPdUF7n2MQZHnQV', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Compose a Jingle Contest for Republic Day 2023', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/compose-jingle-contest-republic-day-2023/', ' Awareness making contests,Contests for all citizen of India,contest,competitions, Music Contests Online, Music compose contest online, free competitions, contest, cash prize, win cash prize, contest reward, competitions, free competitions, Free Contest, Contesting, Online competitions, Government of India Scholarship, Scholarship, Scholarship for all, Government Scholarship\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Contest for Republic Day 2023 - My Gov Contests', 'MyGov is inviting citizens to compose a jingle for Republic Day 2023 | There will be 3 cash prizes | Technical Parameters |  How To Apply', 'Compose Contest for Republic Day', '', 'Ministry of Defence in collaboration with MyGov is inviting citizens to compose a jingle for Republic Day 2023. The Jingle should be apt, relevant, and appealing. It should endeavour to drive a sense of pride & patriotism amongst citizens of all ages. <br>\r\n<li>It should highlight & showcase the importance of Republic Day and imbibe an understanding of the fundamental duties one has towards the country. It must focus on encouraging people to participate in the celebrations of Republic Day with their family and friends. <br>\r\n<li>It may cover aspects like the importance of Republic Day, gratitude to honour the armed forces or significant developments of the country in the past 74 years since being declared a Republic.<br>\r\n <br><br>\r\n<b>Technical Parameters</b><br>\r\n <li>Participants need to provide a script and a jingle of 25-30 seconds, that is easily understandable, is peppy, and connects with the public at large.<br>\r\n<li>The participants should upload their entry as a high-quality audio file on any media platform, such as SoundCloud, YouTube, Google Drive, Dropbox, etc. and enter the publicly accessible link in the comments section.<br>\r\n<li>The script also nee