(1494, 'iTvGbZpT0GNQAl44y6', 'Scholarship', 'Indira Gandhi Girls scholarship ', 'https://scholarships.gov.in/fresh/newstdRegfrmInstruction', 'Scholarship for women, Women empowerment, Single girl child compensate, PG Scholarship scheme, step by step procedure, apply to scholarship, scholarship program, scholarship opportunities, scholarship online, scholarship application, higher education scholarship, scholarship registration, masters scholarships, free scholarships, masters funding, Postgraduate Scholarships, M.tech scholarship, M.E Scholarship, M.Arch Scholarship, M.Pharm Scholarship, Master of technology Scholarship, Master of Engineering Scholarship, Master of pharmacy Scholarship, Master of Architecture Scholarship, Student scholarship, Scholarships, Engineering scholarships, scholarship for student, study grants, Student financial aid, Student funding, Masters scholarships, Technology scholarships, grants for college, scholarship programs, fully funded scholarships, free scholarships, Scholarship 2022, scholarships for college, scholarships for graduate students, scholarships for students, Professional Masters Degree Scholarship, Indira Gandhi scholarship for single girl child', 'Indira gandhi scholarship for single girl child- government of India', 'Post-Graduate Indira Gandhi Scholarship for Single Girl Child 2022-23 is an initiative for girl students up to 30 years of age to promote girl education. Eligibility..', 'Indira Gandhi Scholarship', '', 'Post-Graduate Indira Gandhi Scholarship for Single Girl Child 2022-23 is an initiative for girl students up to 30 years of age who is the only girl child in their family. The scholarship is offered by the University Grants Commission (UGC), Ministry of Human Resource Development, Government of India. The scholarship aims to promote girl education and compensate for the direct costs of girl education at all levels. The selected candidates will receive INR 36,200 per annum for a period of two years.\r\n<br><br>\r\n