(1502, 'CCla8cpNUhNGihTumA', 'Scholarship', 'All India Scholarship Entrance Examination ', 'https://www.aisee.co.in/', 'online scholarship test, free scholarship test, scholarship test for class 12, Scholarship for Class 11 and Class 12, Scholarship for Class 11 Students, Scholarship for Class 12 Students, Class 11 and Class 12 Scholarships, student scholarship, student financial aid, grants for college, scholarship 2022, apply for scholarships, Scholarships, free scholarships to apply for, free online scholarship, free scholarship in india, find a scholarship, best scholarships for indian students, new scholarship, all india scholarship, scholarship after 12th, All India Scholarship Entrance Examination ', 'Free online scholarship test- All India Scholarship Entrance Exam', 'AISEE is the online exam/offline exam for students of the less income family who had passed the 12th std or appeared as candidates for pursuing medical or engineering programs.', 'All India Scholarship Entrance Examination', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vp84OU1ptO4', 'AISEE is conducting the online exam/offline exam for students of the less-income family who had passed the 12th standard or appeared as candidates from a recognized board in different parts of India for pursuing medical or engineering programs.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>AISEE Scholarship started in 2013 in the southern part of India to improve the quality of study of the student by helping them in their educational environment. <br><br>\r\n<li>The main aim of the organization is to motivate the talent of India.AISEE provides a maximum number of talented students of Engineering aspired or medical aspired student gets enrolled in the medical scholarship exam or an engineering scholarship exam.\r\n <br><br>\r\n \r\n<b>\r\nEligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Any 12th passed out or appearing candidate from a recognized board whose appearing this year or passed a year in 2014 and onwards is eligible.<br><br>\r\n<b>Selection Procedure</b><br>\r\n<l