(1508, 'ZLPyKs6pCEaQs2tSFC', 'Scholarship', 'National Scholarship for Higher Education', 'https://scholarships.gov.in/fresh/schemeSelRegfrmInstruction', 'national scholarship apply, national scholarship scheme, national scholarship program, national scholarship form, national scholarship portal registration, national scholarship portal list, national scholarship portal eligibility, nsp national scholarship, scholarship for post graduate students in india, Scholarship for pg nsp national scholarship portal, nsp scholarship details, last date of national scholarship portal, bachelor scholarships, technology scholarships, b tech scholarship, engineering scholarships, study grants, student funding, scholarship programs, fully funded scholarships, undergraduate scholarships, free scholarships, the global scholarship, best scholarship website, scholarships for indian students, financial help for students, student scholarship, student financial aid, grants for college, apply for scholarships, Scholarships, free scholarships to apply for, free online scholarship, scholarships for online courses, apply for scholarships online for free, scholarships for students, free scholarship, apply for college scholarships, graduate student scholarships, apply for scholarship college  scholarships for me, scholarship website, best scholarship websites, scholarship search, scholarship for indian students, university scholarship, free scholarship in india, find a scholarship, best scholarships for indian students, new scholarship, all india scholarship, scholarship after 12th', 'National Scholarship  Scheme For Higher Education | UG & PG', 'A new scheme has been launched by the Ministry of ribal Affairs to provide financial assistance among the ST category students to pursue higher education..', 'National Scholarship for Higher Education', '', 'A new scheme has been launched by the Ministry of Tribal Affairs to provide financial assistance among the <b>ST category students</b> so that they would be able to pursue higher education without thinking about any financial hurdles. <br><br>\r\n<li>Under this scheme, the scholarship amount will be given to the student for their day-to-day expenses while studying. <br><br>\r\n<li>The main aim of launching this scheme is to provide a better future to the students of rural areas so they will be able to stand on their own feet.<br><br> <li>This scholarship is provided to the ST category student so that they will be able to pursue professional courses at graduation and post-graduation level\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Should be a citizen of India>\r\n<li>Have completed 10th  with 50%<br>\r\n<li>Have completed 12th with 50 %<br>\r\n<li>Applicant  should be  admitted to the institution identified by the Ministry of Tribal Affairs.<br>\r\n<li>\r\nThe annual family income of the student should be less than 6 lakhs<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits: </b><br>\r\n<li>Full tuition fee assistance of Rs. 2.5 lakh per annum will be given under this scholarship. <br>\r\n<li>Rs. 3,000 per annum will be given to the student for books and stationery.<br>\r\n<li> Rs. 2,200 per annum with a mixed ceiling of Rs. 26,400 per annum will be given as living expenses.<br>\r\n<li> Rs. 45,000 will be provided as one-time assistance for computer and accessories<br><br>', '1) Applicant Photo<br>\r\n2) Proof of Identity.<br>\r\n3) Proof of Address.<br>\r\n4) Proof of Income.<br>\r\n5) Student Bank passbook/Kiosk.<br>\r\n6) 10th, 12th and latest Marksheet.<br>\r\n7) Current year fee receipt.<br>\r\n8) Admission Letter / Bonafide certificate from institute.<br>\r\n9) Latest College Marksheets (Except first-year students).<br>\r\n10) All documents uploaded shall be clear and must be in a .jpeg .png file only.<br>\r\n<li>Optional document<br>\r\n<li>PAN No/Domicile certificate<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessa