(1509, '3a3xKx9MrBQiXrvqje', 'Competitions and Awards', 'GCSP Prize for Transformative Futures in Peace and Security ', 'https://www.gcsp.ch/events/apply-2023-gcsp-prize-transformative-futures-peace-and-security', 'Geneva Centre for Security Policy, GCSP, global security, ', 'GCSP 2023 Prize for Transformative Futures in Peace & Security ', 'Applications may come from any country, but the potential impact of the concepts submitted should extend beyond national borders in their scope or thinkings', 'GCSP Prize-Peace and Security', '', 'Under the leadership of Ambassador Thomas Greminger, Director of the GCSP, the Prize for Transformative Futures in Peace and Security was initiated by Professor Nayef Al-Rodhan, Head of the Geopolitics and Global Futures Programme, and Ms Anne-Caroline Pissis Martel, Head of the Global Fellowship Initiative and Creative Spark.<br><br>\r\n<li> It seeks to reward groundbreaking concepts that offer exceptional promise in addressing peace and security challenges. The inaugural edition of the prize will be awarded in 2023.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<li>Applications may come from any country, but the potential impact of the concepts submitted should extend beyond national borders in their scope or thinking. <br><br>\r\n<li>Concepts from a wide variety of fields may be eligible for consideration, including, but not restricted to, transformative technologies, pandemics, biothreats, autonomous weapons, climate change, human rights, cybersecurity, education, or disarmament, for example.<br><br>\r\n<b>\r\n<li>The winners will be announced in late May 2023<br><br>\r\nBenefits:</b><br>\r\n<li>The winners (first, second and third place) will be announced publicly during an event to be held in late May 2023. <br><br>\r\n<li>The prize for the application coming in the first position is a fully funded 2-month incubation program within the GCSPâs Creative Spark in Geneva (worth CHF 15â000) and a certificate of excellence. <br><br>\r\n<li>The two other finalist applications will receive a certificate of recognition.\r\n <br><br>\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'CHF 15000', '[\"Bachelors\"]', 'null', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-12-14', '2023-03-27', 'GCSP', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-07 15:34:56', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-04 07:24:42', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1510, 'Zqm7uOVfJe2QrQL8ZX', 'Scholarship', 'Swami Vivekananda  Scholarship', 'https://svmcm.wbhed.gov.in/page/application_procedure.php  ', 'vivekananda scholarships, merit scholarship, nmms scholarship district merit scholarship, national merit scholarships, meritcum means scholarship, merit based scholarships, merit based, state merit scholarship, swami vivekananda merit come means scholarship, merit awards, merit money, merit come means scholarship, merit student, university merit scholarship, national means kam merit scholarship, post graduate merit scholarship, swami vivekananda mcm scholarship, junior merit scholarship, merit aid, Diploma Scholarship, ITI Scholarship, College Scholarship, B.tech scholarship, Student scholarship, Scholarships, Engineering scholarships, scholarship for student, study grants, Student financial aid, Student funding, Bachelor scholarships, Technology scholarships, grants for college, scholarship programs, fully funded scholarships, undergraduate scholarships, free scholarships, apply for scholarships, Scholarship for ITI Students, Scholarship for Diploma Students, Scholarship for College Of Engineering Students, Study Reward for B. tech students , Bachelor of Technology scholarship, Scholarship for bachelor of technology student, High reward scholarship, Best scholarship website, higher education scholarship, scholarship registration, masters scholarships, free scholarships, masters funding, Postgraduate Scholarships, M.tech scholarship, M.E Scholarship, M.Arch Scholarship, M.Pharm Scholarship, Master of technology Scholarship, Master of Engineering Scholarship, Master of pharmacy Scholarship, Master of Architecture Scholarship, Student scholarship, Scholarships, Engineering scholarships, scholarship for student, study grants, Student financial aid, Student funding, Masters scholarships, Technology scholarships, grants for college', 'Meritcum means scholarship for every student of West Bengal ', 'Government of West Bengal provides financial assistance to all those who are suffering from the financial crisis despite not being able to pursue further studies.', 'Swami Vivekananda Merit Scholarship', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BTXNgLD6a7Q', 'The scholarship is named after the Indian Hindu monk and philosopher Vivekananda, which was started by the Government of West Bengal, to provide financial assistance to all those who are suffering from the financial crisis despite not being able to pursue further studies.<br><br>\r\n<li>The government of West Bengal has taken initiative and announced the Swami Vivekananda Scholarship 2023 for meritorious students from economically backward sections of the state. <br><br>\r\n<li>This scholarship program is basically applicable to <b>higher secondary and undergraduate/postgraduate students</b> by providing financial aid with this scholarship program a plethora of students are getting help in their studies and they are forwarding their goals ahead.<br><br>\r\n<li>Swami Vivekananda Merit-cum-Means Scholarship which is shortly known as SVMCM and popularly known as Bikash Bhavan Scholarship is applicable to all the students who are eligible to participate in it.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li> Must be a resident of West Bengal <br><br>\r\n<li>For the Swami Vivekananda Scholarship of Class 11 or Upper Secondary Level, the applicant must have passed the Madhyamik Pariksha or the equivalent exam with 75%.<br><br>\r\n<li>Undergraduate Students need to obtain 75% in class For the postgraduate level, the candidate must have scored at least 53% (for general education), and 55% (in the case of engineering) in graduation.<br><br>\r\n<li>For the diploma (polytechnic level), one should have a Madhyamik Pariksha or equivalent passed certificate with 75% of the course marks leading to the first-year diploma.<br><br>\r\n<li>Upper secondary exam passed or equivalent with at least 75% of the marks for the 2-year diploma in Modern Office Practice and Management, Pharmacy, 3D Animation, and Graphics are applicable to participate in this scholarship program.<br><br>\r\n<li>For the Kanyashree candidate (K3 component), students must receive a valid sanctioned K2 ID card, scholars must take a PG course in arts, science, and business, and students must have graduated with a 45%.<br><br>\r\n<li>For this Swami Vivekananda Scholarship, the income certificate is very important. The studentâs annual family income should be less than 2.5 lakhs.<br><br>\r\n<b>Rewards: </b><br>\r\n<li>The rewards will be distributed according to a scholarship one has filled. Generally, the scholarship amount is INR 1000 to 5000 per month.<br>\r\n<li>Under Graduates- INR 1000 per month<br>\r\n<li>Post Graduates-INR 2000 per month<br>\r\n<li>Diploma Courses- INR 1500 per month<br>\r\n<li>Engineering/Medical-INR 5000 per month<br>', '<li>Marksheet of last board/ Council/ College/ University exam<br>\r\n<li>Admission Receipt<br>\r\n<li>Family Income Certificate<br>\r\n<li>Scanned copy of bank passbook (page continuing <br>\r\n<li>Account Number and IFSC code)<br>\r\n<li>Marksheet of Madhyamik Exam<br>\r\n<li>Domicile Certificate (as Voter ID/ Aadhaar ID/ Ration \r\nCard/ Certificate) issued by Concerned Authority<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '5000/ month.', '[\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"ITI\",\"Engineering\",\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"Diploma\",\"Professional course\"]', 'null', '\"Class 11, Class 12, Undergraduates, Postgraduates, professional courses\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"West Bengal\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 250000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-11-09', '2023-03-15', 'Government of West Bengal,', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-09 10:22:33', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-15 03:34:18', 1,