(1513, 'E838GugJ7eKSR5EF2V', 'Scholarship', 'AIPMST Scholarship Test primary', 'https://aipmstprimary.co.in/', 'online scholarship test, free scholarship test, b pharma scholarship, b sc nursing scholarship, scholarship for bsc nursing students, scholarship for b pharm students, scholarship for paramedical students, bmlt scholarship, paramedical scholarship, bpt scholarship, scholarship b pharma, b pharma scholarship online, scholarship for degree students, graduate degree scholarships, degree scholarship apply, degree scholarship, graduate scholarship, scholarship for degree students in karnataka, degree scholarship status, bachelor scholarships, study grants, student funding, scholarship programs, fully funded scholarships, undergraduate scholarships, free scholarships, the global scholarship, best scholarship website, scholarships for indian students, financial help for students, student scholarship, student financial aid, grants for college, apply for scholarships, Scholarships, free scholarships to apply for, free online scholarship', 'AIPMST  Test - Scholarship for bsc nursing & b pharm students', 'Scholarship Examination is conducted for candidates who are aspiring to study in B Pharma, B Sc Bio Tech, Nursing, Paramedical, B P T, Agriculture & B M L T.', 'AIPMST Test - Scholarship ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=StnMle0gwNI', 'AIPMST (Primary) Scholarship Examination is a unique and the most prestigious pre-medical entrance examination conducted for scholarship and financial support to the aspirants for the best group of participating universities and colleges all over India.<br><br>\r\n<li>This Scholarship Examination is conducted for candidates who are aspiring to study in B. Pharma, B.Sc. Bio-Tech, B.Sc. Nursing, Paramedical, B.P.T, B.Sc. Agriculture (Hons) and B.M.L.T courses AIPMST (Primary) fields. <br><br>\r\n <li>AIPMST (Primary) has helped students to realise their dreams of pursuing graduation in their respective fields after 10+2 (with subjects