d Marksheet\r\n<li>Original Character Certificate from the head of the institution last attended<br>\r\n<li>ST/ SC/ OBC/ PH Certificate from a competent authority (if applicable).<br>\r\n<li>10th Level Pass Certificate and marksheet<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '', '[\"Professional course\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"B. Pharma, B.Sc. Bio-Tech, B.Sc. Nursing, Paramedical, B.P.T, B.Sc. Agriculture (Hons) and B.M.L.T\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 500000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-05', '2023-03-30', 'All India Pre-Medical Scholarship Test', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-12 12:35:54', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-02 03:53:42', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
