(1520, 'lAH06J7fD12Dpng1V3', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Logo Design Competition for G20 DIA', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/logo-design-competition-g20-dia/', 'logo, logo making contest, competition, logo maker, free logo maker, logo creator, logo maker online, contest, cash prize, win cash prize, contest reward, art and artists, artist, digital art, competitions, Logo making, free competitions, logo competition, Logo design contest, contesting, online competitions, art competition, online logo making', 'Logo Design Competition for G20 DIA | win cash prize', 'MyGov is organizing a competition to design a logo for the G-20 Digital Innovation Alliance (G20-DIA). Logo should be aligned with Indiaâs G20 Presidency logo.', 'Logo Design Competition for G20 DIA', '', 'India has embarked upon an ambitious journey by taking over the G20 presidency. During Indiaâs Presidency, we Endeavour to demonstrate Indiaâs leadership on global issues. \r\nThe Digital Economy Work Group (DEWG) is a crucial work stream of G20 through which we intend to anchor our Honâble Prime Ministerâs vision for the world, in line with Indiaâs G20 Presidency theme âVasudhaiva Kutumbakam -One Earth, One Family, One Future.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<li>As part of these efforts, the Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology (MeitY) has launched the âG20 Digital Innovation Allianceâ (G20-DIA). The G20 Digital Innovation Alliance (G20-DIA) mission is to showcase innovative solutions and create an alliance of innovation ecosystem players, including startups, investors, mentors, and institutions who are building digital public goods/innovations for the betterment of economies and the upliftment of societies.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>As part of the G20-Digital Innovation Alliance, MeitY is launching a series of events, expert sessions, webinars, capacity building workshops around the six selected themes to ensure fruitful and constructive engagement of innovators, entrepreneurs, startups, corporates, investors, mentors etc. <br><br>\r\n\r\n \r\n<li>MyGov is organizing a competition to design a logo for the G-20 Digital Innovation Alliance (G20-DIA) that will depict the true potential and objective of G20-DIA, i.e. inclusive, decisive, and outcome-oriented global startup ecosystem working for the upliftment of humanity. The G20-DIA logo should be aligned with Indiaâs G20 Presidency logo.<br><br>\r\n \r\n \r\n<b>Technical Parameters:</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>The G20-DIA logo should be aligned with Indiaâs G20 Presidency logo and reflect the values, vision, and overall approach of Indiaâs G20 Presidency. There should be similarities, complementarity, and synergies between the G20-DIA logo and Indiaâs G20 Presidency logo.<br><br>\r\n<li>The participant should submit a high-resolution (600 dpi) image of the logo in JPEG, PNG, BMP, or TIFF SVG formats only.<br><br>\r\n<li>The logo should be distinctive and scalable. It should be usable in large hoardings, posters, creatives, and any kind of print material and be appropriate for any kind of web device.<br><br>\r\n<li>The winner shall be required to provide the original open-source file of the designed logo.<br><br>\r\n<li>The logo can be in multi-color but should be convertible to monochrome too.<br><br>\r\n<li>Logo should look clean (not pixelated or bit-mapped) when viewed on-screen at 100%.<br><br>\r\n<li>Entries should not be submitted in compressed or self-extracting formats.<br><br>\r\n<li>The logo design should not be imprinted or watermarked.<br><br>\r\n<li>All fonts should be converted to Outlines/Curves.<br><br>\r\n \r\n \r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n<li> Winner will get INR. 10,000 (Rupees Ten Thousand Only).<<br><br>\r\n\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '10000', '[\"All\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"\\\"All\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', NULL, '[\"All\"]', 'Both', '[\"All\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-13', '2023-01-22', 'Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology (MeitY), Govt. Of India.', 10000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-16 16:10:49', 1, NULL, '2023-01-17 06:34:33', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1521, '6bDvbqgURXn3sqTp1A', 'Scholarship', 'Mindler Scholarship and Talent Hunt ', 'https://navigate.mindler.com/scholarship', '', '', '', '', '', 'Mindler has announced the Mindler Scholarship and Talent Hunt for the season and it was launched by Kiran Bedi as per the official statement. \r\n  In order to provide proper opportunities for the students who are currently studying in class 12 and those who are struggling to continue their higher education after completing class 12th exams the scholarship will be provided to them.   <br> <br>\r\n<li>More than 50000 people will be participating in the talent hunt for season 3 and this is a free-of-cost initiative.\r\nThe initiative will be helping the youth to get connected with the right Universities and get the opportunity to continue their higher education without having to worry about financial differences. <br><br>\r\n<li>The candidates will be selected based on different types of parameters such as learning aptitude and also emotional quotient. The assessment will be done on the basis of the co-curricular and extracurricular achievements of the students also.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>The applicant must be a resident of India .<br>\r\n<li>The applicant must be currently studying in class 12th seeking admission to UG universities in 2023.<br><br>\r\n \r\n1. What is the last date to apply for the mindler scholarship and talent hunt 2023?<br>\r\n<li>You can apply for the mindler scholarship and talent hunt 2023 before the last date of <b>20th January 2023</b>.<br><br>\r\n2. What are the benefits available under the mindler scholarship and talent hunt 2023?<br>\r\n<li>The <b>top 10 performers will be able to get a 50% scholarship</b> to any Indian University under the mindler scholarship and talent hunt 2023.<br><br>\r\n \r\n3.How can I check the results for the mindler scholarship and talent hunt 2023?<br>\r\n<li>You can check the result for the mindler scholarship and talent hunt 2023 on<b> 31st Janu