(1522, '9c8Pm7lgp23Yp8lfx4', 'Scholarship', 'Google Venkat Panchapakesan Memorial Scholarship', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfgH-ZuKNz1QjbaKzbHl4fIjmlZ0L2bZf3-laQq39vHR86W4A/viewform', 'scholarship for engineering students, scholarship for civil engineering students, scholarship for Mechanical engineering students, scholarship for CS engineering students, scholarship for Computer science students, College Scholarship, B tech scholarship, Student scholarship, Scholarships, Engineering scholarships, scholarship for student, study grants, Student financial aid, Student funding, Bachelor scholarships, Technology scholarships, grants for college, scholarship programs, fully funded scholarships, undergraduate scholarships, free scholarships', 'Venkat Scholarship - Scholarship from google', 'Google Venkat Panchapakesan Memorial Scholarship will be available for computer science students, The scholarship amount is Rupees 54000 approx', 'Google Venkat Scholarship', 'https://www.youtube.com/@TheGlobalScholarshiporg', 'one of the most prestigious scholarship schemes available for people wanting to study Computer Science as a means of making their life easier in many ways.<br><br>\r\n<li>Google Venkat Panchapakesan Memorial Scholarship  will be available for students who are currently pursuing computer science courses and are wanting to develop solutions so that they can make their daily life easier. <br><br>\r\n<li>The scholarship amount for the beneficiaries will be Rupees 54000 approximately .<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>The candidate must currently be enrolled in an undergraduate or graduate program in any college/university in India.<br><br>\r\n<li>Candidates must be pursuing a degree in computer science, computer engineering, or a closely related field.<br><br>\r\n<li>Venkat Panchapakesan Memorial Scholarship is a one-time scholarship. While previous applicants are encouraged to reapply, unfortunately, previous recipients of any Google scholars