tudying MBBS Course.<br>\r\n<li>The students who are studying the MBBS course will not be provided with Internship payment.<br>\r\n<li>Under Category A, a total of 120 numbered scholarships are available.<br><br>\r\n<b>Category B:</b><br>\r\n<li>Under this category, no postal course will be considered for the scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>The candidates who have got admission to any of the professional courses in the Institutions mentioned below are to be awarded this scholarship under this category.<br>\r\n<li>A total of 360 scholarships will be awarded to the candidates. Out of a total of 240 are given to B category students.<br>\r\n<li>In Category B, scholarship amounts of Rs. 24000/- (Twenty-four thousand) per annum are to be awarded.<br><br>\r\n<b>Discipline details:</b><br>\r\ni) Integrated degree courses in Medicine or Engineering (any branch), including extension centers of BITS Pilani and BIT-Mesra.<br>\r\nii) Postgraduate studies in Engineering, Medicine, Computer Sciences, Business Management, Personnel Management, Agriculture Science, Bio-Technology, Bio-Chemistry, Information Technology, B.Sc. Hospitality & Hotel Management.<br>\r\niii) Diploma course in any branch of Engineering.<br>\r\niv) Degree or full-time diploma courses in Hotel Management & Catering and Fashion Technology.<br>\r\nv) Five-year Degree Course in Law, Five years integrated courses in Law.<br>\r\nvi) Degree course in Journalism / Mass- media Communication.<br>\r\nvii) Sports Management.<br>\r\nviii) Film Fine and Arts.<br>\r\n \r\n', '<li>Photocopy of Original mark sheet of the latest qualifying Examination.<br>\r\n<li>One passport-size photo for Part A of the form.<br>\r\n<li> Photocopy of receipt of Tuition Fee.<br>\r\n<li>Service Certificate Photocopy in case of ESS/ Retired/ MSS/EFBS/FBS.<br>\r\n<li>Bank Pass Book Photocopy.<br>\r\n<li>Handicapped Certificate Photocopy issued by Government authority/photocopy of medical service book.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \