(1529, 'Y7Fb5zF2t9ytBgDOFP', 'Scholarship', 'Great Thinkers International Fellowship Program ', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScg-21dYD7kwTMzd_meOOw6q87HoIa52cEkamX31YtQCxAQRw/viewform', 'family medicine fellowships, fellowship program in management, neuroradiology fellowship, online fellowship, junior research fellowship, fellowship, post doctoral fellowship, fellowship program, research fellowship, the fellows, national fellowship, fellowship in dentistry, free scholarships to apply for, free online scholarship, free scholarship in india, find a scholarship, best scholarships for indian students, new scholarship, all india scholarship, Great Thinkers Fellowship, Think Different Global \r\n', 'Great Thinkers International Fellowship', 'Great Thinkers International Fellowship 2022-2023 - The best speakers will be recognized for the annual Think Different Global Great Thinkers of the Planet List', 'Great Thinkers Fellowship', '', 'Think Different Global is a community of great thinkers and young enthusiastic people who are working on educating people about the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (UN SDGs) using the tools of education, art, media, and events.<br><br>\r\n<li>After the success of last yearâs fellowship program, they are inviting applications for the Great Thinkers International Fellowship 2022-23 in which we are welcoming people from every discipline and culture who live an alive passion to pushing humanity forward by working on the UN SDGs. We believe passionately in the power of ideas and the potential of youth to solve the biggest problems that the world is facing.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<li>If youâre a keynote speaker/author/philosopher/journalist/traveler/artist/musician/poet/activists/entrepreneur / NGO head or someone who has pursued life with a different approach and has some ideas worth sharing to push humanity forward, we want to meet you through this program. <br><br>\r\n<li>During the fellowship, youâll be engaged in producing online blogs, talks, events, etc that will be planned by Think Different Global to structure the effective delivery of your greatest ideas, collective consciousness, and human wisdom.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility: </b><br>\r\n<li> Commitment to working on the mission and vision of Think Different Global. <br>\r\n<li> Be available to work with Think Different Global for at least one virtual webinar and article. <br>\r\n<li>You must also be available to participate in and contribute to a thriving and connected global community, both virtually and in person when possible. <br>\r\n<li>The TDG Fellows program is not an academic fellowship and non-traditional achievers are welcome. <br>\r\n<li> In addition to impressive accomplishments, fine character and a good heart are also important traits they look for in TDG Fellows.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits:</b><br>\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> The best speakers will be recognized for the annual TDG Great Thinkers of the Planet List.<br>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>The fellowship will give access to TDG Resources to discuss challenges and ideas toward achieving the United Nations SDGs and pushing humanity forward.<br>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Youâll give a TDG Talk on youtube Livestream.<br\r\n>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li> Free TDG Membership for all the participants.<br>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<li>Think Different Global Certification to people who will deliver TDG talks.<br>\r\n\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '', '[\"Professional course\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"\\\"Professional courses\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', NULL, '[\"All\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 800000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-12-29', '2023-01-26', 'Think Different Global community .', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-19 16:22:09', 1, NULL, '2023-01-20