(1530, '9UU2rQfLDLv0GNN92h', '', 'JN Tata Endowment for the Higher Education', 'https://jntataendowment.org/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Since its establishment by Jamsetjee Nusserwanjee Tata, the promoter of the Tata Group, in 1892, the 130-year-old J N Tata Endowment has awarded loan scholarships to more than 5,600 Indian students, drawn from all over India. The Endowment supports only overseas higher studies â Masterâs, Ph.D., and Post-doctoral fellowships, in any education stream. Based only on Merit, it seeks to reward, âthe best and most gifted so as to make them of the greatest service to the countryâ.\r\nEligibility:\r\n Candidates should be Indians, not older than 45 years as on June 30, 2023, and graduates of a recognized Indian University with at least 60% marks on average in their undergraduate or post-graduate studies. If the undergraduate degree is not from a recognized University in India, candidates are not eligible to apply.\r\n \r\n \r\n* Candidates who did not get selected in the previous year/earlier for the loan scholarship and candidates who could not avail of the loan scholarship when they were selected are eligible to apply. Such candidates are required to follow the entire selection process.\r\n \r\n \r\n* Candidates who missed applying to the J N Tata Endowment at the beginning of their overseas studies may apply at the end of 1st year or the beginning of 2nd year provided there is a minimum of 12 months remaining in their studies, at the time of award of the loan scholarship, which is usually July of any calendar year.\r\n \r\n \r\n* Candidates in the final year of their degree courses and those awaiting results are eligible to apply. Candidates may apply even if they do not have the admission/offer letters at the time of making the application, from the Universities to which they have applied for the academic year 2023-2024. However, they must update their application status with the Endowment once they secured admission by sending an appropriate email to jnte@tatatrusts.org by quoting the reference number which appears on the top left side of the form.\r\nCandidates who are planning to study for diplomas of at least 1 year duration whose entry-level requirement is higher secondary level are not eligible to apply.\r\nCandidates going overseas for seminars, conferences, training, workshops, paper presentation, undergraduate studies, and any post-graduate degree/diploma/certificates through Distance learning or online medium are not eligible to apply.\r\nCandidates planning to pursue postgraduate and undergraduate studies in India are not eligible to apply.\r\nThe course to which candidates are admitted must be recognized as a Graduate Program (post-graduate in Indian terminology).\r\nJ N Tata scholars who have fully repaid their existing loan scholarship amount are eligible to apply.\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '', 'null', NULL, '\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-03', '2023-01-17', 'Tata Group', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-19 17:55:29', 1, NULL, '2023-01-19 12:25:29', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1531, 'aUZOaRUpoAIloOspKq', 'Scholarship', 'N S Ramaswamy  Fellowship', 'https://www.iimb.ac.in/nsrpredoc-admission', 'family medicine fellowships, fellowship program in management, neuroradiology fellowship, online fellowship, junior research fellowship, fellowship, post doctoral fellowship, fellowship program, research fellowship, the fellows, national fellowship, fellowship in dentistry, free scholarships to apply for, free online scholarship, free scholarship in india, find a scholarship, best scholarships for indian students, new scholarship, all india scholarship, Prof N S Ramaswamy Pre Doctoral Fellowship, research fellowship\r\n', 'N S Ramaswamy Pre Doc Fellowship 2023', 'Prof N S Ramaswamy Pre Doctoral Fellowship is a research opportunity offered by the IIM Bangalore to graduate, postgraduate & professional degree holders.', 'NSR Pre doc Fellowship', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKKSBExfE8E', 'The Prof. N. S. Ramaswamy Pre-Doctoral Fellowship 2023 is a research opportunity offered by the Indian Institute of Management Bangalore (IIMB) to graduate, postgraduate, and professional degree holders. The programme is specially designed around the needs of doctoral-level students. It is a one-year apprenticeship programme that provides individuals interested in an academic career with valuable training and experience before they apply to doctoral programmes in business and related fields.<br><br>\r\n<b>Academic eligibility:</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>A Masterâs Degree (Bachelorâs degree obtained in 10+2+3 pattern, followed by a Masterâs degree) or a 5-year Integrated Masterâs Degree (obtained after completing higher secondary schooling in 10+2 pattern) in any discipline, with a minimum of 60 per cent marks in the Bachelorâs as well as the Masterâs degrees.  OR<br><br>\r\n   \r\n<li>A professional qualification such as CA, ICWA, or CS with at least 50 %marks.OR<br><br>\r\n  \r\n\r\n  \r\n<li>A 4-year/8-semesters bachelorâs degree (10+2+4 pattern) with at least 60 % marks.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<li> The applicants holding a Doctoral degree or pursuing a Doctoral programme are not eligible to apply.<br><br>\r\n \r\n \r\n \r\n<li>Candidates in the final year of the qualifying programme can also apply. Such candidates, if selected, will be allowed to join the programme provisionally only if they submit a certificate by the date of registration to the programme (latest) from the Principal/ Head of the Department / Registrar or Director of the University / Institute (issued on or before the date of registration to the NSR Pre Doc 2023 programme) stating that they have appeared for the examinations (including practical examinations) in all the subjects required for obtaining the Masters / 4-year Bachelorâs degree / equivalent eligible qualification. Their admission will be confirmed when they submit the mark sheet and a certificate of having passed the Masterâs / 4-year Bachelorâs degree / equivalent eligible qualification referred to in the certificate issued by the Principal / Registrar of their College / Institute. The deadline for submission of the mark sheets and the Degree Certificate is September 30, 2023.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Please note that all applications must meet the 60% eligibility norms. Non-fulfilment of these conditions will automatically result in the cancellation of the provisional admission. If you are currently working and want to join our programme you need to quit your current job before the start date of the programme.\r\n<br><br>\r\n <b>Area of Specialization:</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>The 2023-24 N. S. Ramaswamy Pre-Doctoral Fellowship is available in the following disciplinary areas within management scholarship and research: \r\nDecision Sciences, Economics, Entrepreneurship Finance & Accounting Information Systems, Marketing, Organizational Behavior & Human Resource Management, Public Policy Production and Operations Management, Strategy.<br><br>\r\n \r\n \r\n<b>Duration of the Programme:</b><br>\r\n \r\n \r\nThe programme\'s duration is 12 months (April 2023 through March 2024).<br><br>\r\n \r\n<b>Benefits:</b>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The selected candidates will receive a tuition fee waiver, a monthly stipend of INR 30,000 and a house rent allowance of INR 15,000.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Degree Certificates', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '15000', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Graduates, Postgraduates, Professional courses\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-12-21', '2023-01-31', ' Indian Institute of Management Bangalore ', 15000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-20 13:25:33', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-31 05:01:15', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
