(1561, '7sDOSm2unDly87zJiS', 'Scholarship', 'Danish Siddiqui Journalism Scholarship', 'https://dsfasia.org/scholarships/', '', '', '', '', '', 'An Immersive Scholarship Program Providing students with a comprehensive learning environment outside the classroom while taking care of the financial barriers to education for all-around development.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li> \r\nPreference will be given to applicants from economically weaker sections.,br>\r\n<li>Family income should be less than Rs. 350,000.<br>\r\n<li>Those whoâve secured admission in journalism degree courses at a government college are eligible to apply.<br>\r\n<li>Students who are admitted in any Journalism Degree course at any college in India are eligible for Danish Siddiqui Journalism Scholarship<br>\r\n<li> This scholarship will be provided on the basis of academic performance & financial needs.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<b>1]. What Is The Selection Criteria ?</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>Scholarships will be awarded on the basis of academic merit and financial needs. The decision made by the selection panel will be considered final.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<b>2]. What Is The Duration Of The Scholarship Award?</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>The scholarship is for one<br>\r\n (1) year with an extension to the second year of study, as appropriate on case to case basis and shall be conditional on the scholar maintaining a satisfactory level of performance as determined by the college. <br>\r\nThe maximum duration of the scholarship award is two (2) years.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<b>3]. When Is The Deadline For Submission Of Application?</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>You can send applications for scholarships once youâve secured admission to the college. Scholarships are awarded on a rolling basis.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<b>4]. Can I Apply To More Than One College At The Same Time?</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>Yes. You may apply to more than one college simultaneously. However, you should mention this in the application form.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits:</b><br>\r\n<li>Yearly Scholarship- Rs. 50,000.<br>\r\n<li>Career Planning & Guidance.<br>\r\n<li>Mentees From News & Media.<br>\r\n<li>Internships.<br><br>\r\n<b>Scholarship Application Procedure:-</b><br>\r\n<li>Online Application.<br>\r\n<li>Interview.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Contact Details:-</b><br>\r\nAddress- 2A, FF, <br/>Kehar Singh State, <br/>Saidulajab, ND 110030.</br>\r\n<b>Email- info@dsfasia.org</b>\r\n \r\n', 'As prescribed', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '50000', '[\"Bachelors\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Undergraduates (journalism degree)\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', NULL, '[\"All\"]', 'Both', '[\"All\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 350000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-01', '2023-01-31', 'Danish Siddiqui Foundation', 50000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-31 10:24:59', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-31 05:40:53', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1562, 'tBGa9nedf9eQi6jDQN', 'Abroad', ' Huayu Enrichment Scholarship', 'https://docs.google.com/document/d/1y_hin3QaUAOjO0F6XcLE3pNQGjLhK3sz/edit?usp=share_link&ouid=104204871366814080442&rtpof=true&sd=true', '', '', '', '', '', 'The MOE Huayu Enrichment Scholarship Program is offered for the Mandarin learner including beginners to study at any university-affiliated language center in Taiwan. (https://lmit.edu.tw/lc/school).<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>To encourage South Asian students/applicants to undertake Mandarin courses in Taiwan; in order to provide them with opportunities to increase their understanding of Taiwanese culture and society, and to promote mutual understanding and interactions between Taiwan and the international community.<br><br>\r\n <li>Applicants should apply directly to the Mandarin language centers (as attached) for admission, and submit the scholarship application form and all required documents to Education Division, TECC in India, in person or through an agent, from <b>Feb 1st to March 31st, 2023.</b> From 2023, applicants are required to submit the certificate/transcript of TOCFL. The level of the result is not mandatory.<br><br>\r\n \r\n<li>You are requested to read the guideline and obey the directions. Your application will not be accepted if you fail to submit all required documents. You will receive a registration serial number once you have submitted the application with all the required documents.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Applicants above the age of 18, who possess a high school diploma or above, have shown excellent academic performance, and are of good moral character are eligible.<br><br>\r\n<li>âCertificate/transcript of Test of Chinese as Foreign Language (TOCFL)â is required to apply for Huayu Enrichment Scholarship. The level of the result is not mandatory. <br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Candidates with one of the following qualifications cannot apply: </b><br>\r\n<li>An overseas Chinese student or a national of the R.O.C. (Taiwan).<br>\r\n<li> Currently registered as a student at a Mandarin Language Center or has sought a degree from a university or college in Taiwan.<br>\r\n<li>Has already received a HES or a Taiwan Scholarship, in the past.<br>\r\n<li> An exchange student to Taiwan, during the scholarship period. <br>\r\n<li>Currently receiving financial benefits from the Taiwan government or another educational institution. <br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits: </b><br>\r\n<li>The recipient will be awarded a monthly stipend of NTD 25,000. The duration of the scholarship is 3 months, 6 months, or 12 months, starting from September 1st, 2022. South Asian students above the age of 18 and possessing at least a high school diploma are eligible to apply.<br><br>\r\n<b>Important links:</b><br>\r\n<li>2023- Application-Guideline-TECC-in-India.<br>\r\n<li> 2023 â Scholarship-Application-Form TECC in India.<br>\r\n <li>Apply admission through Mandarin Language Centers.<br>\r\n<li> Registration fees-INR 1500- 2000/-.<br>.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Contact details:</b><br>\r\n<li>(For inquiries or editable version of application form, please contact Education Division, TECC in India at 11-4141 2416. ).<br>\r\n<li>Applicants need to submit the following documents to the Education Division, TECC in India, in person or through an agent, before March 31st, 2023 to the given address below.<br>\r\n<b>Address:.<br>\r\n34 Paschimi Marg, <br/>Vasant Vihar, <br/>New Delhi 110057.<br/></b><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>An application form with a photo.<br>\r\n<li>A photocopy of passport. <br>\r\n<li>A photocopy of the certificate of the highest credential and transcript.<br>\r\n<li> A photocopy of the admission/application to the Mandarin Language Center. <br>(https://lmit.edu.tw/lc/school).<br>\r\n<li> One reference letter. (eg. Taiwanese Mandarin teacher at Taiwan Education Center).<br>\r\n<li>A photocopy of an English/Mandarin/ other language proficiency certificate. (eg. IELTS/TOCFL).<br>\r\n<li> Other documents required by TECC in India (if necessary.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '25000 NTD [67000 INR]', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Diploma\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Diploma, Undergraduates\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-10', '2023-03-31', 'Ministry of Education', 67000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-31 11:08:42', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-01-31 08:51:49', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
