(1570, 'bbMzhNYjfQJ8UuyhKU', 'Scholarship', 'Dr KVR Prasad  Memorial  scholarship', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeNHeH4tQvHGYBz2E-AzVWHAcmLOiBnokRsmjKB--6DMFM5qg/viewform', '', '', '', '', '', 'Members of the HES Society have announced Dr KVR Prasad Memorial Scholarship for medical students who have cleared NEET (National Eligibility cum Entrance Test).HES Society was founded by the family members of Dr. KVR Prasad earlier this year to aid and mentor deserving individuals to excel in the fields of education, and sports and help those who need access to good healthcare but cannot afford it.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Students who are eligible for admission to a medical college on merit but cannot afford to pay the fee due to low family income can avail of this scholarship. The society will fund the studentâs undergraduate college fees for four years.HES earlier supplied essential commodities to over a hundred households during the lockdown period. The society is currently funded by the family members of the society, and the sale of the book âIâmPossibleâ, authored by Dr. K Hari Prasad.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li> Applicant should be a domicile of Telangana.<br>\r\n<li>Candidates should have secured a seat through NEET UG in a government medical college in Telangana.<br>\r\n<li> Candidates\' family income should be less than Rs 1 lakh per annum.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits:</b><br>\r\n<li>The scholarship will sponsor a Tuition fee for one year for one eligible candidate.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'As Prescribed', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'Financial Assistance', '[\"Medical\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"M.B.B.S\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"Telangana\"]', '[\"All\"]', '[\"All\"]', NULL, '[\"All\"]', 'Both', '[\"All\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 250000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-