(1600, '1o6EcFp17mnL0FfnaJ', 'Scholarship', 'West Bengal Freeship Scheme', 'https://wbhed.gov.in/wbfs/', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD4Zc0rxSLc', 'Since 2011, Govt of West Bengal has come up with a scheme about awarding of Half-tuition fee waiver or Half-freeship and Full-tuition fee waiver or Full-freeship to students belonging to specific income brackets who become eligible for the same; by virtue of their admission into Government as well as Self-financing Engineering and Technological Institutes besides Engineering Departments of state-aided Universities of the State of West Bengal after featuring among the selected candidates through the counseling conducted by the WBJEEB. The waiver is limited to the Tuition fee only for all the Institutions concerned. All other fees except tuition fees will have to be borne by the beneficiary.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Under Graduate students level in Engineering & Technology/ Pharmacy/ Architecture conducted by the self-financing private Engineering and Technical Institutions of the State, are eligible for WBFS Scholarship Scheme.<br>\r\n<li>Merit rank in State Level/National Level Entrance Examination.<br>\r\n<li>Candidate must be a domicile of West Bengal.<br>\r\n<li>The annual family income of the candidate must not be more than Rs.2.50 lakhs.<br>\r\n<li>The aforesaid WBFS scheme will be implemented for all AICTE approved Govt. Engineering & Technology Colleges, Govt. Aided self-financing Engineering & Technology Colleges and non-aided Self Financing Engineering & Technology Colleges of the state.<br>\r\n\r\n<li>Candidates of SVMCM West Bengal Swami Vivekananda Merit-cum-Means Scholarship Scheme  are not eligible to apply.<br>\r\n<li>Student should not Get any other scholarship from other State/Central Government source to apply for this scholarship.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits:</b><br>\r\n<li>The waiver is limited to the tuition fee for all the institutions concerned.<br>\r\n<li>All other fees except tuition fees will have to be borne by the beneficiary.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>Aadhar card.<br>\r\n<li>Class 10th and 12th mark sheet.<br>\r\n<li>PAN card.<br>\r\n<li>College fee receipt.<br>\r\n<li>Income certificate.<br>\r\n<li>Bonafide certificate.<br>\r\n<li>Latest academic mark sheet.<br>\r\n<li>Bank account passbook.<br>\r\n<li>Passport size photograph.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '20000', '[\"Engineering\",\"PHARMD\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"B.E, B.Tech, B.Pharm, B.Arch.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 250000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-01', '2023-03-31', 'Government  of West Bengal', 20000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-09 14:20:49', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-09 10:34:44', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
