r\n\r\n\r\n', 'A valid identity document. ID Card or passport.\r\nA photograph of the candidate taken within the last year.\r\nNational Exam results(if any).\r\nDiploma or temporary graduation certificate.\r\nTranscript.\r\nInternational exam results( GRE, GMAT, SAT.etc) if required by the chosen university or program.\r\nInternational language test results such as TOEFL, and DELF if required by the chosen university or program.\r\nA proposal for the research topic and a written example of the research you have carried out ( only for Ph.D. applications.)\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', ' 1,800 TL/month.', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', NULL, '\"Undergraduates, Postgraduates, Ph.D.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-26', '2023-02-20', 'Turkish Government', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-09 15:34:13', 1, NULL, '2023-02-09 10:04:13', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
