(1609, 'ujisEKq6tG4OjZtUwT', 'Scholarship', 'Gaon Ki Beti Scholarship ', 'https://scholarshipportal.mp.nic.in/Index.aspx', '', '', '', '', '', 'If you are currently living in the small villages of the Madhya Pradesh state then you must be very eager to know more about the Gaon ki Beti scholarship scheme presented by the Madhya Pradesh Government. The main objective of this scheme is to provide basic educational facilities to the girl child of the Madhya Pradesh state. People are not able to overcome their poverty because of illiteracy and to fill this gap the Madhya Pradesh Government is providing scholarship schemes to the poverty-stricken people of the Madhya Pradesh state.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>A girl candidate must be a resident of a village in Madhya Pradesh.<br>\r\n<li>Only a girl student is eligible for this scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>Applicants must have cleared 12th with a minimum of 60% marks.<br>\r\n<li>Must have a certificate of a village daughter.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits:</><br>\r\n<li>500 rupees for 10 months will be provided to the beneficiaries i.e a scholarship will be given of 5000 Rupees every year to each of the beneficiaries.<br><br>\r\n', '<li>Aadhar card.<br>\r\n<li>Class 10th and 12th mark sheet.<br>\r\n<li>PAN card.<br>\r\n<li>College fee receipt.<br>\r\n<li>Income certificate.<br>\r\n<li>Bonafide certificate.<br>\r\n<li>Latest academic mark sheet.<br>\r\n<li>Bank account passbook.<br>\r\n<li>Passport size photograph.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>\r\n', '5000\r\n', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Undergraduates, Postgraduates.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 200000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2022-12-30', '2023-04-14', 'Madhya Pradesh Government', 500