(1615, 'BXa2Lyydj5SJKXp5IJ', 'Scholarship', 'Rajasthan CM Higher Education Scholarship', 'http://www.hte.rajasthan.gov.in/', '', '', '', '', '', 'With the benefit of the Chief Minister Higher Education Scholarship Scheme 2023-24, every poor child who is intelligent in reading and willing to pursue higher education will be able to do so. This is a very good initiative of the Chief Ministerâs Higher Education Scholarship Scheme to provide financial assistance to children. The scheme was announced by Chief Minister Vasundhara Raje. By taking advantage of this scheme, even poor children will be able to stand on their feet after doing good studies and brighten their future.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>This scheme was implemented so that poor families do not have to face any kind of financial problem in raising their children. Despite being smart in their study, those students are unable to get further education due to poverty. The state government is aware of this, so it has announced the scheme. Due to this scheme, now every poor child will be able to get higher education. Now there will be no shortage of money in the way of such students.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>An applicant must be a permanent resident of Rajasthan.<br>\r\n<li>The annual income of the candidateâs family should not exceed more than Rs. 2.5 per annum.<br>\r\n<li>An applicant must have passed their 12th class with at least 60% of marks.<br>\r\n<li>The student who has taken place of the first 1 lakh student in the primary list of the board is eligible to apply.<br>\r\n<li>The candidate who has availed the scholarship from any other state, can also avail of the benefit under the same scheme.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits: </b><br>\r\n<li>Under the Chief Minister Higher Education Scholarship Scheme 2023-24 Rajasthan government will provide scholarships of â¹ 5000 to 1 lakh rupees annually to poor meritorious students.<br><br>\r\n<li> Under this scheme, for the students who will be eligible in the merit list of the secondary examination, the government will give a scholarship of â¹ 500 per month for 10 months i.e. the annual scholarship will be â¹ 5000. \r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>Students who are going to get higher education and get a scholarship will be given a scholarship amount at the time of study of 5 years.<br><br>\r\n', '<li>Aadhaar Card Copy is compulsory with the application form.<br>\r\n<li>The candidates will have to attach a copy of their 10th / 12th pass certificate.<br>\r\n<li>The student must be having a bank account and with the application form, he/she must need to attach a copy of the bank passbook.<br>\r\n<li>The applicants will also have to submit a copy of the Bhamashah Card with the application form.<br>\r\n<li>The candidates will have to affix his/her passport-size photo with the application form.<br>\r\n<li>The candidates will have to provide their signature on the application form.<br>\r\n<li>Attach a copy of the permanent address proof or domicile certificate with the form.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '5000', '[\"Bachelors\"]', 'null', '\"Undergraduates \"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 250000.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-05', '2023-02-16', 'Government of Rajasthan.', 5000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-11 12:35:15', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-11 07:06:27', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1616, 'Mj2cd6Elf8g9CdXmQS', 'Competitions and Awards', 'iF Design Student Award ', 'https://ifdesign.com/en/if-design-student-award', '', '', '', '', '', 'iF Design is known for outstanding design and social engagement. Our events and exhibitions celebrate just that. In addition, our brand-new iF Design Trend Report summarizes the influence of megatrends on current global design - showing the impact design disciplines have on each other and how social trends and megatrends influence each other.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>One of the most important design prizes for students from all over the world, with about 10,000 submissions each year.Together with our Sponsors, iF Design provides a platform for students and their future-oriented concepts. <br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b>\r\n<li>Students and recent graduates from all design-related courses and programs (up to 2 years after graduation) are welcome to register their entries for the iF DESIGN TALENT AWARD.<br>\r\n<li>The concepts should not be older than 2 years at the time they are submitted. We will also accept works by small teams of designers with maximum 4 team members<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n<li>Winners receive international acclaim and the best concepts earn a share of the 50,000 EUR prize money which is INR 44,14,511.01.<br>\r\n<li>On 21 and 22 June 2023, the winners of the iF DESIGN STUDENT AWARD 2023 will be celebrated in Istanbul, Turkey.<br><br>\r\n<b>Dates:</b><br>\r\n \r\n<li>Registration deadline: 8 March 2023.<br>\r\n<li>Online Jury: 18 â 27 April 2023.<br>\r\n<li>Final Jury, Berlin, Germany: 17 May 2023.<br>\r\n<li>Information to the award winners: from 23 May 2023.<br>\r\n<li>Awards Ceremony, Istanbul, Turkey: 21 â 22 June 2023.<br>\r\n<li>Publication of the award winners: 29 June 2023.<br>\r\n\r\n', 'As Prescribed.', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '50,000 EUR \r\n', '[\"Class 10 \",\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"Bachelors\"]', 'null', '\"Students, Undergraduate.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-01', '2023-03-08', 'iF Design', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-11 14:49:08', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-16 10:46:41', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1617, 'nMMgl9DzNAlVxRhnAr', 'Abroad', 'NPU International Scholarships', ' https://brightscholarship.com/npu-international-scholarships-2023-24/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Applications are invited to apply for the NPU International Scholarships 2023-24 in China.  All International Students from all over the world are eligible to apply for Scholarships at  Northwestern Polytechnical University. Students who want to pursue their Undergraduate Degree, Masterâs Degree, or Ph.D. Degrees are encouraged to apply. The University is offering Chinese Government Scholarships and NPU Presidents Scholarships. These are Fully Funded Scholarships for the Academic session of 2023-2024.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>All Academic Fields & Majors are available at the NPU under these scholarships. The Duration of the Scholarship in China will be 4 Years for a bachelor\'s Degree, 2.4 Years for Master & 4 Years Ph.D. Degree. The scholarships will cover all the expenses.\r\nNorthwestern Polytechnical University (NPU) was established in 1938 located in Shaanxi, China. NPU is ranked 27th in China. More than 28,000 students from all over the globe are currently studying at this University. <br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Foreign citizens, in good physical and mental health.<br>\r\n<li>Masterâs candidates must have a Bachelorâs Degree and should not exceed 35 years old at the time of application.<br>\r\n<li>Ph.D. candidates must have a Masterâs Degree and should not exceed 40 years old at the time of application. \r\n<br>\r\n<li>All applicants should be in good health.\r\nAged between 18 and 30 years old For Undergraduate.\r\nMust have a Valid Passport.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits and rewards:</b><br>\r\n<li>Full Tuition Fee Covered, Accommodation, Insurance, Living Allowances.<br>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Undergraduate: </b>15,00RMB/Month.<br>\r\n<li><b>Master: </b>2000RMB/Month.<br>\r\n<li><b>PhD: </b>3500RMB/Month.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>Chinese Government Scholarship (CSC) Application Form â CSC Applicants only.<br>\r\n<li>A scanned clear copy of valid passport.<br>\r\n<li>Notarized highest diploma (in Chinese/English or notarized in Chinese/English).<br>\r\n<li>Academic transcripts (in Chinese/English or notarized in Chinese/English).<br>\r\n<li>The applicantâs study plan in China (in Chinese or English).<br>\r\n<li>Certificate of Chinese/English proficiency (Exempt for those who Studied at English Institute).<br>\r\n<li>Non-criminal record (within 5 months).<br>\r\n<li>A copy of the physical examination form.<br><br>\r\n<b>For Undergraduate Applicants:</b><br>\r\n<li>Guardianâs Authorization Letter (scanned copies of both original and Notarized documents).<br>\r\n<li>Scanned copy of the guardianâs ID card.<br><br>\r\n<b>For Postgraduate Applicants:</b><br>\r\n<li>Two Letters of Recommendation in Chinese/English.<br>\r\n<li>The Acceptance Letter from the Supervisor.<br>\r\n<li>Notarized Copies of Research Achievements.<br>\r\n\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '3500 RMB/Month.\r\n', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Undergraduates, Postgraduates, Ph.D.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-26', '2023-03-15', 'Northwestern Polytechnical University', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-13 10:55:33', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-13 06:04:29', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1618, 'VN14zMadNPh6ZExL6n', 'Abroad', 'Chongqing University CSC Scholarship ', 'https://brightscholarship.com/chongqing-university-csc-scholarship-2023-24/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Applications are invited to apply for Chongqing University CSC Scholarship 2023-24 in China. The Scholarship is provided by Chinese Government. All International Students from all over the world are eligible to apply for Chinese Government Scholarships at Chongqing University of Posts and Telecommunications. Students those who want to undertake their Masters Degree or PhD Degree from Chongqing University of Posts and Telecommunications China are encouraged to apply. This is a Fully Funded Scholarship available for academic year of 2023-24.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>Multiple academic fields and majors are offered by Chongqing University of Posts and Telecommunications under Chinese Government Scholarship to study Postgraduate Degree Programs. IELTS/TOEFL is not required for CSC Scholarship. The duration of the Masterâs Degree is 3 Years & for Doctoral Degree 4 Years. The award will cover all the expenses.<br><br>\r\n<li>Chongqing University of Posts and Telecommunications (CQUPT) was established in 1950 and is a public research university. It is the fourth-largest university in China. More than 25,000 students from all over the world are currently studying at the university.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Non-Chinese citizens, and in good health.<br>\r\n<li>The requirements for the applicant\'s degree and age are that applicant must:<br>\r\n<li>Be a bachelorâs degree holder under the age of 35 when applying for the masterâs programs.<br>\r\n<li>Be a masterâs degree holder under the age of 40 when applying for doctoral programs.<br>\r\n<li>Language Proficiency Requirement<br>\r\n<li>Do not obtain any other scholarships.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Benefits and rewards:</b><br>\r\n<li>Bachelor Students: CNY 25,000/year.<br>\r\n<li>Master Students: CNY30,000/year.<br>\r\n<li>Doctoral Students: CNY35,000/year.<br>\r\n\r\n', '<li>Chinese Government Scholarship Application Form\r\nCurriculum Vitae(CV).<br>\r\n<li>Notarized highest diploma and transcripts.<br>\r\n<li>A Study Plan or Research Proposal.<br>\r\n<li>Two Recommendation Letters.<br>\r\n<li>A valid Copy of the Passport Home Page.<br>\r\n<li>Non-criminal record.<br>\r\n<li>Foreigner Physical Examination Form.<br>\r\n<li>A copy of a valid HSK or English Certificate (if available).<br>\r\n<li>Other documents, such as Papers or Articles.<li>Published or to be Published or Awarded (if available).<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'CNY35,000/year\r\n', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Undergraduates, Postgraduates, Ph.D.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-02', '2023-03-15', 'Chinese Government', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-13 11:03:10', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-13 06:03:28', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1620, '9D5xm38JLkMz0qTm3z', 'Abroad', 'University of Detroit Mercy Scholarship', 'https://brightscholarship.com/university-of-detroit-mercy-scholarships-2023-24/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Applications are invited to apply for the University of Detroit Mercy Scholarships 2023-24 in United States. All International Students from all over the world are eligible to apply for Bachelors Degree Scholarship at University of Detroit Mercy. The University of Detroit Mercy is going to provide the International Undergraduate Scholarship for the academic year 2023-2024. Students from all over the world can apply to Study Free in USA.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>The University is offering all academic fields and majors for International Students for Bachelors Degree Program. A couple of scholarships are offered by the university to students. Students can also extend their scholarship to nest year.<br><br>\r\n<li>The University of Detroit Mercy was founded in 1877 and it is the largest university in the US. it offers more than a hundred academic degrees and programs of study in liberal arts, clinical psychology, business, dentistry, education, law, engineering, architecture, nursing, and allied health professions. The university helps students to pursue their careers in their chosen subject area. It also provides valuable opportunities for students which is beneficial for the real world. <br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li><b>Eligible Countries: </b>Candidates from all nationalities can apply.<br>\r\n<li><b>Eligible Course or Subjects: </b>Pursuing a bachelorâs degree coursework in any subject.<br>\r\n<li><b>Language: </b>Candidates are required to provide evidence of English language proficiency for admission.<br>\r\n<li><b>Eligible courses:</b>\r\nSchool of Architecture, College of Business Administration, School of Dentistry, College of Engineering & Science, College of Health, professions/McAuley School of Nursing, School of Law\r\nCollege of Liberal Arts & Education.<br><br>\r\