(1621, 'KNrBuX3VyjnpVuZ0eE', 'Abroad', 'Monash University Research Scholarships', 'https://brightscholarship.com/monash-university-research-scholarships-australia/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Applications are invited to apply for the Monash University Research Scholarships 2023 in Australia. All International & Domestic Students are Eligible to apply for Monash University Scholarships. Fully Funded Scholarships are available to Pursue  Masters Degree Program or a Doctoral (Ph.D.) Degree Program at the University. These Australian Scholarships are provided by the Australian Government for Students from all over the World. The award is available for the academic session of 2023-2024.\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Every year Monash Scholarship opens two times for all students to Study Postgraduate Courses at the university. All Academic Fields and Majors are accepted for these Scholarships. More than 800 candidates will be selected every year for these awards.<br><br>\r\n<li>Monash University is a public research university based in Melbourne, Australia. Monash University staff produce over 3,000 research publications each year When averaging the worldâs major rankings, Monash University appears to be ranked fourth in Australia. QS World ranked Monash University #2 globally for Pharmacy & Pharmacology, and #26 globally for Law.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>You Must be a Domestic or an International Student.<br>\r\n<li>An Australian citizen or A New Zealand citizen.<br>\r\n<li>Australian permanent resident.<br>\r\n<li>Australian humanitarian visa holder.<br>\r\n<li>You must have a bachelor\'s Degree.<br>\r\n<li>Scholarships are awarded based on an applicantâs academic record, research output, and prior research experience.<br>\r\n<li>English Language Requirements are mandatory<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligible courses:</b><br>\r\n<li>Arts, Design & Architecture, Humanities and Social Sciences, Business, Education, Engineering, Information Technology, Law, Medicine, Nu