(1622, 'kIYYYhMxuLiqJp3vci', 'Abroad', 'King Abdullah University Scholarship', 'https://kaust.askadmissions.co.uk/emtinterestpage.aspx?ip=inquire&_ga=2.123179273.38785890.1667131821-1102282607.1667131821', '', '', '', '', '', 'Applications are invited to apply for the King Abdullah University Scholarship 2023-24 in Saudi Arabia. All International Students from all over the world are eligible to apply for KAUST Scholarship for Master and PhD Students in 2023. KAUST is Accepting Applications for the Spring and Fall of 2023. Students who want to undertake their Master, MS/Ph.D., Ph.D. Doctorate Degrees are encouraged to apply. There is No Application Fee to apply for the Scholarship 2023 at King Abdullah University of Science and Technology.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>Every year almost 100+ awards are provided by KAUST to students from all over the world. KAUST is offering a wide range of academic fields which consists of Natural Sciences, Engineering, Computer, Physical Sciences & many more subjects.<br><br>\r\n<li>KAUST University was founded in 2009 and is located in Thuwal, Saudi Arabia. It is a private research institution. This university is the 8th fastest-rising university in the world. University has a lot of national and international students enrolled. It is providing high-quality education.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Candidates from all over the world with any Nationality are eligible.<br>\r\n<li>Applicants with a Bachelorâs degree are eligible to apply for Masterâs Degree programs.<br>\r\n<li>Aspirants with a Masterâs degree are eligible to apply for Doctoral Degree programs.<br>\r\n<li>Applicants must be healthy both physically and mentally, excellent in academic standing and with good conduct.<br>\r\n<li>Applicants may not hold any other scholarship at the same time.<br>\r\n<li>Complete and Full Application Form should be submitted.<br>\r\n<li>There is No Application Fee.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits:</b><br>\r\n<li>Registration Fee and Full Tuiti