(1623, 'cpueW5Manbgxj6NF0p', 'Abroad', 'GIST International Scholarships', 'https://brightscholarship.com/gist-international-scholarships-korea-2023-24/', '', '', '', '', '', 'One of the Prestigious Universities. All International Students from any part of the world are eligible to apply for the Gwangju Institute of Science and Technology Scholarship 2023/24. GIST is offering Masters\'s Degree Scholarships, Doctoral Degree Scholarships, and master\'s leading to Ph.D. Scholarships for all students. Aspirants who want to study on Fully Funded Scholarships in Korea are encouraged to apply.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>GIST is offering all study fields and majors under this scholarship to undertake Masters\'s Degree, Ph.D. Degree, or MS leading to Ph.D. The scholarship will cover all the expenses to study abroad. The award duration for Masters\'s Degree is 2 Years and for Ph.D. degree, it is 4 Years.<br><br>\r\n<li>The Gwangju Institute of Science and Technology (GIST) was established in 1993 located in South Korea. GIST is a research university by Korean Government. According to QS World Universities Ranking it is ranked 3rd worldwide and 4th in South Korea. Students can learn leadership qualities at this university. <br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Students with any nationality from any part of the world are eligible to apply.<br>\r\n<li>To apply for Masters\'s Degree Scholarship, applicants must hold an Undergraduate Degree.<br>\r\n<li>To apply for Doctoral Degree Scholarship, You must hold a Masterâs Degree.<br><br>\r\n <b>Benefits:</b><br>\r\nGIST International Scholarships 2023-24 in South Korea is a Full Free Scholarship for International Students to pursue masters or PhD degree from Korea\'s number 1 university. The award will cover all the expenses to complete your degree. Detail is given below:<br><br>\r\n1. Complete Tuition Fee: 3,415,000 won per semester.<br>\r\n2. Monthly Stipends:<br>\r\n<li>Masters\'s Degree: 140,000 won per month.<br>\r\n<li>Ph.D. Degre