(1642, 'MnuHWpLgzG0vKIrxSy', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Hindustan Olympiad ', 'https://www.hindustanolympiad.in/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Hindustan Olympiad 2023 is a national-level Olympiad that is presented in order to empower around 11 lakh students so that they can continue their education without the problem of financial differences. The students who will perform really well in the Olympiad will be able to get the benefits according to the number of marks that they have achieved in the Olympiad. \r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>Hindustan Olympiad 2023 is created in order to provide opportunities to the people who are Academy gifted and through the development of this opportunity the people will be able to identify their talent and they will be able to apply for the different types of scholarships available on the different levels of education. The students will have to register themselves before the last date in order to be eligible for the opportunity. A proper examination will be conducted by the concerned authorities and the students will be able to take that exam in order to successfully get the scholarship opportunity presented by the organization. The students who will get good marks in the exam will be getting this scholarship.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>It is open for all students of classes 1st to 12th. <br>\r\n<li>Unlike most âone-subjectâ examinations, Hindustan Olympiad reveals the competence levels in all major subjects where every participant is given a certificate and an assessment report.<br><br>\r\n<b>Benefits and awards:</b><br>\r\n1. School Level Prizes this year.<br>\r\n<li>Participation â Certificate.<br>\r\n2. District Level.<br>\r\n<li>The Topper of each class (1st to 12th) at the District level will get a cash scholarship of Rs 2100 & a merit certificate.<br>\r\n3. State Level.<br>\r\n<li>The Topper of each class (1st to 12th) at the State level will get a trophy, a cash scholarship of Rs 5100 & a merit certificate.<br>\r\n\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'Rs. 50 Lakh\r\n', '[\"Primary\",\"Secondary\",\"Class 10 \",\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\"]', 'null', '\"Class 1st to Class 12th.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-31', '2023-02-22', 'Hindustan Times.', 5000000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-16 16:07:21', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-16 10:38:35', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
