(1681, '0NuhLJFCXStFqnTA4w', 'Scholarship', 'DCT Scholarship Scheme Goa', 'https://www.dempos.com/', '', '', '', '', '', 'A new scheme has been launched by the famous Dempo Charities Trust to provide the chance amongst the financially weaker students of Goa for further studies.To provide an opportunity of pursuing post-graduation or professional education among the weaker section students of Goa, the Dempo Charities Trust has launched a new scheme known as DCT Scholarship Scheme Goa.   <br><br>\r\n\r\n<li>Under this scheme, meritorious and deserving students of the weaker section of society will be able to pursue post-graduation and professional courses without thinking about any financial hurdles. The main aim of launching the DCT Scholarship Scheme in Goa is to help financially weak students to take admission in further studies to build their future and develop self-confidence. All interested applicants who want to apply under this scheme will have to visit the official website of  Dempo Charities Trust.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:- </b>Above given schedule is tentative as it may vary according to the situation of the country or as per the norms provided by the concerned.authorities<br><br>\r\n<b> Eligibility:</b><br>\r\nThe following eligibility criteria are required to avail of the benefit under DCT Scholarship Goa.<br>\r\n<li>An applicant must be a permanent resident of Goa.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The candidate must have taken admitted to a professional or postgraduate program in Goa.<br>\r\n<li>The applicant must have completed the graduation degree with 80% of marks from the recognized University.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The candidate must not be availing the benefit of any other scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>The annual family income of the applicant should not exceed more than Rs. 6 lacs from all the sources.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Benefits and Rewards:</b><br>\r\nThe following rewards will be provided to the selected student to avail the benefit under DCT Scholarship Scheme Goa.<br>\r\n<li>This scholarship will help the financially weak Students of Goa to pursue higher education.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Under DCT Scholarship Goa, the student will be able to pursue their post-graduation and professional education.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>All the selected students will get the total Financial Assistance of Rs. 5,00,000.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>This scholarship will be provided to the hundred deserving students of the state.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>This financial assistance will cover tuition fees and other charges including mess fees and hostel fees.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>Selection Criteria Under DCT Scholarship Goa:</b><br>\r\nThe following selection criteria are needed to avail the benefit under DCT Scholarship Goa.<br>\r\n<li>Firstly the Dempo Charities Trust will appoint a panel.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>They will be responsible for the verification of applicants.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>After the verification, they will give a list of selected students to trustees.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The list of candidates which has been given to the trustees will get a reward.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>50% of the scholarship is reserved for the girlâs candidate.<br>\r\n', 'The following documents are needed to avail of the benefit under DCT Scholarship Goa.<br>\r\n<li>Aadhar card.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Income certificate.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Previous yearâs examination marksheet.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Letter of admission to the professional of post-graduation program.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Receipt of tuition fees hostel fees mess fees.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Date of birth certificate.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>IT returns both parents.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Bank account passbook.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Domicile certificate.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Passport size photograph.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Mobile number.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '5,00,000\r\n'