Masters\",\"Professional course\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"\\\"Undergraduate, Postgraduate, Technical, and Professional courses\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 100000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-28', '2023-04-26', 'Odisha Government', 15000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-28 13:03:29', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-28 07:40:47', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1683, 'hDR3DMQ4ThRtYov9N6', 'Scholarship', 'Padala Charitable Trust Scholarship', 'https://pct-india.org/', '', '', '', '', 'https://youtu.be/Bw6dBQeeYj8', 'It is no secret that higher education is the ticket for a better life. But due to poverty and lack of resources many students drop out after 10th class and Intermediate. Helping the needy to have access to higher education through scholarship is increasingly important to assist them in realizing their dreams.\r\nPadala Charitable Trust (PCT) started Scholarship Programme in 2002 with a theme of âEncouraging Brilliance Among the Poorâ. PCT identifies academically talented students who cannot pursue higher education due to financial handicap and encourage them by providing monetary and moral support.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>Padala Charitable Trust Scholarship It is quite plain for those students who are financially and economically disabled students but they are very much Desirous about their studies and willing to study this scholarship in the hope of providing a little help to those students. Padala Charitable Trust Scholarship Scheme has been started in 2002. There will not be any hindrance to get this scholarship, irrespective of caste and religion, and all the gender candidates are eligible for this scholarship. To date, these organizations have awarded 812 scholarships to students and given only through the Educational Scholarship Program.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Objectives:</b><br>\r\n<li>We have strict guidelines for scholarship applicant selection.<br>\r\n<li>We support students only from government schools & colleges.<br>\r\n<li>The selection process is unique to pick the most needy.<br>\r\n<li>We inculcate values in our scholars by involving them in our other programmes as well. We have 2-3 interactive sessions & workshops every year to train scholars on employability skills & Life Skills.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Candidates must be Bonafide students of Andhra Pradesh or Telangana.<br>\r\n<li>The student must have completed his previous education from an affiliated college or university.<br>\r\n<li>Candidates should have got 75% in his qualifying exam and relaxation for the physically handicapped applicant will be given<br>\r\n<li>The candidate must have qualified for the 10th or 12th examination.<br>\r\n<li>The candidate must be from a poor family with no other source to fund his/her education.<br>\r\n<li>The candidate who got a free seat in college must have secured a good rank in the entrance test.<br><br>\r\n<b>Courses Considered by PCT Scholarship:</b><br>\r\nPehchaan Charitable Trust scholarship 208 will offer educational scholarships for deserving students pursuing Intermediate (2 years), Diploma in Engineering (Polytechnic) (3 years), Diploma in Education / Pharmacy (2 years), Undergraduate Non-Professional Courses (3 years), (B.A, B.Sc, B.Com), Undergraduate Professional Courses (4 years), (B.E, B.Tech), B.Ed Course (1 year), Postgraduate Non-professional Courses (2 years) (MA. M.Sc, M.Com), Medicine (MBBS) (5 years).<br><br>\r\n<b>Instructions to fill out the application form:</b><br>\r\n1. After Downloading the Application form from the official website then fill the application form with necessary details such as name, DOB and Candidates have to note this point that is separate applications are available for Fresh And Renewal applicants.<br><br>\r\n2. The application form must be filled out correctly and sent to PCT address.<br>\r\n<b>Registered Office<br/>\r\nPadala Charitable Trust<br/>\r\nEleswaram (PO), <br/>E.G.Dist. â 533429<br/>\r\nAndhra Pradesh, INDIA.</b><br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Contact details:</b><br>\r\n<b>Address:</b>Padala Charitable Trust, \r\nYeleswaram E.G.Dist 533429 A.P.<br>\r\n<b>E-mail: </b>padalasurya@yahoo.com<br><br>\r\n\r\n', '<li>Address proof.<br> \r\n<li>Voter id card.<br> \r\n<li>Two passport size photo.<br>\r\n<li>Income certificate.<br>\r\n<li>12th certificate.<br>\r\n<li>Entrance exam marks.<br> \r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '5000\r\n', '[\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"Diploma\",\"Professional course\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Class 11, Class 12, Diploma, Pharmacy, B.A, B.Sc, B.Com, B.Ed MA. M.Sc, M.Com, B.E, B.Tech, MBBS\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 150000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-27', '2023-04-25', 'Padala Charitable Trust ', 5000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-28 13:13:47', 1, 'nikhil@triwits.com', '2023-03-15 04:00:59', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1684, 'XBX4N8OU8q6PNKI8nY', 'Scholarship', 'Balika Distance Education Scheme', 'https://hte.rajasthan.gov.in/online-scholarship', '', '', '', '', '', 'The Balika Durasth Shiksha Yojana for girls and women has been implemented in Rajasthan by the Chief Minister of Rajasthan, Ashok Gehlot. Through this scheme, every year 36 thousand 300 girls and women of the state will be provided higher education through distance medium, who cannot go to college and university regularly due to various reasons.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<li> The state government will also give reimbursement of fees paid to these girls and women institutions for taking education. For which approval of Rs 14.83 crore has been given.State Chief Minister Ashok Gehlot had announced to implement this scheme in the state in the budget of 2022-23. It was approved by the Chief Minister only in the implementation of the said announcement. Now Balika Durasth Shiksha Yojana has been implemented by the government in the entire state.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Objectives </b><br>\r\nThe objectives of the proposed fee reimbursement scheme in Rajasthan state are as follows:-<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>To support education of girl child in UG, PG, Diploma, Certificate courses under ODL (open and distance learning) by reimbursing fee. <br>\r\n<li>To improve Gross Enrollment Ratio (GER) as well as the ratio of female and male proportional representation in higher education that is, Gender Parity Index (GPI).<br> <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Target group for Balika Distance Education Scheme Rajasthan.</b><br>\r\n<li>Girl students of Rajasthan who are admitted in courses under distance education mode in the state funded Universities/ State Government Institutes including IGNOU. <br>\r\n\r\n<li>State funded Universities of Rajasthan included under section 2(f) & and 12(B) of UGC Act and IGNOU are only allowed in the scheme. <br> <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>Age limit: No age limit. <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The scheme is applicable to Girl candidate, who is resident of Rajasthan and has taken admission in distance education mode in UG, PG. Diploma, Certificate courses etc. in any state funded university/ State Government Institutions including IGNOU. Preference will be given in order of PG, UG, Diploma, Certificate courses.  <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Only Distance education mode is covered under the scheme. <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The candidate who is availing of other foo reimbursement in State Government Schemes during the same tenure is not eligible in this scheme. But these students will get reimbursement of difference amount of \"existing scholarship\" and \"distance education scheme for girls-2022\". In addition, prize/incentive scholarship holders will also not be excluded. <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The candidate who is eligible for distance education course in Post matric/ Other Schemes of Social Justice department, Government of Rajasthan will get fee reimbursement from the existing process of fee reimbursement under Social Justice Department Other Department. The candidate will not get fee reimbursement from SJE portal under the category \"DE-HIE\". <br>\r\n<li>Girls who are outstanding in studies will get incentives/prize. <br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Nature of assistance Under Balika Distance Education Scheme</b><br>\r\n<li>Fee reimbursement for UG, PG, Diploma, Certificate courses under distance education mode for full duration of a course. <br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>No other additional grant will be payable.<br>\r\n', '<li>Aadhar card.<br>\r\n<li>Class 10th and 12th mark sheet.<br>\r\n<li>PAN card.<br>\r\n<li>College fee receipt.<br>\r\n<li>Income certificate.<br>\r\n<li>Bonafide certificate.<br>\r\n<li>Latest academic mark sheet.<br>\r\n<li>Bank account passbook.<br>\r\n<li>Passport size photograph.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'Fee reimbursement\r\n', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"Diploma\",\"Professional course\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"Diploma, Undergraduates, Postgraduates, Professional Courses.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 200000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-25', '2023-03-08', 'Government of Rajasthan.', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-28 13:37:29', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-07 04:59:59', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
