(1687, 'TjSNkWCWueq6q8Wn9t', 'Competitions and Awards', ' Future Generation Art Prize', ' https://futuregenerationartprize.org/', '', '', '', '', '', 'The Future Generation Art Prize is a biannual global contemporary art prize to discover, recognise and give long-term support to a future generation of artists. A highly respected selection committee appointed by a distinguished international jury reviews every application and nominates 20 artists for the shortlist. These artists will be commissioned to create new works on view in exhibitions at the PinchukArtCentre in Kyiv and the Venice Biennale.<br><br>\r\n<li>Generation Art Prize, established in Ukraine and run by Ukrainian foundation, will not accept submitted Russian and Belarusian applicants. The competition is open to artists from around the world. Participants must be aged between 18 and 35.All works of art, regardless of category or media are eligible for submission.Applications are accepted via the internet. \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Submission must include:</b><br>\r\n<li>Your portrait photo.<br>\r\n<li>CV (bio, your exhibitions).<br>\r\n<li>descriptions and photos or videos of your works <li>(you will need to upload at least 3 works).<br>\r\n<li>The competition is free to enter.<br><br>\r\n<b>Prizes:</b><br>\r\n<li>The main prize winner receives US $100,000 split between a $60,000 cash prize and a $40,000 investment in their practice.<br>\r\n<li>A further $20,000 is awarded as a special prize/s between up to five artists at the discretion of the jury for supporting projects that develop their artistic practice.<br>\r\n\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', ' $60,000', '[\"Class 12\",\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\",\"Post Doctoral \"]', 'null', '\"Between 18 and 35 years.\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-23', '2023-04-30', 'Ukrainian foundation', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-28 16:00:18', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-02-28 10:34:54', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1688, 'psrJMtPBq8HobGSUXK', 'Scholarship', 'Talentsprint Scholarship', 'https://we.talentsprint.com/?utm_source=PR&utm_medium=Businesswire&utm_campaign=WECohort5', '', '', '', '', '', 'Women played critical roles in the development of computer programming, software engineering, and computer science. However, the percentage of women in the global tech workforce has been declining, with women holding less than 26% of tech jobs globally. To address this gender gap, Women Engineers (WE) is a 24-month immersive and LIVE online learning experiential program offered by TalentSprint and supported by Google. The program aims to select, train, and nurture deserving first-year women engineering students to become world-class software engineers. Talentsprint Scholarship for Women Engineers 2023 offers a 100% scholarship that covers the complete program fee along with a rewarding cash scholarship to the selected participants.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>Talentsprint Scholarship for Women Engineers 2023 has already positively impacted over 730 students who were shortlisted from over 78,000 applicants in its first four cohorts. The program alumni are currently working with top-tier tech companies, showcasing the potential of the program in shaping the future of women in tech. The upcoming cohort will have 200 seats, and the program will offer a 100% fee scholarship that covers the complete program fee and a rewarding cash scholarship to the participants. This initiative provides an excellent opportunity for women engineering students to receive specialized training, gain hands-on experience, and develop the necessary skills to succeed in the tech industry. By providing opportunities to deserving women engineering students and supporting them in their career goals, we can empower women to make their mark in the tech industry and drive innovation and progress.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<li>The applicant must be a first-year student pursuing an undergraduate degree in engineering (B.Tech/BE) in a recognized college or university in India.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Specializing in IT / CSE / ECE / EEE / Maths / Applied Maths or equivalent.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The applicant should have a minimum aggregate score of 70% in their 10th and 12th standard board examinations.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The applicant must have a valid JEE Main or JEE Advanced score.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The applicant must be a woman.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Benefits of Talentsprint Scholarship for Women Engineers</b><br>\r\n<li>The Women Engineers (WE) program offers a 100% scholarship that covers the complete program fee along with a rewarding cash scholarship to selected participants. The program aims to select, train, and nurture deserving first-year women engineering students to become world-class software engineers.<br>\r\n<li> The scholarship covers the complete program fee, including all the training, mentorship, and other resources provided by the program. The program offers a 24-month immersive and LIVE online learning experiential program that provides specialized training in software engineering. <br>\r\n<li>The program offers various opportunities for hands-on experience, including working on real-world projects, participating in hackathons, and collaborating with industry experts. These opportunities can help the students gain valuableinsights into the industry, make meaningful connections, and advance their careers in engineering.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n', 'The following documents require in order to successfully apply for the scholarship opportunities:<br>\r\n<li>Scanned copies of 10th and 12th standard board examination certificates and mark sheets.<br>\r\n<li>Scanned copy of a valid JEE Main or JEE Advanced scorecard.<br>\r\n<li>A statement of purpose (SOP) explaining the applicantâs interest in pursuing a career in software engineering and how the program will help them achieve their career goals.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Any additional documents as specified in the application form.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>\r\n', '1,00,000', '[\"Engineering\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"\\\"\\\\\\\"B.Tech, BE\\\\\\\"\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 300000.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-22', '2023-03-08', 'TalentSprint and supported by Google ', 100000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-01 09:34:35', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-09 05:51:49', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1689, '0mhlkGUbuhJG1yHgxb', 'Scholarship', 'All India Meritorious Scholarship Test ', 'https://www.aimset.in/', '', '', '', '', '', 'All India Meritorious Scholarship Test 2023 also famous with its short name as AIMST is a yearly competition test for all those type appliances who recently passed in class 11th, 12th, and 12th giving them a facility to compete in the country level and get grants of the listed rewards. AIMST scholarship sample papers you can download from google online. AIMST provides the biggest opportunity for young minds to show their talent and also to let them know their aptitude skills, problem-solving capabilities, etc. Also, the candidates belonging to a weak financial background are eligible to apply for this scholarship under the need cum merit-based scholarship. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>AIMSET Application Procedure</b><br>\r\n<li>Step 1. Registration at www.aimset.in Applicants are requested to register themselves at www.aimset.in with their active Email id and Mobile Number.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Step 2. Application Fee Payment the applicants must fill up their application forms, pay fees (through Debit card/Credit card/Net Banking), and submit them online.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Step 3: Upload your Document After completing the payment you can proceed to upload the document like Aadhar, 10th & 12th Marksheet etc.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Step 4: AIMSET Counselling Result will be released * @ www.aimset.in\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Application Fee:</b><br>\r\n<li>General / OBC:Rs. 1200/- +GST,br>\r\n<li>Girls Candidates of all Category: Rs. 1000/-+ GST<br>\r\n<li>SC/ST/PH: Rs. 1000/-+GST<br><br>\r\n \r\n<b>AIMST 2023 Dates:</b><br>\r\n<li>Online Registration & Date of Notification Available:May 2023<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Application Form Last Date Submission is:August 2023<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Entrance Exam Date: 05 August 2023 and 07 August 2023<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Result Declaration Date: 10 September 2023<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Counselling Result: 20th October 2023<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\n<b>Educational Qualification:</b><br>\r\n<li>The candidate must have passed the final examination of 10+2 50% marks in all subject PCB. 10+2 appearing students are eligible. NEET appearing students are eligible can apply for All India Meritorious Scholarship Test 2023 because you are eligible for this exam.<br><br>\r\n<li>500 students securing 95% or above marks in AIMSET are eligible for scholarship (Full Tuition Fee for 4 years in Govt. Colleges and, 1- Year fee in Pvt. Colleges as per mention the list of colleges on the website) for studying in any of the 300+ Govt. Approved AIMSET Participating colleges and universities.<br><br>\r\n<li>700 students securing marks more than 85% and less than 95% in AIMSET are eligible for scholarship (Tuition fee for 1st year in Govt College and, 50% tuition fee for 1 year in Pvt. College) for studying in any of the 300+ Govt. Approved AIMSET Participating colleges and universities.<br><br>\r\n<li>5000 students securing marks more than or equal to 75% and less than 85% in AIMSET are eligible for scholarship (Standard Laptop) for studying in any of the 300+ Govt. Approved AIMSET Participating colleges and universities.<br><br>\r\n<b>AIMST Pattern:</b><br>\r\n<li>There will be Objective type or Multiple Choice questions .<br>\r\n<li>Total 60 questions.20 questions from each subject. Duration is 40 minutes.<br>\r\n<li>Topics/Subjects: Elementary Math/Mental Ability, Current Affairs / GK, Verbal Ability.<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b> Important information for the participants of the AIMST Exam â Firstly, there will be no negative marking for the wrong or missing solutions. Secondly, the medium of the question paper will be English only.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>AIMST selection procedure</b><br>\r\nThere are two phases to receive the scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>Merit-based scholarship:- Students have to pass online Tests and Interviews for a scholarship.<br>\r\n<li>Need cum merit-based scholarship:- Studentsâ family income and board marks and Written exams are seen for the scholarship.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Rewards:</b><br>\r\n<li>1st Prize;- 25,000 for 4 students <br>\r\n<li>2nd Prize:- 10,000 for 40 students<br>\r\n<li>3rd Prize:- 5,000 for 80 students<br>\r\n<li>80 percentile & Above:- Certificates for 1,000 students<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>AIMST Exam Contact Details:</b><br>\r\n<li>All India Meritorious Scholarship Test<br>\r\n<li>Website: https://www.aimset.in/<br>\r\n<li>Phone Number: +91-8527484563<br>\r\n<li>Email: contact@aimset.in<br><br>\r\n', '<li>10+2 Marksheet.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>5 Photograph<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Age proof certificate (Birth certificate / 10th marksheet).<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>AIMSET Scorecard and Admit card of AIMSET.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Migration Certificate.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>NEET Scorecard for MBBS, BDS, BAMS.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>SC / ST / OBC / PH certificate.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Seat allotment certificate / Admission receipt.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Student Aadhaar card & Father Aadhaar card.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>\r\n', '25000\r\n', '[\"Class 12\",\"Medical\"]', 'null', '\"Recently passed 11th & 12thSTUDENTS,  NEETAspirants\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 200000.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-03-27', '2023-03-31', 'AIMST ', 25000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-01 10:34:21', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-01 05:06:50', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1690, '9HwEkReHYpd5HzPD5W', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Inviting videos of transformative impact', 'https://innovateindia.mygov.in/beneficiary-videos/', '', '', '', '', '', 'Over the last few years, the government has launched various schemes for the welfare of the citizens. These schemes have not only helped citizens to financially empower themselves, but have also improved their lives in every way resulting in making India the 3rd largest economy in the World. These schemes have helped in eradicating India from the clutches of poverty, malnutrition, and other social challenges. At the same time, these schemes have created huge infrastructure to be used by citizens.<br><br>\r\n<li>The implementation of these schemes is based on various aspects, including the evaluation process, understanding, accessibility, acceptability, and capabilities for last-mile implementation.\r\nMyGov is a citizen engagement platform to give easy and single-point access to information about several welfare schemes of the Government. In this context, MyGov is organizing a \"Inviting Videos of Transformative Impact,\" encouraging all citizens to submit videos of beneficiaries describing how a particular scheme/schemes have benefited them or their community or their village/ city.<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b>The video should focus on the âBeforeâ and âAfterâ transformation and should highlight the benefits received from the scheme/schemes.<br><br>\r\n<b>Participation Guidelines:</b><br>\r\n<li>The video should focus on the âBeforeâ and âAfterâ transformation and should highlight the benefits received from the scheme/schemes.<br>\r\n<li>In the case of video submission, participants should upload their video to any media platform such as SoundCloud, YouTube, Google Drive, Dropbox, or any social media platform and share that link in the submission box.<br>\r\n<li>The maximum length of the video is 2 minutes, and the minimum length should not be less than 50 seconds.<br><br>\r\n<b>Awards and Recognition:</b><br>\r\n<li>The Best submitted videos will be rewarded with cash prize of Rs. 2,000/- each to the maximum of 25 BEST videos in a month.<br>\r\n<li>For the month of January 2023, BEST videos to the maximum of only 10 will be awarded.<br>\r\n<li>All selected BEST video winners will receive a Certificate of Recognition from MyGov.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Terms and Conditions:</b><br>\r\n<li>All Indian citizens may participate.<br>\r\n<li>Participants are required to register themselves on the platform <br>\r\nhttps://innovateindia.mygov.in/by filling a simple registration form.<br>\r\n<li>Citizens can participate in all the categories choosing from the drop down Menu, but can upload only one video for each category.<br>\r\n<li>Multiple submission is allowed for a participant.<br>\r\n<li>Incomplete entries will not be considered.<br>\r\n<li>The video entries should be original.<br>\r\n<li>All entries obtained through unauthorised sources or which are incomplete, illegible, mutilated, altered, reproduced, forged, irregular, or fraudulent in any way or otherwise not in compliance with the rules are automatically void.<br>\r\n<li>All videos will be intellectual property of MyGov and participants shall not exercise any right or claim over it.<br>\r\n<li>The winning entries may be used by the Government of India or at any other place for promotional/ or display purposes, Information and Communication materials, and for any other use as may be deemed appropriate.<br>\r\n<li>It is strongly advised not to wait until the deadline for the submission of entries. Organisers shall not be responsible for non-receipt of entries on account of server errors/ traffic.<br>\r\n<li>The organizers reserve the right to select or reject any submission without assigning any reasons whatsoever and without thereby incurring any liability to the participant(s) whatsoever.<br>\r\n<li>The organizers will reserve the right to use the submitted entries for promotional, advertising and display purposes and to assign it to any person or group of people.<br>\r\n<li>The organizers reserve to cancel the competition or modify the rules, dates of the competition anytime. The Organizers shall have no liability whatsoever for any inconvenience/loss directly or indirectly caused to any Participant due to such modification of rules/cancellation of competition and the Participants shall accordingly not be entitled to raise any claims pertaining to the same.<br>\r\n<li>Once the participants have made submissions on the platform, they shall have no claim even in the event of stoppage/cancellation of the competition.\r\n<li>Removal/ voluntary withdrawal of members is not encouraged. No other form of modification will be entertained at any point.<br>\r\n<li>Once such a nomination has been received, organizers may correspond with the nominee/nominator for supplementary information, if necessary.<br>\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'Rs. 2000 & Certificate of Recognition', '[\"All\"]', 'null', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-01-23', '2023-03-31', 'MyGov', 2000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-01 11:53:27', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-01 06:34:28', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1691, 'qucYqLP5DfiPmpityE', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Capture beauty of Rajasthan photo contest', 'https://rajasthan.mygov.in/task/capture-beauty-rajasthan-photography-competition', '', '', '', '', '', 'Rajasthan is one of the most beautiful, old and colourful states of India which is known for the land of kings and queens and grand forts and palaces. Rajasthan is a hit tourist spot among Indians as well as international travellers. It is a state whose cities are nicknamed after various colours, like Jaipur is the Pink City, Jodhpur is the Blue City and so on.<br><br>\r\n<li>In this context, MyGov Rajasthan is organising a âPhotography Competitionâ, encouraging the citizens to visit their nearest tourist attractions and capture Rajasthan\'s true essence and beauty.Participants can also share their photographs using #BeautyofRajasthan tagging @MyGovIndia and @MyGovRajasthan on any social media platforms like Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Koo, Roposo etc.<br><br>\r\n<b>Gratification:</b><br>\r\nThe Best entry will be rewarded with a Certificate of Appreciation.<br>\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', ' Certificate of Appreciation\r\n', '[\"All\"]', 'null', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-27', '2023-03-31', 'MyGov Rajasthan', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-01 12:12:29', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-01 06:44:03', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1692, 'kDxEbDCUuMadlv6HBe', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Share unknown spots of Mizoram', 'https://mizoram.mygov.in/task/photography-competition-share-unknown-spots-mizoram', '', '', '', '', '', 'Mizoram is one of India\'s most beautiful and lush green State, also known as the \"Songbird of India.\" Mizoram\'s moderate climate, which is comfortable even during the summer, makes it an appealing destination for all tourists. The state\'s vast culture and grand festivals have an irresistible charm that cannot be explained or read; it can only be felt once you are in the peaceful, serene land of Mizoram. The dense greenery and the 21 hill ranges that stretches across Mizoram\'s territory are sure to drive you to another world.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<li>Mizoram provides a calm, serene environment with exciting outdoor activities in beautiful lush green surroundings that keep you close to nature. Mizoram welcomes you to explore its beauty and richness with grand festivals and happy people dressed in colourful traditional costumes.<br><br>\r\n<li>In this context, MyGov-Mizoram is organising a âPhotography Competitionâ, encouraging the citizens to visit and capture the true beauty of Mizoram, which is still unknown to the world.Participants can also share their photographs using #MyMizoram tagging @MyGovIndia and @MyGovMizoram on any social media platforms like Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Koo, Roposo etc.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Gratification:</b><br>\r\nThe Best entry will be rewarded with a Certificate of Appreciation.<br>\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'Certificate of Appreciation', '[\"All\"]', 'null', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-21', '2023-03-31', 'MyGov-Mizoram ', 0.00, 'javer