(1697, 'MMXkhdycnCahs1AQL9', 'Abroad', 'PTDF Overseas Scholarship Scheme', 'https://scholarship.ptdf.gov.ng/create/applicant', '', '', '', '', '', 'Under its PTDF Overseas Scholarship Scheme, the Petroleum Technology Development Fund (PTDF), an agency of the Federal Government, is currently accepting applications from qualified individuals for overseas MSc and PhD scholarships to particular programs at particular institutions for the academic year 2023â2024.<br><br>\r\n<li>The Oil and Gas Industryâs needs are being met by the Petroleum Technology Development Fund (PTDF), a federal body with the responsibility of building indigenous human capability and petroleum technology.<br><br>\r\n<li>The scheme was developed to offer candidates the opportunity to benefit from a diversified pool of knowledge and the facilities offered by world-class institutions across the globe. Under it, candidates are invited to apply through PTDF to specific programmes at partner institutions.The award includes the provision of flight tickets, payment of health insurance, payment of tuition and bench fees (where applicable), and the provision of allowances to meet the costs of accommodation and living expenses.<br><br>\r\n<li>For the 2023/2024 award, applications will be limited to PTDF partner universities in the United Kingdom, Germany, France, and Malaysia where it feels the scholarshipâs high standards can be maintained and the objectives of the scheme will be best served.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b><br>\r\nTo be eligible for PTDF Overseas Postgraduate Scholarship Scheme, applicants are expected to meet the following conditions:<br>\r\n<li>Academic merit as evidenced by the quality of degrees, full academic transcripts and other professional qualifications acquired.<br>\r\n<li>Relevant publications to be referenced by applicant (PhD applicants only)\r\n<li>Membership in professional bodies.<br>\r\n<li>The viability of the study/research plan.<br>\r\n', 'Applicants are advised to scan copies of the following documents and attach them to their online application forms:<br>\r\n<li>First Degree Certificate or Statement of Result.<br>\r\n<li>NYSC discharge certificate.<br>\r\n<li>WAEC/GCE/SSCE/NECO results and the PINs on the application forms to enable PTDF to view the Oâlevel results on the relevant website.<br>\r\n<li>Recent Passport Photograph.<br>\r\n<li>Local Government Identification Letter<br>\r\n<li>Masterâs Degree Certificate (PhD Applicants only).<br>\r\n<li>Evidence of membership in professional association.<br>\r\n', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', 'Financial Assistance', '[\"Masters\",\"PHD\"]', 'null', '\"Masters, Ph.D\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-02-28', '2023-03-24', 'Petroleum Technology Development Fund ', 0.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-02 11:40:13', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-02 06:19:33', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1698, 'fpKU5LkidFKA3YoUuK', 'Competitions and Awards', 'Suggest Name for Hub  Empowerment of Women', 'https://www.mygov.in/task/suggest-name-hub-empowerment-women/', '', '', '', '', '', '<li>The Government of India has launched \'Mission Shakti,\' an integrated women empowerment programme as an umbrella scheme for women\'s safety, security, and empowerment, for implementation during the 15th Finance Commission period of 202l-22 to 2025-26.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The scheme aims to economically empower women while giving them control over their minds and bodies in an environment free of violence and threat. It also aims to reduce the care burden on women and increase female labour force participation by promoting skill development, capacity building, financial literacy, and access to microcredit, among other things.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>\'Mission Shakti\' is split into the sub-schemes \'Sambal\' and \'Samarthya\'. While the \"Sambal\" sub-scheme is for women\'s safety and security, the \"Samarthya\" sub-scheme is for women\'s empowerment.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The components of the \'Samarthya\' sub-scheme include modified versions of previous schemes such as Ujjwala, Swadhar Greh, and Working Women Hostel. Furthermore, the existing schemes of the National Creche Scheme for working mothers\' children and Pradhan Mantri Matru Vandana Yojana (PMMVY) under the umbrella of ICDS have now been incorporated into Samarthya. The Samarthya Scheme now includes a new component of Gap Funding for Economic Empowerment.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>The Ministry of Women and child development, in collaboration with MyGov, is hosting an activity where we are inviting citizens to show their creativity and suggest a suitable âNameâ that is easily relatable to the concept of Hubs at National, State/ UT and District Levels for its popularisation and broader outreach.<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>To know the mandate and functions of \'Hub for Empowerment of Women\', the participants may refer to the Guidelines of \'Mission Shakti\' available on the website of the Ministry at URL: https://wcd.nic.in/acts/mission-shakti-guidelines-implementation-during-....<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Gratification:<br>\r\n<li>Entry selected by the Jury will be rewarded with Rs. 25,000/-<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Last date of submission is 31/03/2023</b>\r\n', '', '1. Hit the below \" click here to apply \" button<br>\r\n2. Read the scholarship details carefully<br>\r\n3. Fill out the form and attach the necessary documents<br>\r\n4. Submit<br>', '25000\r\n', '[\"All\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"All\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-03-02', '2023-03-31', 'Government of India ', 25000.00, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-02 12:18:31', 1, 'javeriyayub@triwits.com', '2023-03-02 07:03:42', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
