(1749, 'qwtDdwlQxPsbSLpOgk', 'Scholarship', 'Empowerment  Equity Opportunities for Excellence ', 'https://www.serbonline.in/SERB/Registration', '', '', '', '', 'https://youtu.be/LJaANuZuTSw', 'Science and Engineering Research Board (SERB) invites applications for Empowerment and Equity Opportunities for Excellence in Science 2023 from researchers belonging to the SC and ST communities</br>\r\n<li> SERB has adopted a scientific social responsibilities policy to culture of social commitment among SERB grantees</br>\r\n<li> The board funds all the areas of Science and Engineering without discriminating any discipline to search proposals outside the normal activities of the such institution will be preferred for the proposals involving securely survey-oriented work and routine studies will not be normally considered the proposal will be funded if it has Novelty and then regulator computers to execute the project</br></br>', '<li> Biodata (under the user profile section)</br>\r\n<li> Certificate from Principal Investigator</br>\r\n<li> Endorsement Letter from the Head of Institution</br>\r\n<li> Category Certificate</br>\r\n', '<li>Applicants should first visit the official website of the SERB online portal</br>\r\n<li>The homepage will appear on your screen where you have to click on the Register link</br></br>\r\n<b>Register</b></br>\r\nNow registration page will open on your display where you have to enter your required details such as:</br>\r\n<li>  Personal details</br>\r\n<li>  Biodata</br>\r\n<li>  Photo</br>\r\n<li>  E-mail ID</br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>Funding is provided up to a maximum of Rs. 50.0 lahks (excluding overhead charges)</br>\r\n<li>The research grant will cover equipment, manpower, consumables, travel, and contingency</br>\r\n<li> Overhead Will be provided as per prevailing norms of SERB</br>\r\n<li>The duration of the project shall be a maximum of three years</br></br>\r\n', '[\"Engineering\",\"Bachelors\",\"PHD\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"\\\"Ph.D. De