(1806, 'AkxegVvui7juNZhRQs', 'Scholarship', 'Babulal Nagarmal Satnalika ', 'https://www.scholarships.net.in/uploads/590-form%281%29.pdf', '', '', '', '', '', ' Babulal Nagarmal Satnalika Scholarship is offered by  Dr Niraj Satnalika and Debi Prasad Satnalika to provide financial stability to capable and needy students. The main aim of this scholarship is to prevent dropout rates</br>\r\n<li> This endowment is offered in memory of the respected Babulal Nagar Satnalika who believed in the importance of education and wanted to see every child grow through education</br>\r\n<li> The scholarship has helped many students in completing their education and uplifting their standards in terms of knowledge and living</br>\r\n<li> It is also focused on the education of female students from classes 1st to 12th</br>\r\n<li> The scholarship will beawarded to ten students that fulfil the eligibility criteria of the scheme</br>\r\n<li> Generally, the emphasis is given to the financial background of the students i.e. need-based but merit will not be ignored as it will define the capability of the students</br></br>\r\n<b>Eligibility Criteria</b></br>\r\n<li> Only girls candidates can apply for this scholarship who are studying in class 1st to class12th</br>\r\n<li> Students must be residents of West Bengal. \r\nApplicants must apply with 80% marks throughout</br>\r\n<li> The annual family income of the applicant must not exceed 3LPA</br></br>', 'Marksheet of previous two classes attended. \r\n<li> Family income proof through salary slip, form 16, Income certificate</br>\r\n<li> ITR or any other mode</br>\r\n<li> Address Proof</br></br>', '<li> Go through the link given in this section</br>\r\n<li> Click on â Check Eligibilityâ</br>\r\n<li> You will be landing on the application page</br>\r\n<li> If you have not registered on Edufund then you must get registered with an email/mobile/Gmail account</br>\r\n<li> After registration, you will be redirected to the âBabulal Nagarmal Sc