(1809, 'OQJLPQDmggO8wLfcuj', 'Abroad', 'GeneTex Scholarship Program', 'https://www.genetex.com/article/company/index/scholarship', '', '', '', '', '', 'GeneTex believes in accelerating scientific advancement and the notion that the genesis of future discoveries begins with the support of young scientists now. The GeneTex Scholarship Program will award a $2000 (USD) scholarship to students pursuing a STEM undergraduate or graduate degree. The scholarship will be awarded to one student each semester.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b>\r\n<li>Student in good standing and enrolled at an accredited college or university\r\n<li>Declared STEM major\r\n<li>Open to international students\r\n<li>Type of institution award is open to: two-year college\r\n<li>Type of institution award is open to: four-year college\r\n<li>Award is available to U.S. citizens\r\n<li>Award is available to Canadian citizens\r\n<li>Award is available to citizens of countries other than the U.S. and Canada.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<li>Application form required\r\n<li>Essay required<br>\r\n<b>Note:</b>\r\nPlease download, complete, and return the application form and supporting documents (i.e., transcripts, letter of acceptance for incoming or transfer students, etc.) to scholarship@genetex.com. Please review your application form prior to submitting it to ensure that it is complete. Include your application and all required documents in one email.\r\n\r\n', '<li>Hit the below âClick here & applyâ button\r\n<li>Read the Scholarship details carefully \r\n<li>Fillout the form & attach necessary documents carefully\r\n<li>Submit\r\n', ' $2000\r\n', '[\"Bachelors\"]', 'null', '\"\\\"UG\\\"\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-03-11', '2023-07-16', 'Gene Tex', 0.00, 'yadwadaishwarya@triwits.com', '2023-05-15 13:57:22', 1, 'yadwadaishwarya@triwits.com', '2023-05-15 08:30:23', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL,