(1814, 'E63VNdNyv2O3Hs4RyF', 'Scholarship', 'Nirman Shramik Kalyan Yojana', 'https://scholarship.odisha.gov.in/website/student-registration', '', '', '', '', '', ' Nirman Shramik Kalyan Yojana Scholarship for ST/SC/OBC/SEBC/GENERAL/EBC Communities 2022-23, Odisha is an opportunity offered by the Labour & ESI Department, Government of Odisha to General/ST/SC/OBC/SEBC/EBC students</br>\r\n<li> Under this scholarship scheme, the students fulfilling the eligibility criteria will receive up to INR 40,000 per annum</br></br>\r\n<b>Benefits</b></br>\r\nThe selected candidates can receive the following benefits - </br>\r\n<li> Educational Assistance (on completion of 1 year) Benefits (INR) per annum</br>\r\n<li> For Class 6 and 7 to girl children 2,000</br>\r\n<li> For Class 8 to all children 2,000</br>\r\n<li> For Class 9 to all children 3,000</br>\r\n<li> For Class 10 to all children	4,000</br>\r\n<li> Cash award to all children securing 90% or above in Class 10 10,000</br>\r\n<li> For Class 11 and 12 5,000</br>\r\n<li> For B.A., B.Sc.,B.Com. and PG studies 7,000</br>\r\n<li> For\r\nB.Tech./BCA/MBA/B.Arch./M.Arch./M.Tech./M.Sc./B.Pharma./Hotel Management and catering services/Medical (includes allopathic, ayurvedic and homoeopathic) in Government colleges only 40,000</br>\r\n<li> For B.Ed/CT/Nursing training in Government colleges 10,000</br></br>', '<li> Aadhaar Card of student</br>\r\n<li> Income Certificate of parent/guardian</br>\r\n<li> Residence certificate of student</br>\r\n<li> Copy of passbook of bank account with the  account number and IFSC code of bank branch</br>\r\n<li>Passport size photograph of a student</br>\r\n<li> College Id card of the student</br>\r\n<li> Marksheet of qualifying examination</br></br>', '<li> Click on the link given here to go to the official </br>\r\n<li> webpage of the scholarship</br>\r\n<li> The homepage will open on your screen</br>\r\n<li> Click on the option called Feedback</br>\r\n<li> A new page will open on your screen</br>\