(1895, 'aGAUiwI8kd2foqE7Yh', 'Scholarship', 'E Grantz Scholarship 2023', 'https://egrantz.kerala.gov.in/', '', '', '', '', '', ' E Grantz Scholarship 2023 was launched by the Government of Kerala. This Scholarship is for the Students studying in Pre Matric and Post Matric both</br>\r\n<li> So if you are Studying in Pre or Post Matric and belongs to the Backward Category of Kerala. Then this article is for you.  Read the whole article to get the information about this Scholarship</br>\r\n<li> Main Objectives of the Scholarship is to provide financial help to the needy students from Kerala. Students can get monthly basis help from the Government of Kerala</br>\r\n<li> This scholarship portal is for all of those students who are interested in completing their education with the help of the scholarship. On this portal students can apply for various scholarship hosted on portal</br></br>\r\n<b>Eligible Criteria</b></br>\r\n<li> The Student should be studying in pre or Post-Matric level of Studies from a recognized university/Board</br>\r\n<li> Student should be from Kerala</br>\r\n<li> Scheduled Caste(SC), Scheduled Tribes(ST) and Other Backward Class(OBC)\r\nStudents belonging to SC/ST, there is no income limitation</br>\r\n<li> Students from OBC Category Income of His/Her Family should not be more than INR 1 Lakh per Annum, for +2 courses, Degree, PG and Professional Courses</br></br>\r\n<b>Note</b></br>\r\n<li> E Grantz Scholarship 2023 does not have deadline. So there is no specific time limit for any scholarship</br>\r\n<li> Eligible students can apply anytime but they need to ensure that they apply within a week of joining the institutional course program</br></br>', '<li> Adhar Card</br>\r\n<li> Second Identity Card</br>\r\n<li> Proof of Income</br>\r\n<li> Age Proof</br>\r\n<li> Caste Certificate</br>\r\n<li> Last Exam Mark Sheet</br></br>', '<b>One Time Registration</b></br>\r\n<li> First of all go to the official website of E Grantz Scholarship 2023</br>\r\n<li> Now click on the option called âOne Time Registrationâ</br>\r\n<li> New page will appear on your screen</br>\r\n<li> Now validate your Adhar</br>\r\n<li> Enter your Adhar Number and Name</br>\r\n<li> Now click on Validate Adhar</br>\r\n<li> After clicking you will go to another page</br>\r\n<li> Now enter your other personal details and mobile number</br>\r\n<li> Click on register button displayed on the page</br>\r\n<li> Your registration is complete</br>\r\n<b>Login</b></br>  \r\n<li> To login firstly go to the official page of E Grantz Scholarship 2023</br>\r\n<li> Now click on option called âStudent Loginâ given on the page</br>\r\n<li> Now login using your Credentials like Email ID/Adhar and Password</br>\r\n<li> Click on sign in button given on the page</br>\r\n<li> New application form will appear on your screen</br>\r\n<li> Fill the form with your details like Details of your Institute, Bank Details, etc</br>\r\n<li> Now click on option called âApplyâ</br>\r\n<li> Scholarships option will appear select the scholarship</br>\r\n<li> After selecting scholarship your application form will appear on your screen</br>\r\n<li> Upload your document and click on âSubmit âbutton</br>\r\n<b>Application status</b></br>\r\n<li> To track the application status first go to the official website of E Grantz Scholarship 2023</br>\r\n<li> Click on the option called âTrack Application\"</br>\r\n<li> New page will display on your screen</br>\r\n<li> Now enter Adhar number and your Date of Birth</br>\r\n<li> Finally click on the button called âTrack Applicationâ</br>\r\n<li> The status of your application will be displayed on your screen</br></br>', 'Financial Help', '[\"Class 10 \",\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"Bachelors\"]', 'null', '\"Pre Matric or Post Matric\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-04-30', '2023-12-31', ' Government of Kerala', 0.00, 'asham@triwits.com', '2023-05-25 16:09:23', 1, 'asham@triwits.com', '2023-05-25 11:16:24', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(1896, 'YGWeP99IkJR222JncG', 'Scholarship', 'Maharishi Balmiki Chatravriti Yojana', 'https://scholarships.gov.in/fresh/schemeSelRegfrmInstruction', '', '', '', '', '', ' This Maharishi Balmiki Chatravriti Yojana is a great scheme of the Himachal Pradesh government through which girl children of the state will be able to get the financial benefit from the government for their further studies</br>\r\n<li> The main motive of this scheme was to make sure to provide all the necessary things and financial help to the poor girl student of the state so that they can also get a better education for themselves</br>\r\n<li> With the help of this scheme, candidates will not be facing any problems in their education and every girl child of the state will be able to get a higher education. Through this scheme, all these girls will also feel empowered and strong</br></br>\r\n<b>Benefits</b></br>\r\n<li> Through the help of this scheme girl children of Himachal Pradesh will be able to get the finical benefit</br>\r\n<li> Through this scheme, the government will be giving 9000 rs to the girl students of the Valmiki families of the state</br>\r\n<li> To get the benefit of this scheme girls need to make sure to first clear their matric and they need to take admitted to the college</br>\r\n<li> Through this scheme girls studying in government or private the college can get the benefit</br>\r\n<li> To make the application process in this scheme applications can be made by applicants by 30th November 2023</br>\r\n<li> To make the application process in this scheme candidates need to visit the National scholarship portal</br>\r\n<li> Through this scheme, all the girls in the state will be able to get an education</br>\r\n<li> Through the help of this scheme, girls will also feel empowered</br>\r\n<li> Through the help of this scheme finical situation of the state will also get improved</br></br>\r\n<b>Eligibility Criteria</b></br>\r\n<li> The First candidate needs to be a permanent resident of the Himachal Pradesh state</br>\r\n<li> Through this scheme, only a girl child can take benefit</br>\r\n<li> Girls should be a part of the Valmiki family to get the befit of this scheme</br>\r\n<li> To get the benefit of this scheme candidate needs to be admitted in post-matric educational qualifications</br></br>', '<li> Aadhaar card</br>\r\n<li> Marksheet or certificate of educational qualifications</br>\r\n<li> The bank details of the girl child</br>\r\n<li> Passport size photograph of the girl</br>\r\n<li> Bonafide of the Himachal Pradesh</br>\r\n<li> Parents id proof</br>', '<li> The First candidate needs to visit the official website of this scheme</br>\r\n<li> After reaching the home page of the website they need to click on the registration notification and then they need to read all the instructions carefully without making any mistakes in the form</br>\r\n<li> After that, they need to click on the apply now button and then they need to fill in all the details asked in the paper form</br>\r\n<li> After this, they need to submit the scan copy of the documents asked for in the form along with the signature and the ID Proof</br>\r\n<li> After this, they need to log in first to apply</br>\r\n<li> After this, they can also take the printout of the application form for future reference</br>\r\n', '9000 Rs Yearly', '[\"Class 11\",\"Class 12\",\"Bachelors\"]', 'null', '\"Post-Matric\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-04-30', '2023-11-30', 'Himachal Pradesh Government', 0.00, 'asham@triwits.com', '2023-05-25 16:58:35', 1, 'asham@triwits.com', '2023-05-25 11:29:29', 1, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
