(1903, 'Q9GrY3ZARctsPcJ2qS', 'Scholarship', 'Esri India M.Tech Scholarship Program 2023', 'https://www.esri.in/content/dam/distributor-share/esri-in/pdf/esri-india-gis-scholarships/m-tech-scholarship-form-updated-version-2.pdf', '', '', '', '', '', ' Esri India M.Tech Scholarship Program 2023 is an opportunity offered by Esri India* to students who are at the beginning of 2nd year of their postgraduate course [M.Tech./M.Sc.] in Geoinformatics or a course that involves studying remote sensing, GIS, spatial modelling, spatial analysis, digital image processing for GIS and related subjects, for their respective students</br>\r\n<li> A total of 10 selected students will receive an annual scholarship of INR 1 lakh</br>\r\n<li> Established in 1996, Esri India Technologies Pvt. Ltd. (Esri India) is an end-to-end Geographic Information Systems (GIS) solutions provider</br></br>\r\n<b>Eligibility</b></br>\r\n<li> Be of 18 years of age</br>\r\n<li> Be residents of India</br>\r\n<li> Be at the beginning of 2nd year of a postgraduate course [M.Tech./M.Sc.] in Geoinformatics or a course that involves:\r\nRemote sensing</br>\r\nGIS</br>\r\nSpatial modeling</br>\r\nSpatial analysis</br>\r\n<li> Digital image processing for GIS and related subjects</br>\r\n<b>Note - </b>The scholarship program applies to students who get promoted to the second year of the course</br></br>\r\n<b>Benefits</b></br>\r\n<li> A total of 10 selected students will receive an annual one-time scholarship of INR 1 lakh</br>\r\n<li> Also, the selected candidates will also receive an ArcGIS Personal Use License for 1 year</br>\r\n<b>Selection Criteria</b></br>\r\n<li> The applications will be evaluated by a Jury. Institutes/Universities will be notified about the shortlisted candidates who will have to appear for a virtual interview</br>\r\n<li> The final selection will be done based on the interview results and other submitted documents</br>\r\n<li> The decision of the Jury with regard to the selection of the applicants for the scholarship will be FINAL</br>\r\n<b>Terms and Conditions</b></br>\r\n<li> The bank details provided by the student, along with the scanned copy of a cancelled cheque, for receiving the scholarship will be considered final for crediting the amount</br>\r\n<li> The company disclaims any liability due to student/ third-party actions or omissions</br>\r\n<li> Esri India reserves the right to withdraw, change the value or cancel the scholarship money or change the mode of payment, at its sole discretion</br>\r\n<li> Applicant must ensure that all submissions submitted to the Company are not subject to controls requiring government authorization for the export or release of certain technology and technical data</br>\r\n<li> Any false information provided within the context of the scholarship program by the applicant concerning identity, mailing address, telephone number, email address, ownership of right or non-compliance with these terms and conditions or the like may result in the immediate elimination of the applicant from the scholarship program without any notice</br></br>', 'Self-attested copy of the studentâs permanent address proof\r\nSelf-attested copy of the studentâs Institute ID-Card\r\nStudentâs previous\r\nFirst-year marksheet\r\nSynopsis of GIS projects done\r\nA Statement of Purpose of about 250 words', '<li> Hit the below âClick here & applyâ button</br>\r\n<li> Read the Scholarship details carefully</br>\r\n<li> Fill out the form & attach necessary documents carefully</br>\r\n<li> Submit</br></br>', '1 lakh', '[\"Masters\"]', '[\"\"]', '\"2nd year of a Postgraduate [M.Tech. M.Sc.]\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', NULL, '[\"\"]', 0, 0, '[\"\"]', 0.00, '', '[\"\"]', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-04-30', '2023-07-10', 'Esri India', 0.00, 'asham@triwits.com', '2023-05-26 12:39:18', 1, 'asham@triwits.com', '2023-05-26 07:12:25', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
