(1928, 'H5HFoyg5N08QYcB97d', 'Scholarship', 'Indira Gandhi Scholarship ', 'https://scholarships.gov.in/', '', '', '', '', '', 'University Grants Commission (UGC) introduced the Single Girl Child Scholarship to empower the girls of our country through the means of education. This Indira Gandhi Scholarship for Postgraduate Girl students will encourage them to continue their Higher Education and also support financially, especially those girls who happen to be the only child of her parents.<br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b>\r\n<li>This scholarship applicable only the Girl students.\r\n<li>Girls students, who had taken admission in a regular, full-time 1st year Master Degree (Postgraduate) course in any recognised University or a postgraduate college.\r\n<li>The age of the candidates must be within 30 years at the time of admission in the 1sf year of PG course.\r\n<li>The girl candidates must be the only child of her parents. The candidates must not have any brother though the girl students who are twin daughters / fraternal daughters can apply for this scholarship.\r\n<li>Students who are pursuing their PG course in Distance mode, are not eligible to apply for this scholarship.\r\n\r\n', '<li>Copy of Aadhar Card / Aadhar Enrollment.\r\n<li>PG Course Admission Receipt.\r\n<li>Marksheet of the last exam passed.\r\n<li>Passport Size Photograph and Signature\r\n<li>Income certificate issued by the Component Authority.\r\n<li>Single Girl Child certificate issued by the Component Authority.\r\n<li>Scanned copy of bank passbook.\r\n<li>Residential / Domicile Certificate.\r\n', '<li>Hit the below âClick here & applyâ button\r\n<li>Read the Scholarship details carefully \r\n<li>Fillout the form & attach necessary documents carefully\r\n<li>Submit\r\n', '36200\r\n', '[\"Masters\"]', 'null', '\"PG\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-06-10', '2023-09-30', 'University Grants Commission', 0.00, 'yadwadaishwarya@triwits.com', '2023-05-30 13:18:52', 1, 'yadwadaishwarya@triwits.com', '2023-05-30 07:50:08', 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
