(1934, 'xCTxQ3extH3Ccwg9To', 'Abroad', ' Teesside University Global Scholarship', 'https://www.tees.ac.uk/sections/international/international_scholarships_criteria.cfm', '', '', '', '', '', 'The Global Excellence Scholarships are based on Grade Point Average, where applicants demonstrate they exceed the advertised academic entry criteria for their course. Eligibility is assessed upon <br><br>\r\n<b>Eligibility:</b>\r\n<li>Available to full-time sponsored or self-funding international students who meet the eligibility criteria and are starting their course in September 2022.\r\n<li> The Global Excellence Scholarships are based on Grade Point Average, where applicants demonstrate they exceed the advertised academic entry criteria for their course.\r\n<li> Check the relevant country page for the specific qualifications/entry criteria that you must exceed to be considered for the Global Excellence Scholarship <li>Eligibility is assessed upon application and details are included in all offer letters. \r\n<li>The Teesside University Global Excellence Scholarships are awarded as a fee reduction.\r\n<li> These Scholarships apply to full-time students on Foundation, Undergraduate, Postgraduate Taught and Postgraduate Research programmes. Excludes students on a foundation/pathway programme delivered at Teesside University International Study Centre.<br><br>\r\nContact Email: international.scholarships@tees.ac.uk<br>\r\nContact Number: 01642 218121\r\n\r\n', '', '<li>Hit the below âClick here & applyâ button\r\n<li>Read the Scholarship details carefully \r\n<li>Fillout the form & attach necessary documents carefully\r\n<li>Submit\r\n', ' $ 12000\r\n', '[\"Bachelors\",\"Masters\"]', 'null', '\"UG, PG\"', NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'null', 'null', 'null', NULL, 'null', NULL, 'null', 0, 0, 'null', 0.00, '', 'null', 'null', 0.00, 0, 0, 0, '2023-05-28', '2023-09-01', 'Teesside University', 0.00, 'yadwadaishwarya@triwits.com', '2023-05-30 15:14:03', 1, 'yadwadaishwarya